desc: Universal Bulin. Can be used to limit break all ships of Elite rarity or below.
name: Universal Bulin

desc: Buli? Did I just get an upgrade buli? Now, I can fight too buli!
name: Universal Enhanced Rigging (Experimental) +α

desc: Prototype Bulin MKII. Can be used to limit break all Super Rare ships.
name: Prototype Bulin MKII

desc: Puriiin! The savior of the fleet disembarks, wielding a heaven-piercing drill in hand, purin! Heheh! I bet you're trembling with excitement at my latest and greatest work outfit, purin!
name: Prototype Advanced Weaponry (Prop)

desc: Specialized Bulin Custom MKIII. Can be used to Limit Break all Ultra Rare ships.
name: Specialized Bulin Custom MKIII

desc: Commander, you just breathe easy and get behind me, bulin! This time, the invincible Bulin Brigade will carry out justice for you, bulin!
name: The Bulin Bringer of Justice

desc: Farragut-class destroyer – Dewey, Hull Number DD-349.
name: Dewey

desc: Saratoga went over there, and Lexington is... Oh, Commander, good morning! Are you here to play with us, or were you just out for some fresh air...?
name: Summer Longing

desc: Lexington gave me this Christmas costume as a thank-you for always supporting her. Commander, do you think I look... pretty in it?
name: A Christmas Thank-You

desc: Mahan-class destroyer - Cassin, Hull Number DD-372!
name: Cassin

desc: I know I said we'd go shopping after school, but walking is so exhausting... I'll just hitch a ride in this cart. Looks sturdy enough...
name: Shopping Carte Blanche

desc: Commander... I think I've been in the house too long. My body feels different... Oh? I've improved? I see... Wonderful! I guess I can keep staying inside...
name: Cassin (Retrofit)

desc: Mahan-class destroyer - Downes, Hull Number DD-375!
name: Downes

desc: I heard another person was coming to help out at the store, but I never thought it'd be you, Commander! What am I doing here? Ahaha, well uh, I had a little bit of free time on my hands... right~♪
name: Part-Time Bomber

desc: Rawr! I'm Tiger Downes! What do you think, Commander? I feel great now! Faster. Stronger! Let's head out to sea and cause some trouble!
name: Downes (Retrofit)

desc: Gridley-class destroyer - Gridley, Hull Number DD-380!
name: Gridley

desc: Commander, Merry Christmas! Guhehe~ Won't you attend my "Super Special Sexy Sara (tentative)" photoshoot event?
name: Christmas Photoshoot

desc: Gridley-class destroyer - Craven, Hull Number DD-382!
name: Craven

desc: I much rather cheer for my Commander than go to class...but no matter where I go, I will definitely give it my all! Commander, wait for me to come back as the top student of this school year.
name: Cheerleader On The Playground

desc: Gridley-class destroyer - McCall, Hull Number DD-400!
name: McCall

desc:
Gridley-class destroyer, Maury, Hull Number DD-401
<color=#fad545>Unlock build after receiving</color>
name: Maury

desc: Maury, fourth ship of the Gridley-class destroyer squadron, is back with new equipment! I feel like I can run even faster than before! Commander, can we go for a test run?
name: Maury (Retrofit)

desc: Fletcher-class destroyer - Fletcher, Hull Number DD-445!
name: Fletcher

desc: Fletcher-class destroyer – William D. Porter, Hull Number DD-579.
name: William D. Porter

desc: Commander, um, we agreed that I'd be a maid for a day, right? Ahahaha... See, I couldn't make it in time. Ran into a teensy bit of trouble, and, well... Basically, I need you to come help me!
name: The Daredevil's Maidly Service

desc: Fletcher-class destroyer - Charles Ausburne, Hull Number DD-570!
name: Charles Ausburne

desc: Captain Ausburne of the Little Beavers, upgraded and ready to go! Heh heh, my new-and-improved justice isn't just for show! Evildoers are gonna be in for a bad time!
name: Charles Ausburne (Retrofit)

desc: Fletcher-class destroyer - Thatcher, Hull Number DD-514!
name: Thatcher

desc: Fletcher-class destroyer - Aulick, Hull Number DD-569!
name: Aulick

desc: Fletcher-class destroyer - Foote, Hull Number DD-511!
name: Foote

desc: Fletcher-class destroyer - Spence, Hull Number DD-512!
name: Spence

desc: Benson-class Destroyer - Benson, Hull Number DD-421!
name: Benson

desc: Fighting for love and peace this Halloween night, it's none other than the pumpkin-style Planet Bunny cutie pie, Benson!
name: Cutie Pumpkin Pie

desc: Benson-class destroyer - Laffey, Hull Number DD-459!
name: Laffey

desc: Mmph... The waistline is too high... and a little too tight... The sleeves are too breezy cause they're so big... It's not like I wanted to change clothes, but... what do you think, Commander?
name: Snow Rabbit and Candy Apple

desc: Have a happy and auspicious New Year? Uh.... can I go now...? I'm feeling a bit sleepy, so can I go back to sleep?
name: White Rabbit Welcomes the Spring

desc: I'm done changing... how is it? Today, I’m supposed to call you “valued guest?” Um... I don’t really get it...
name: Bunny Clerk?

desc: Commander, ahhn... Umm, Commander, Laffey does not need to be fed... Rather, Laffey should be the one feeding you...
name: Picnic Adventure?

desc: "Laffey came from Planet Bunny..." Umm, I forgot that line Benson told me to say... In any case, everyone, please give me lots of support... Actually, just a little support is fine... Uhh, I have to do it again with more motivation?
name: Bunny Idol @Unmotivated

desc: Yaaawn... Laffey's cleaning her room, Commander... If you don't wanna help then just find a place to sit... Anyway, back to cleaning... Zzz...
name: Sleep to Clean Another Day

desc: Laffey seems to have changed a bit... Commander, do you like how Laffey is now?
name: White Rabbit's Oath

desc: Laffey, improved and reporting in! I feel energized and ready to redouble my efforts! Hey, Commander, I still don't want you to touch my ears...
name: Laffey (Retrofit)

desc: Sims-class destroyer - Sims, Hull Number DD-409!
name: Sims

desc: Y'know, Commander~ No matter how nice you are to me, I'm still going to prank you~ Oh, but if you want my help with pranking others, I'll consider it~ Heehee~
name: Sims (Retrofit)

desc: Sims-class Destroyer - Hammann, Hull Number DD-412!
name: Hammann

desc: I'm not really happy at all! But since you're bonding with me for once, I have to say... thank y... H-hmph! I didn't say anything!
name: Rebellious Summer

desc: Hmph! I'm only here because you pleaded so desperately for me to come! Don't get any funny ideas! ...Why did I take so long to pick out my clothes? It... it's not like I was trying to impress anyone! I definitely wasn't looking forward to this party or anything!
name: Prideful Fairy of the Ballroom

desc: Ughh... These gloves are so heavy and the dress is too revealing. Why on earth did I decide to put these on... I can't show myself to Yorktown like this!
name: Hammanyan Pawnch!

desc: I-I'm nobody's surprise! Ugh, I should've never listened to Sims... Stop staring already and undo these ribbons around my arms!
name: Holy Night Surprise!

desc: Wh-why do I have to dress like this just to cheer for the Commander... Why not just let me dress how I want? Ugh... It's embarrassing, but everyone else will tease me if I run away, so what do I... Huh?! C-Commander?!
name: Blushing Fellow

desc: I'm just wearing new clothes, so why should I have to raise my skirt like this? Huh? You want me to look more upset? You... you pervert!
name: Hammann (Retrofit)

desc: Cannon-class Destroyer Escort - Eldridge, Hull Number DE-173!
name: Eldridge

desc: Merry Christmas... Commander, Eldridge's outfit... cute?
name: Holy Night's Embrace

desc: Commander, do you like Eldridge...this way? Meow~...look what I've done to my books...
name: The Inquisitive Recluse

desc: Commander... Sakura Empire's New Year, looks very fun, let's go together...? (Eldridge looks at you expectantly)
name: New Year's Outing

desc: Eldridge and kitties, idol mode... Commander, you like...?
name: Kitty Idol

desc: Eldridge, arriving at designated altitude... Moon, mooncake, and Manjuus spotted...
name: Moon Festival Spacewalk

desc: School's out... Hmm, what do we do now? ...Go out and play? (Eldridge eyes you questioningly.)
name: After-School Good Girl

desc: Everyone says this outfit is special...? Commander, do you like me... like this? (Eldridge has an expectant look in her eyes.)
name: Afternoon Worship in the Woods

desc: I got... new gear to show off to you... Commander, I'm super duper strong now...
name: Eldridge (Retrofit)

desc: Benson-class Destroyer - Bailey, Hull Number DD-492!
name: Bailey

desc: Can you see the ghost next to me? Hehehe— the black witch from Planet Bunny is none other than me, Bailey!
name: Trickster Black Rabbit

desc: Your Bunny Santa has arrived! That's right – not regular ol' Santa, but Bunny Santa! The real Santa's busy, so Bailey from Planet Bunny is here to help out!
name: Jolly Saint Bunnylass!

desc: The day has finally arrived~! Bunnies, are you ready? Bailey's debut show is about to begin! Commander, sisters, come and see my bunny magic!
name: Bailey (Retrofit)

desc: Fletcher-class Destroyer - Radford, Hull Number DD-446!
name: Radford

desc: Commander, the sweet magic within my tome lets me turn things into candy! Hehe, that sounds pretty convincing— ...Eh, Commander? Wh-when'd you get here?!
name: Sweet Magic!

desc: Fletcher-class destroyer - Jenkins, Hull Number DD-447!
name: Jenkins

desc: Commander, g-good evening...? Right now, I'm bringing presents to Radford and the others...? Could you give me a hand? Th-thank you... Um, your present.. this apple, do you want it?
name: Light of the Holiest Star

desc: Fletcher-class destroyer – Nicholas, Hull Number DD-449!
name: Nicholas

desc: I love doing relief missions as a nurse... I don't need to go outside or take part in any training, I just need to look after injured people... What about treating them? No worries, they just need to rest and they'll get better.
name: Nurse Nicholas

desc: Merry Christmas, Commander. I'm your present, probably... Would you mind closing the lid for me so I can sleep a bit more... zzz...
name: Surprise!?

desc: Commander, did you also come to play in the pool? ...Me? Fletcher said I have to help clean up because I was slacking off... Mm, watch your step~
name: Summer Cleaning "Volunteer"

desc: Commander, because you kept your promise and came... here's some chocolate, and a letter for you. Please read it later. No, it's not that big of a deal... Just a little embarrassing...
name: After-School Promise

desc: Commander, what month is it...? I think I overslept a bit... am I taller than I was before? *Yawn*... Gotta be because I slept the whole time...
name: Nicholas (Retrofit)

desc: Fletcher-class destroyer – Bush, Hull Number DD-529.
name: Bush

desc: Tadaaah! All done! How does it look? I think I'm pretty talented as an artist!
name: Budding Painter

desc: Fletcher-class destroyer – Hazelwood, Hull Number DD-531.
name: Hazelwood

desc: Yoohoo~! You the Commander? You look kinda weaksauce, though~! Name's Bache! I'm joining this fleet, starting today! I'll take good care of you, so just kick back and get ready for my greatness!
name: Bache

desc: Ahaha~! Are you seeing this, Commander? This sturdiness, this gorgeous paint job, and these special accessories hand-picked by yours truly! Muahaha! I am the true speed-star of this port!
name: Gorgeous Speed-star

desc: Tada! Your favorite tennis superstar, Bache, is right here! ...Hey Commander, you're supposed to cheer for me like you're one of my fans in the stands!
name: Showy Sports Star

desc: Benson class Destroyer— Hobby, hull number DD-610.
name: Hobby

desc: Here comes the debut of school uniform Hobby~ Commander, how do I look? Hobby is all grown up~
name: Little Idol Schoolgirl

desc: Benson class Destroyer— Kalk, hull number DD-611.
name: Kalk

desc: Kalk, reporting in once again, now with a new outfit! Hehe... Commander, will you walk me to school?
name: Snow Fairy Schoolgirl

desc: Fletcher-class Destroyer - Kimberly (DD-521)
name: Kimberly

desc: While wearing clothes from the Dragon Empery, I can't help but reminisce about those days... Hehe, Commander, do you prefer me in Empery-style clothes, or Union-style clothes?
name: Style of the East

desc: Fletcher-class Destroyer - Mullany (DD-528)
name: Mullany

desc: What's with the weird look, Commander? Ah, I got this outfit while studying abroad in the Dragon Empery. Umm... does it suit me?
name: Eastern Etiquette

desc: Farragut-class destroyer – Aylwin, Hull Number DD-355.
name: Aylwin

desc: So this is an aquarium... What a novel experience! Oh, also, I won't be your guide today as it's your turn to escort me around, Commander. Please don't get us lost, okay? Ehehe~
name: Sunday Aquarium Visit

desc: Fletcher-class destroyer - Stanly , Hull Number DD-478.
name: Stanly

desc: Destroyer Smalley, reporting in. Interests: kickboxing.
name: Smalley

desc: I am the courier of the night. In other words, it's my job to bring stuff straight to you, Commander. Here you go, this jack-o-lantern is for you.
name: Candy Courier

desc: Fletcher-class destroyer – Halsey Powell, Hull Number DD-686.
name: Halsey Powell

desc: Halsey Powell is making her debut as your lucky star for the Spring Festival! Commander, if you show me a fun time, you'll be blessed with good luck this year!
name: Spring's Lucky Star

desc: Allen M. Sumner-class destroyer – Cooper, Hull Number DD-695.
name: Cooper

desc: 30 to 15... Next match will be mine, you hear! Oh, Commander, are you here to play a round of tennis?
name: Blazing Tennis Battle

desc: Hm? I'm just wrapping up some presents! Can't just present them as-is, and all that. Hehe~ I could sure use a little help, Commander!
name: Heartwarming Holiday Hearth

desc: I'm Eagle Union destroyer Allen M. Sumner! Just call me Allen! It's a pleasure, Commander! Anyway, I've heard you've got yummy food and cushy work here at this port. That true?
name: Allen M. Sumner

desc: Welcome, Commander! I would fetch you our menu, but I've had a teensy accident here... Don't worry, I'll fix this somehow!
name: Charming Rabbit

desc: Heheh! Policewoman who protects the city's order by day, vigilante who takes from the rich and gives to the poor by night! She is phantom thief Miss Terious, or PhantoM for short! Your riches are now mine! Your dumb little traps wouldn't catch me in a hundred years!
name: Two Faces of Justice

desc: Fletcher-class Stephen Potter here. You've probably met a million of my sisters already, so I'll spare you my life story. See you around.
name: Stephen Potter

desc: Welcome to my private retreat, where you can skip work and veg out all you want. And by "skip work" I mean "enjoy your regularly scheduled day off." Anyway, make yourself at home, Commander.
name: Chillaxation Station

desc: Fletcher-class destroyer – Morrison, Hull Number DD-560.
name: Morrison

desc: Zzz... Commander? S-sorry, I fell asleep for a bit... Uh, umm, what would you like me to do...?
name: Sleeping Bunny

desc: This looks like the perfect place to film a ninja training scene... Ahem! Allow me to demonstrate my ninjutsu to you, Commander! Pl-please keep your eyes peeled! Transformation ninjutsu! Hiyah!
name: Technology or Ninjutsu?

desc: Allen M. Sumner-class destroyer – Ingraham, Hull Number DD-694.
name: Ingraham

desc: Hmm... Could use a little more sweetness, and a splash of the secret ingredient... Oh, you're here? Great. I appoint you as my first dedicated taste-tester, Commander. We're gonna come up with some novel and fresh drinks, you and I!
name: Fixin' for a Mixin'

desc: Allen M. Sumner-class destroyer – Bristol, Hull Number DD-857.
name: Bristol

desc: Happy Lunar New Year, Commander! The time's finally come to look into the age-old legends from the Dragon Empery! The truth behind these legends is bound to be as fascinating as the legends themselves!
name: Tales from the Empery

desc: Heheh! You're finally here, Commander! My current investigation is into this thing in my... Correction – into that thing that's chasing me! We gotta run, like, now!
name: "Head" Investigator

desc: Edsall-class destroyer escort – Hammann II, Hull Number DE-131.
name: Hammann II

desc: Hmph! I only promised to come to the beach because I was worried you'd be lonely! There's no deeper meaning—w-wait! What are you doing?! Stooop!
name: Another Rebellious Summer

desc: A-almost missed my chance... Ahem! N-newbie maid Hammann will... cast a scrumptious spell on you♡ Delicious, delicious, be delicious♪ Moe moe pyun! ...G-gosh, what am I doing?!
name: Hammann's Scrumptious Spells

desc: Allen M. Sumner-class destroyer – Laffey II, Hull Number DD-724.
name: Laffey II

desc: Laffey's helping out around the pop-up shop... Commander, sit wherever you want... Any open seat is probably fine.
name: Sleepy on a Busy Day

desc: Mmm, eepy... The honorable Lady Laffey of the Castle of the Bunnies requires rest... Commander... I mean, Magistrate... Our tour must wait for now...
name: Lady Laffey's Languid Tour

desc: Fletcher-class destroyer – Bell, Hull Number DD-587.
name: Bell

desc: Welcome to our saloon... Oh, no! I can't hold all these mugs! ...C-Commander? Why are you here?
name: Saloon Mishaps

desc: Fletcher-class destroyer – Miller, Hull Number DD-535.
name: Miller

desc: Don't move, Commander! ...Heheh, looks like it's time for the GOAT to take the stage. That was a sick entrance, right?! Hm? N-no, I'm not here to help you out! I'm here to, uhh... Yeah, to take revenge on the scientists who experimented on me!
name: Monster Experiment M-01

desc: Fletcher-class destroyer – Clarence K. Bronson, Hull Number DD-668.
name: Clarence K. Bronson

desc: Welcome, Commander. Your maid, Clarence K. Bronson, will serve you today. Rest easy and accept my special hospitality.
name: Special Functional Testing

desc: Omaha-class light cruiser – Omaha, Hull Number CL-4!
name: Omaha

desc: Omaha-class light cruiser – Raleigh, Hull Number CL-7!
name: Raleigh

desc: Brooklyn-class Light Cruiser – Brooklyn, Hull Number CL-40!
name: Brooklyn

desc: Brooklyn-class light cruiser – Phoenix, Hull Number CL-46!
name: Phoenix

desc: Brooklyn-class Light Cruiser – Helena, Hull Number CL-50!
name: Helena

desc: I... want to be part of the new year festivities too. Oh, you don't have to worry about me. I'm no longer the fledgling I once was.
name: New Year's Bluebird

desc: Um, Commander, could we... share a dance? I have things I want to tell you...
name: May I Have this Dance?

desc: Commander, what do you think... umm... about this swimsuit? Actually, umm, never mind. If I were to hear your impressions directly, I'd be too embarrassed to stand in front of you... So, would you mind, umm... secretly whispering it to me?
name: Shimmering Triangle Wave

desc: Eek! C-Commander? Um, I'm fine! Nothing's wrong, I just tripped on– Wait, why did the smart glass turn off?! Oh nooo!
name: Basking in the Cypress' Warmth

desc: Wh-what do you think, Commander? Does it suit me? ...I never could've imagined getting to wear this even in my dreams, let alone experience the bliss I feel now... Thank you so, so much.
name: Miracle in White

desc: This new equipment... might take some time to get used to... N-no, I'm sure I can handle it now! Commander, Helena will... meet your expectations!
name: Helena (Retrofit)

desc: Atlanta-class light cruiser – Atlanta, Hull Number CL-51!
name: Atlanta

desc: Atlanta-class light cruiser – Juneau, Hull Number CL-52!
name: Juneau

desc: This swan is so soft and pettable... Heehee, it even let me put a ribbon on it. Now we have matching looks... Huh? You could take a picture of us? I-if it's not too much work then please, by all means!
name: In the Swan Garden

desc: After all that painstaking work, I've f-finally managed to complete my retrofit! Even though I'm still afraid of getting hurt, I'll try to be brave for you, Commander!
name: Juneau (Retrofit)

desc: Atlanta-class Light Cruiser – San Diego, Hull Number CL-53!
name: San Diego

desc: Merry Christmas! Super idol San Diego, making her dazzling debut! Commander, you must come to my performance! ...Venue?! What's that?
name: Sandy Claus

desc: Commander, with the power of your love, San Diego is sure to become number one in this port! ...Number one in what? I'm not really sure myself, but I'll definitely make it happen!
name: No. 1 June Bride!

desc: Heheh~☆ I have no idea what just happened, but I feel like I've gotten super strong! Commander, can you see my sparkly aura~?
name: San Diego (Retrofit)

desc: Cleveland-class Light Cruiser – Cleveland, Hull Number CL-55!
name: Cleveland

desc: There's room for two on this pumpkin. C'mon, hurry and get on... Ah, that reminds me! I've got some pumpkin pie as well. Wanna try some, Commander?
name: Reaper Fever

desc: Why am I stuck with this tuxedo when everyone else is wearing a dress?! ... Though it does feel slick, so I guess it's pretty nice. So, weren't we gonna go to the party, Commander? Then it's about time we head out!
name: Gentry Knight

desc: Good timing! I was just about to take my little buddy here out for a road trip! Commander, there's room for two if you want to come!
name: Road Trip!

desc: Happy New Year's, Commander! I heard everyone from the Sakura Empire was dressing like this, so... Hehehe, think this looks good on me? I thought I'd ask for your impression first, Commander.
name: New Year's Challenge!

desc: Isn't it real exciting visiting a place you don't normally get to go? We don't often get opportunities to travel like this, so let's go look for delicious food and spectacular scenery!
name: Southbound Journey

desc: Ahem... I, Cleveland, am your conductor for tonight! Whoa, the echo really IS faint! How did I not know we had such a fancy concert hall at the port? ...Oh, you wanna shout something too, Commander?
name: Golden Conductor

desc: Commander, you're early. There's plenty of time until the pop-up shop opens. But this is a good opportunity to ask – what do you think of the outfit I made just for this occasion? ...G-girly and cute? Woohoo! That's exactly the reaction I wanted!
name: Knight of the Pop-Up Shop

desc: Man, this is so embarrassing... C-Commander, w-w-what do you, umm, like, think of my d-d-d-dress...?
name: Heartfelt Moment

desc: Cleveland-class light cruiser – Columbia, hull number CL-56.
name: Columbia

desc: Commander, here, I made some chocolate for you~ Come on, hurry up and take it already! Holding this pose makes me look like I'm waiting for some Prince Charming, and it's super embarrassing.
name: After-School Odette

desc: ...Mm, that's good enough for today's journal entry. Wonder what Cleve's gonna think after reading this~ What do you think, Commander? Wait... Commander? Jeez, don't wander off when I'm all focused on my writing...
name: Across the Vast Prairies

desc: Richmond
name: Richmond

desc: Brooklyn-class Light Cruiser – Honolulu, Hull Number CL-48!
name: Honolulu

desc: If everyone's focusing on the teacher, they probably won't stare at me from up front... As for the umbrella, it's... I know it makes me stand out, but I don't want people to stare at me from behind either...
name: Umbrella Girl

desc: Aaaahh! My sundae! What's up with this stupid hose?! Commander, don't just stand there, help me!
name: Summer Accident?!

desc: Just where did St. Louis find something like this... such shameless undergarments, if someone found out... Awawawaa! Commander, what are you doing in here? Get out right now!
name: Manjuu Mischief

desc: Come on, Louis, the goldfish stall is this way! ... W-why are you giving me that weird look like th– Wait... Eeeek! C-Commander?! When did you get here?!
name: Among the Stalls

desc: Brooklyn-class Light Cruiser – St. Louis, Hull Number CL-49!
name: St. Louis

desc: What do you think of this foreign dress, Commander? *Giggle* ...Perhaps it's rekindled something within you?
name: Blue and White Pottery

desc: The Sakura Empire's clothes are just so refined. Ahaha... Aren't you cold standing out there, Commander? Sit down with me and have a drink.
name: Spirits in the Snow

desc: Oh my, what a good little commander you've been, waiting here all this time for me. Hop in~ Did you think you would be driving? Hehe, you shouldn't underestimate me~
name: Luxurious Wheels

desc: Commander, I've been waiting for you. Lazing about and enjoying the sights here does sound nice, but... Heheh, it just isn't the same without you by my side♪
name: An Afternoon on the Lido Deck

desc: Cleveland-class light cruiser – Montpelier, hull number CL-57.
name: Montpelier

desc: So this is Sakura-style New Year's attire... If Cleve was also interested in this... Hm? Commander, were you watching? Um, well, Happy New Year's.
name: Flower of the Snowy Night

desc: As unreliable as you are, I didn't think you'd be too scared to approach a movie prop... You're just "admiring it from a distance?" ...Fair enough.
name: Persephone's Throne

desc: Ugh... It's so humid... And this water tastes weird... Commander? Did you just finish bathing? Alright, we could hang out if... No, you see, I've got this weird fever right now...
name: Heat Relief for the Tipsy

desc: Cleveland-class light cruiser - Denver (CL-58)
name: Denver

desc: Aahhh... This is heaven! Hm? Commander, wanna join me? Oh, the bath just felt so good I couldn't help but moan! There's no funny business going on!
name: Steam Dream

desc: Omaha-class light cruiser – Memphis, Hull Number CL-13.
name: Memphis

desc: Oh my, do I really look so unusual in this outfit? I want to be able to enjoy my day off as well, you know? Hehe, don't you think it feels nice to just sit back and take in the ocean breeze?
name: Casual Vacation

desc: We have to work hard if we want to play hard, isn't that right, Commander? Are you ready for our happy Halloween?
name: Mystical Night

desc: Oh, what a wonderful breeze. Maybe the windows ought always to be open during class... Commander? What are you standing around for? There's a vacant seat right here for you.
name: A Breath of Fresh Air

desc: Omaha-class light cruiser— Concord, hull number CL-10.
name: Concord

desc: Apple candy, Taiyaki, and fried noodles~ The Sakura Empire’s Temple Fair really is something~ Hehe Commander, do you also want to take a bite of my apple candy? Here you go~
name: Red Apple Candy

desc: Merry Sweetsmas, Commander! Today, I get to eat as many sweets as I want without anyone saying things about it~♪ Hmm, I already eat this much every day? I guess so~
name: Sweet☆Christmas

desc: Brooklyn-class light cruiser – Helena (CL-50)
name: Lena

desc: Cleveland-class light cruiser – Cleveland (CL-55)
name: Clevelad

desc: Atlanta-class light cruiser – San Diego (CL-53)
name: Li'l Sandy

desc: Atlanta-class light cruiser – San Juan, Hull Number CL-54.
name: San Juan

desc: All right, dress looking good. Now just to check my makeup... Need to be thorough, so I don't embarrass myself in front of– What?! C-Commander?!
name: The Longing Princess

desc: Cleveland-class light cruiser – Birmingham, Hull Number CL-62.
name: Birmingham

desc: Good morning, Commander. Unfortunately, this bicycle only seats one person, but I could dismount and lead it along as we walk together.
name: Rider of Red

desc: Happy Lunar New Year, Commander. I'm trying out Dragon Empery fashion for a change, though this dress will some getting used to. Hey, uh, do you want to join me under the umbrella? For cover against the snowfall, I mean.
name: Fruitful Snow of an Auspicious Year

desc: The wind and the waves are great today. You wanna try windsurfing after this, Commander? It's a lot of fun and I can teach you the... Hang on, there's a good wind coming and I've got to catch it!
name: To Where the Wind Blows

desc: Step back, Commander. I hear something up ahead... As your adjutant maid, I will protect you against interference from uninvited guests.
name: Briar Maid

desc: Light cruiser Cleveland, right here! I'm new to this whole idol biz, but I'll go with the flow and give it my all! Oh, and I'm counting on your support, Commander!
name: Cleveland μ

desc: Cleveland-class light cruiser – Biloxi, Hull Number CL-80.
name: Biloxi

desc: We're celebrating an overseas holiday, hence my not-so-casual outfit today. Heheh, what do you think? Looking slick?
name: Dapper Gangstress

desc: "Hehe... Now that you've finally fallen into my hands, why don't we take the day to get to know each other real well, Commander?" Oh my, was my acting a bit too realistic~?
name: Empress in the Silk Seat

desc: I heard that this place is famous for its festivals with beautiful fireworks, so I made sure to come dressed for the occasion... What do you think? ...I'm even more beautiful? Well, I couldn't let the fireworks be the only things leaving an impression upo
name: Night Sky's Brilliant Blue Blossoms

desc: The cast is all here. So, what do we rehearse first? The part where we elope and live happily ever after? Hahahah!
name: Romeo or Juliet?

desc: Atlanta-class light cruiser – Reno, Hull Number CL-96.
name: Reno

desc: This really is a huge clash of all the biggest names from all the factions. It's one exciting match after another! I gotta cheer my hardest too. Eagle Union, go get 'em!
name: Biggest Little Cheerleader

desc: "Superhero spin-off! The superhero who saved the world is enjoying a hard-earned vacation on the afternoon beach with the sidekick!" ... Hehe, Commander, a tagline like that sounds pretty cool, doesn't it?
name: Summer Spin-off

desc: Come on in, Commander! Don't you recognize me? I'm Reno Bunnino – cutesy bunny girl by day, villain-vanquishing superhero by night! Pretty neat concept, am I right?
name: Reno Bunnino

desc: Check this out, Commander! Hehehe, I added a little firework launcher to my superhero gadgets. Cool, huh? ...Your interest lies more in my new look? But... the firework...
name: Spring's Inspiration

desc: Omaha-class light cruiser – Marblehead, Hull Number CL-12.
name: Marblehead

desc: After trying out a whole bunch of activities, I settled on joinin' the boxing club in the end. Everyone wants to exercise now and then, right? Come along, Commander, and we'll have a fun workout together~
name: Boxing Girl!

desc: Whoa! Talk about a stunning view! You like, totally know all the best spots in the city, Commander~ Hehe, okay, so... Merry Christmas!
name: Charmer in the Snowy Reflection

desc: The annual moon gazing festival's upon us again~ Ah, so you know a thing or two about the Mid-Autumn Festival, Commander? Then I reckon you know what we're doing tonight, right~? ♡
name: Moongazing on the 29½th

desc: Phew... Should be in the clear now. Oh, hey, Commander. Whatcha doing here? Waiting for a cutie to show up or something? Surely it can't be a coincidence... right?
name: Not-So-Serendipitous Rain

desc: Brooklyn-class light cruiser – Boise, Hull Number CL-47.
name: Boise

desc: Huff... Puff... Deep breaths... I'll never get used to wearing this outfit in front of others... I think...
name: Sheepish Sapphire

desc: Um, I decided to try on a costume, since it's Halloween and all... Do you think I got that witchy look down...?
name: Castle Tales

desc: Huff... Puff... These Dragon Empery clothes look good on me? It's rather revealing and breezy, and makes me feel self-conscious... but if you like it, I suppose it's fine...
name: Jade Mermaid

desc: Commander, did I get ketchup on you? Sorry... Huff, puff... Th-this is the first time I'm letting you see me in a maid outfit, so I'm a little nervous...
name: Flawed but Delectable

desc: Cleveland-class light cruiser – Houston II, Hull Number CL-81.
name: Houston II

desc: Thank you for waiting! Houston is here and ready to serve! Mm... I've never worn a costume like this. It's kind of embarrassing... And is it just me, or is it a size or two too small?
name: Ready to Serve!

desc: I'm Cyanidin light cruiser, Boise... Huff, puff... Umm, does this outfit get your attention better? Good...
name: Boise μ

desc: Fargo-class light cruiser – Fargo, Hull Number CL-106.
name: Fargo

desc: Milk the cows? Okay, I'll give it my best shot. Firsthand experience helps me better emulate emotions, after all... Although, isn't it way too hot outside for milking?
name: Dairy in the Dreary Sun

desc: Cleveland-class light cruiser – Santa Fe, Hull Number CL-60.
name: Santa Fe

desc: Huh? You're already in bed, Commander? Come on, it's time for late-night gossip! Nyahaha! Let me slip into bed with you so we can chat the night away!
name: The Rumor Mill Never Sleeps

desc: Cleveland-class light cruiser – Pasadena, Hull Number CL-65.
name: Pasadena

desc: Surprise! How do you like my special showdown outfit? I got it specifically for the game we're gonna play! Ahaha♪ Let the Meow-Meow Celebration Service begin!
name: Surprising Game

desc: Pensacola-class Heavy Cruiser – Pensacola, Hull Number CA-24!
name: Pensacola

desc: Pensacola-class Heavy Cruiser – Salt Lake City, Hull Number CA-25!
name: Salt Lake City

desc: Northampton-class Heavy Cruiser – Northampton, Hull Number CA-26!
name: Northampton

desc: Northampton-class Heavy Cruiser – Chicago, Hull Number CA-29!
name: Chicago

desc: Northampton-class Heavy Cruiser – Houston, Hull Number CA-30!
name: Houston

desc: Portland-class Heavy Cruiser – Portland, Hull Number CA-33!
name: Portland

desc: Commander, look, look! This is my handmade Indy plushie! Isn't it utterly adorable?! It's the magnum opus of my work in the Arts & Crafts Club!
name: At School With Indy!

desc: Nice to meet you, I'm Indianaportland! ... Hm? Who's Indy? She's my precious little sister, and my most beloved...
name: Portland (Retrofit)

desc: Portland-class Heavy Cruiser – Indianapolis, Hull Number CA-35!
name: Indianapolis

desc: School life... It's nice as long as you and my sister are here... I think...
name: At School With My Sister...

desc: Oh. Good evening, Commander. Do you want some steak? It goes great with wine.
name: The Light of Circle City

desc: New Orleans-class heavy cruiser – Astoria, hull number CA-34.
name: Astoria

desc: Huh? Commander? ... Wait, why are you staring at me like I'm some exotic animal? C-cute? Ehehe... Th-thanks...
name: Pure "Gurl?"

desc: Heyyo! You ready for this, Commander? It's carnival day! You can have all the drinks you want, it's on the house!
name: Black Bunny Carnival

desc: New Orleans-class heavy cruiser – Quincy, hull number CA-39.
name: Quincy

desc: Everyone's so cheerful and energetic... Commander, um, if you're tired, want to rest here with me?
name: Sizzling Summer, Brisk Breeze

desc: New Orleans-class heavy cruiser – Vincennes, hull number CA-44.
name: Vincennes

desc: Zzz... sho comfy... Huh? Commyander...?
name: Sweet Dreams

desc: Off to school we go~ Being punctual makes me a good girl~
name: Leisurely ABC's

desc:
Wichita-class heavy cruiser – Wichita, Hull Number CA-45! 
<color=#fad545>Unlock build after receiving</color>
name: Wichita

desc: It's about time you showed up, Commander. Now, show me some spirit! As my lieutenant, don't do anything slovenly that would incur the mockery of others! Very well, let's move out!
name: The General's Banquet

desc: Tonight I am not a renowned naval general, I am a feared commander of witches! And you... Yes, you're not my lieutenant, you are my arcane familiar!
name: Domineering Witchita

desc: Lock on... Fire!
name: New Orleans

desc: To your prestige, and to your continued victories, Commander. Hehe, I do find myself in the mood for rum tonight. Care to keep me company for a while?
name: Evening Agricole

desc: New Orleans class Heavy Cruiser— Minneapolis, hull number CA-36.
name: Minneapolis

desc: Textbooks, pencils and erasers... hey, must students always pay attention in class... Commander? Can you arrange for us to get more extracurricular activities?
name: Wild Huntress Schoolgirl

desc: Oh crap! Move outta the way, Commander! Come on, man, look out next time! You'd have gotten hurt if I'd slammed into you!
name: eXtreme Games

desc: Merry Christmas, Commander! Right now, I'm Santa Claus! And this guy over here is my partner in delivering presents! Right, this is a present for you. C'mon, go ahead and take it!
name: Holy Night Ride

desc: Commander, why's that Quincy so happy to see me in this outfit? It's hard to move around in, and there's all this stuff flapping around that makes it hard to hunt. What do you think of this outfit?
name: Trapper White

desc: New Orleans-class heavy cruiser – San Francisco, Hull Number CA-38.
name: San Francisco

desc: Music! Lights! Refreshments! We're all set! Welcome to San Francisco's party! Come and enjoy yourself!
name: Funny Bunny!

desc: Good evening, Puddin'! Welcome to my pole dancing show! You aren't going home tonight 'til you're head over heels for me♪
name: It's Showtime!

desc: Baltimore-class heavy cruiser – Baltimore, Hull Number CA-68.
name: Baltimore

desc: Oh, you wanna observe my club activities, Commander? Ahah, as you can tell, it's just a sports club with the goal of making you sweat. Nothing suspicious about that, is there...?
name: After-School Ace

desc: Heya, you here to watch the game? Heh, heavy cruiser Baltimore, the passerby solver of troubles, here to play it cool!
name: Black Ace

desc: Damn, that Bremerton... What did she make me wear this time... Even though I was the one to ask her for advice... Um... Ugh... This doesn't look too weird, right...?
name: Evening Breeze Minuet

desc: "Our meeting here must have been preordained by fate. Hail to you. I am a passing traveler by the name of Baltimore." ...Hahah, it's nothing. Just some lines I came up with to match my traditional getup. Did they do the trick, Commander?
name: Ace's Travel Journal

desc: Heya, Commander. You here to spectate the race? Strap in, 'cause it's gonna be wild... My getup? They asked me to help out the grid girls, so yeah. Just hope I'll do a good job of building hype for the race.
name: Finish Line Flagbearer

desc: The scenery is even prettier on days like today... Huh? What do I mean? I mean our w-wedding, obviously... Ugh, quit teasing me already!
name: When the Breeze Blows

desc: Baltimore-class heavy cruiser – Bremerton, Hull Number CA-130.
name: Bremerton

desc: *pant*... *pant*... Man, it's so sunny today... Commander, or should I say, "Coach," could ya lend me your parasol? I'm starting to feel my brains melting away...
name: Scorching-Hot Training

desc: "Stop right there, evildoers! You've managed to evade justice all this time, but the hour of judgment is finally upon you!" ...Hmm, making the perfect flashy debut is pretty tough, isn't it?
name: Kung Fu Cruiser

desc: I reckon we've done enough shopping for the moment. Let's stop and chill here for a bit, then have another look around~♪
name: Day-Off Date

desc: Welcome to Bremerton's counseling corner! Actually, I came up with this idea just for you, since you're always working so hard... Tadaaah~! I've prepared us some matching sleepwear~♪
name: Relaxation Consultation

desc: Hold still, Commander! You gotta relax in this position or else I can't do my thing. Take it easy and let me handle them weary bones. Alright, from your hands to your arms, then to your neck and shoulders, time to press down!
name: Pillowed Counseling

desc: Three, two, one, go! Did you get a pic of me tossing the bouquet, Commander? Ahahah! I'm postin' this to Juustagram later, so you should do the same! It'll be like... retaking our pledge of love♪
name: Joyride of Love

desc: The name's Baltimore, Eagle Union heavy cruiser. Whoops, right, I'm not just a soldier anymore, but an idol as well. I agreed to do it, and I'm gonna do it as best I can. We'll be counting on your support, Commander.
name: Baltimore μ

desc: Oregon City-class heavy cruiser – Northampton II, Hull Number CA-125.
name: Northampton II

desc: Whew. How many laps have I done since my last break...? Oh. Commander, are you here to hone your swimming skills too?
name: Swimming Star

desc: Phew... This getup does help me get into the festival mood. It looks nice, and it's supremely comfortable, but I can't shake this embarrassment... Huh? Commander? When did you get here?
name: Comfy Crane Amidst the Clouds

desc: Northampton-class heavy cruiser – Louisville, Hull Number CA-28.
name: Louisville

desc: Commander, here's your order of... Umm, it's written on the ticket, right... Huh? Where did I put that thing? Oh no, I'm in real trouble if I mess up the Commander's order...
name: An Order of Dreams

desc: Baltimore-class heavy cruiser – Pittsburgh, Hull Number CA-72.
name: Pittsburgh

desc: Welcome to the saloon, Commander. Be it drinking juice, or playing games of chance, I'm happy to join you. And I offer more special services, too...
name: The Bartender's Gambit

desc: Heavy cruiser – Anchorage.
name: Little Anchorage

desc: Lexington-class battlecruiser – Constellation, Hull Number CC-2.
name: Constellation

desc: Welcome, Commander. If you want me to take your order, please subscribe for one month to my horoscope reading on Juustagram... Heehee, I'm joking. If you have any questions, I will gladly answer.
name: Galaxy's Finest

desc: Nevada-class battleship – Nevada, Hull Number BB-36!
name: Nevada

desc: Howdy, young'un! Aren't you tired from goin' around greetin' fancy people? Come over here and relax with me and some good food.
name: A Magnificent Banquet

desc: Heh, with this, I won't be outperformed by those fancy greenhorn battleships. Young'un, from now on, just leave everything to Nevada here!
name: Nevada (Retrofit)

desc: Nevada-class battleship – Oklahoma, Hull Number BB-37!
name: Oklahoma

desc: Howdy, Commander! Oh, this outfit? I've been super into this kind of stuff lately! I even added some jack-o-lanterns for extra ambiance and had some Manjuus help out. So what's the verdict? Pretty cool, isn't it?
name: Piratey Transformation!

desc: Thanks a ton, Commander. With my new strength, do you think I've managed to catch up to my sister a little? Ehehe, for your sake, I'll work even harder!
name: Oklahoma (Retrofit)

desc: Pennsylvania-class battleship – Pennsylvania, Hull Number BB-38!
name: Pennsylvania

desc: Halt! Who are you?! ...Oh, it's you, Commander. I briefly mistook you for a spy there. Why are you here? To spectate? Or, God forbid, to gather intel on my army?
name: The Keystone General

desc: Pennsylvania-class Battleship – Arizona, Hull Number BB-39!
name: Arizona

desc: I heard these clothes are from the Dragon Empery, but they're a bit... Umm, it's not that I dislike them, but the thought of you seeing me in them is rather embarrassing... B-but it's not like I'm going to start crying...
name: Enchantress from Afar

desc: Tennessee-class battleship – Tennessee, Hull Number BB-43!
name: Tennessee

desc: Tennessee-class battleship – California, Hull Number BB-44!
name: California

desc: Colorado class battleship— Colorado, hull number BB-45
name: Colorado

desc: Hmm-hum-hum... So very cute~♪ ...Commander? Um, about that... Please do me a favor and forget you heard anything.
name: Traveling Melody

desc: You'd rather stay here and watch the sunset with me than bathe with the rest in the sea? You sure you wanna spend your beach day that way? Err, well... I'm fine with it if you are.
name: Sunset Cavatina

desc: You called, and I returned stronger, fiercer, and more complete. Now I await your orders. On my name as a Big Seven, I swear to decimate anyone who stands in your way.
name: Colorado (Retrofit)

desc: Colorado class battleship— Maryland, hull number BB-46
name: Maryland

desc: Oh, hey, Commander – you here for a break, too? Relax, I won't rat you out to anyone else. Just kick back and enjoy the fireworks.
name: Red-Hot Drummer

desc: My retrofit is capital-D done! Hah, I generally know what's changed – the details, I'll discover in live battles! That alright with you?
name: Maryland (Retrofit)

desc: Colorado class battleship— West Virginia, hull number BB-48.
name: West Virginia

desc: Colorado, Maryland, you two ready to rock? Keep your cool! Commander, and everyone in the audience, get ready for the Big Seven's big performance!
name: Scenic Rhapsody

desc: West Virginia, completing retrofit. Back when I joined the fleet, I said I'd show you my strength – now, after you've made me this much stronger, I feel humbled. Once more, Commander, my strength is yours.
name: West Virginia (Retrofit)

desc: North Carolina class battleship, North Carolina. Hull Number BB-55.
name: North Carolina

desc: Commander? Oh, umm, this is just, err, equipment changing practice... Also, I recall you saying you like bunny girls. You still do, right?
name: The Heart's Desire

desc: North Carolina class battleship, Washington. Hull Number BB-56.
name: Washington

desc: Sup, Commander? ...Looking good? I don't think this outfit's anything special... You better not be trying to cozy up to me, or I'll knock your teeth out!
name: Jubilant Smile

desc: Yo, Commander. Called for a nurse, didn'tcha? ...You didn't? Bullcrap, you totally did! Listen up, you're a patient, so act like it – drop your damn work and let me examine you.
name: Making the Rounds

desc: South Dakota-class battleship – South Dakota, Hull Number BB-57!
name: South Dakota

desc: Massachusetts suggested I learn something useful that's unrelated to combat, so I started playing the piano... It seemed impossible at first, but after actually trying it, I've developed a pretty good feel for it.
name: Solo Concert

desc: South Dakota-class battleship – Indiana, Hull Number BB-58.
name: Indiana

desc: Oh, look who's here. What am I doing here? Well, I figured through the roof was the fastest way in, so I punched a hole through the ceiling. The bandits are all down for the count, so let me take it from here.
name: High Noon Arrest

desc: Iowa-class battleship – New Jersey, Hull Number BB-62.
name: New Jersey

desc: One, two, jump! Woah, think I nailed it this time~♪ So, how many points would you give me for that? Naturally, a perfect 100, right? Don'tcha just love it when things go smoothly?
name: Exhilarating Steps!

desc: Sooo hot... Are you alright, honey? You're not heat-exhausted, are you? I'll share my drink with you if you're thirsty, but in return, I'll need you to put my sunscreen on for me. Heheh, that's just what you like to do, right, honey~?
name: Midsummer Leisure

desc: Phew... It was really hard to cinch the ending, but I can handle anything! So, honey, did you like it? Hellooo, honey? Aww, are you so mesmerized that you can't speak? Hahaha!
name: Dancing in the Moonlight

desc: There you are, honey! I've got a super-special, super-speedy gift for you before the race! Get over here, aaand... Mwah!
name: Black Blur Prelude

desc: The indomitable Black Dragon... I mean, the adorable New Jersey makes her bridal appearance! Hehe~ Stunned, arent'cha? Of course you are, honey~♪ How wouldn't you be?
name: Snow-White Ceremony

desc: South Dakota-class battleship – Massachusetts, Hull Number BB-59.
name: Massachusetts

desc: Hey... Is this outfit that strange to you? Thought it looks just like what my sister's wearing... so what are you staring at? I don't get you at all...
name: Dressed to Impress

desc: South Dakota-class battleship – Alabama, Hull Number BB-60.
name: Alabama

desc: Hrmm... Lotta orders to work through... Runnin' a Dragon Empery restaurant ain't easy. Hmm? You here for some chow too, Commander? Then how about... I put you ahead in line?
name: Untarnished Silver, Silken Gold

desc: Mmh... I reckon it'll be more excitin' if I show more skin... Commander? Great timing. Could you help me press the shutter?
name: Through Your Lens, My Everything

desc: Long Island-class escort carrier – Long Island, Hull Number CVE-1!
name: Long Island

desc: Everyone's favorite and talked-about Long Island, actually has another hidden secret...
name: Long Island - Indoor Slacker

desc: "Tune in everyone, Gamer Girl L.I. is about to begin her spooky Halloween special stream~" ...Well, that should do it for my channel intro... Hmm, wonder how many viewers I'll get~
name: Long Island's Spooky Stream

desc: Ring-ring-ring... Hi, this is Long Island at the information desk speaking. What'd you say? Alright, sure. Don't worry, I'll relay aaall your feedback to the Commander. I'm going to hang up now. Buh-bye!
name: Ghostly Receptionist

desc: Commander~ I am Long Island~ I've changed? Ghosts don't cha... Huh? I seemed to have become a little more alive!
name: Long Island (Retrofit)

desc: Bogue-class escort carrier — Bogue, Hull Number CVE-9!
name: Bogue

desc: Commander, there's no need to be so afraid. There are only two things my balls hit-- Enemies, and victory! Ah, sometimes they do hit the windows too, ahaha...
name: Bogue (Retrofit)

desc: Casablanca-class escort carrier – Casablanca, Hull Number CVE-55.
name: Casablanca

desc: Phew... Can't train hard if you don't stay hydrated! Oh, Commander, good day! Did you come to watch us practice?
name: Cheer Squad on Break

desc: Langley-class aicraft carrier ー Langley, Hull Number CV-1!
name: Langley

desc: Listen carefully or I'll step on you!
name: Langley (Retrofit)

desc: Lexington-class aircraft carrier ー Lexington, Hull Number CV-2!
name: Lexington

desc: Hehe… sometimes you can completely change the way people see you with just a simple change in attire. Don't you agree, Commander~? Don’t worry, I'm still your Lexington~
name: The Beauty of Spring

desc: Lexington-class aircraft carrier ー Saratoga, Hull Number CV-3!
name: Saratoga

desc: Even if we don't get to relax on holiday, it's always good to have a swimsuit! Ok, let's go! Are you ready to swim?
name: Seven Seas of Rest

desc: Hey everyone~! This time, Sister Sara has brought you fashion from a faraway land! Commander, what do you think of it?
name: Hibiscus-scented Idol

desc: HAI DOMO~! I’m the virtual idol, Saratoga! Well, Commander, what do you think? I asked Kizuna AI to make this dress specifically for me, modeled after her outfit!
name: Virtual Idol

desc: Friends of the blue sea and sky, your guardian angel and idol Sara has arrived! Ehehe~ Commander, join me in protecting the beauty of the blue seas!
name: Superstar of the Blue Seas

desc: Merry Christmas! Here comes Christmas Sara, shining like a star in the silent night! Hehehe, how's that for a holiday greeting? So, have you decided where we're gonna spend our Christmas Eve yet?
name: Silent Night Songstress

desc: Tadaaah! Happy Lunar New Year, Commander! How do you like this fresh new spring look that Sara's rocking? Hope you haven't forgotten our promise to check out the port's spring festival together~ Ready, then? Let's go!
name: Spring's Opening Act!

desc: Tada! Welcome to Sister Sara's special picnic! Look at all the delicious food I brought~ See, Commander, I told you it wasn't just another prank~♪
name: The Sweetest Picnic!

desc: You ready, Commander? ...Come on, don't give me a "just one moment" right before the finish line~ It's time to imprint my adorable dress into your memory forever~♡
name: Ring the Bell of Joy

desc: Sister Sara is leaving her nest and going in a new direction! I'm now making my official debut as Saratoga: The Little Witch Idol! I'm leaving my PR to you, Commander~
name: Saratoga (Retrofit)

desc: Ranger-class aircraft carrier ー Ranger, Hull Number CV-4!
name: Ranger

desc: I didn't realize I could still become more powerful! I'll work harder from here on out to teach everyone how to fight!
name: Ranger (Retrofit)

desc: Yorktown-class aircraft carrier ー Yorktown, Hull Number CV-5!
name: Yorktown

desc: Hey, Commander, are you lost? How about a drink? ... Huh? Drunk? Me? Oh, Commander, you're such a card. This is just grape juice... isn't it?
name: Evening I Can't Remember

desc: Across seven steps, in a tower atop a hill, you'll find the king's resting place... Hehe. Will you come with me to Utopia, Commander? I'm joking, of course, but I am very glad we could make this journey together.
name: Saintly Wings

desc: This wedding dress, brimming with light, flutters like a feather in the wind... I'm sure that I'm still in a long, deep, slumber... That's right, Commander. The two of us are surely sharing a blissful dream together, heehee.
name: Towards Tomorrow's Brilliant Breeze

desc: Yorktown-class aircraft carrier ー Enterprise, Hull Number CV-6!
name: Enterprise

desc: Merry Christmas, Commander! I shall be Santa Claus tonight, so make sure to hang up your stockings on the fireplace before going to sleep!
name: Reindeer Master

desc: So this is the traditional attire of the Dragon Empery? Hmm... it fits quite well. Oh? Custom-made bow and arrows… Interesting, let's see how far these arrows can fly.
name: Blooming Peony

desc: Happy Anniversary! Commander, celebrate to your heart's content today! I'll be praying for our continued victories!
name: Anniversary Ride

desc: There is no doubt in my mind that I was born to fight. For the azure lanes of liberty, Enterprise, engaging!
name: Soaring Wings of Freedom

desc: My ballgown? I don't normally get to wear clothes like these, so it took me a while to change. Ah, let's hurry to the venue. We shouldn't keep everyone else waiting.
name: Heroic Finery

desc: Commander, did you come to watch the race? You know... I'd rather be down there competing than standing around over here. That feeling of being able to seize the wind... Don't you think that racing and sailing share the same essence?
name: Wind Catcher

desc: It feels odd taking an extended leave just to go on vacation... but I guess you need breaks to stay on top of your game. With that in mind, let's make every minute count, Commander!
name: Bon Voyage

desc: How, how does it look? Do I look a bit strange... no, of course I like it. I'd say every girl dreams about this day, just that...
name: Starlight Oath

desc: Yorktown-class aircraft carrier ー Hornet, Hull Number CV-8!
name: Hornet

desc: Congratulations! You did it, Commander! Now let's pop the champagne and celebrate! It's party time!
name: Bubbly Anniversary!

desc: Mmmmm... Nothing beats pizza straight outta the oven! Here, Commander, wanna give it a try? We're gonna have to recommend this to Enty next time!
name: Freshly-Baked Bonding!

desc: Let's keep it up, everyone! One more point, and we can make a comeback!!! ...Hah... *gulp gulp*... Whew~! Thanks a billion for the drink, Commander! And thanks for watching over us as well!
name: Cheering Justice!

desc: Wasp-class aircraft carrier, Wasp. Hull Number CV-7.
name: Wasp

desc: Essex-class aircraft carrier – Essex, Hull Number CV-9.
name: Essex

desc: I'm not trying to go anywhere in particular; I just want to enjoy the scenery along the way. Commander, let's go experience the thrills of the road together.
name: A Trip Down Route 66

desc: Commander?! Ah, um, no, I'm not drunk! ...I, uh, just had a bit too much to drink... just a bit! Please don't tell the others though!
name: Craft Fairytail

desc: The Dragon Empery's attire and tools of calligraphy... I see, just wearing this outfit makes me feel more scholarly and artistic! I shall put forth my best effort to prepare for the port's Spring Festival!
name: Brush and Ink

desc: My eagle has gone missing... Just as Enterprise said, there's something strange going on in this port–– Wait, I definitely smell a case in the making! Commander, let's get to the bottom of this together!
name: Detective Essex

desc: "Anchors aweigh! Arr, pirate aircraft carrier Essex be ready for battle! Nothing in the seven seas will escape my grasp!" Hic... Hehehe... I wanna be a piraaate...
name: Crossbones Especial

desc: Cooldown lap completed! Did you see me on the racetrack, Commander? Heehee. Thanks for everything, from setting up the race to assigning racers and supporters!
name: The Gale of Course 88

desc: Don't worry, Commander. I'm making sure your ride is squeaky clean before the race! Check it out – I bet your car is the most dazzling one on the track now.
name: Start Line Splash

desc: Essex's retrofitting has finished! Now Enterprise will be– No, YOU will be 120% satisfied with me, Commander! Anyway, I, Essex-class aircraft carrier Essex, am at your command!
name: Essex (Retrofit)

desc: Essex-class aircraft carrier – Yorktown II, Hull Number CV-10.
name: Yorktown II

desc: How does this look? ...Ah, it's nothing to worry about. Do you think I should adjust the string a bit...? Hmm... Eek!!! I'm so sorry, Commander... A-are you alright...?
name: Bright-Sky Mermaid

desc: I just had a little aperitif... How am I already so drunk? C-Commander, wait a second. I'll make you a cocktaaail... Where'd I put that shaker?
name: An Evening's Companionship

desc: Welcome to my... no, YOUR own bar, Commander. Relax a little and enjoy exclusive service courtesy of yours truly. Umm... Okay, what now?
name: An Evening's Companionship

desc: Essex-class aircraft carrier – Intrepid, Hull Number CV-11.
name: Intrepid

desc: There's been a lot of inter-port meets recently... But before I can join a team with my other Eagle Union colleagues, I've got to up my game first! So, Commander, mind training with me?
name: One Intrepid Pitch

desc: Essex-class aircraft carrier – Hornet II, Hull Number CV-12.
name: Hornet II

desc: The title of fastest in the port is miiiine, hahaha! Commandeer, did you see how badass I was just now? There's a whole lot more I'd like to show you, but it'll hafta wait 'til the next race... Well, I'll let you ride with me later, so look forward to it~♪
name: Racing Across the Waves!

desc: Essex-class aircraft carrier – Franklin, Hull Number CV-13.
name: Franklin

desc: Phew... Sorry I took so long, Commander. I'll be your examiner today. Ah, you're wondering how good I am as a nurse? Heehee. Let's just say you'll find out by... touch♡
name: Heart-Throbbing Records

desc: Essex-class aircraft carrier – Ticonderoga, Hull Number CV-14.
name: Ticonderoga

desc: It's showtime! The stage is all set for the performance! Let's enjoy this perfect evening together, Commander~!
name: Show Stopper!

desc: Hi! Thoughts on my swimsuit, Commander? Does it suit your tastes? Heheh, thanks! If you had to leave a comment, what would you say? ...Where did you learn how to tease people so well?
name: Sunshine Princess

desc: Essex-class aircraft carrier – Lexington II, Hull Number CV-16.
name: Lexington II

desc: I guess dressing up as maids is all the rage at port these days. It piqued my interest, so I just had to try it! Together, let's make this place as clean and relaxing as it can be.
name: The Fluffiest of Maids

desc: Essex-class aircraft carrier – Bunker Hill, Hull Number CV-17.
name: Bunker Hill

desc: Mission complete. Next up, a new recommendation from Long Island... Oh, Commander? Come make yourself comfortable.
name: Mission Relaxation

desc: Independence-class light aircraft carrier – Independence, Hull Number CVL-22.
name: Independence

desc: So this is my new school, huh? Hmm... gotta put my stuff down first before checking in with the teacher.
name: Transfer Student From Afar

desc: Hmm... Isn't this one a bit too garish? Mm... What if we pair it with a necklace or some sort of purse? ...Commander, your thoughts? C'mon, don't just stare at me, give me something to work with here...
name: The Independent Line

desc: Whew... A bit of stretching helps keep the body flexible. Hm? I'm in loungewear, what about it? I'd appreciate it if you wouldn't stare too much, though...
name: Liberty and Leisure

desc: Just need to feed it a coin, then operate the crane with the joystick... Oh! I got one! That was easier than I expected.
name: The Tailwind of Opportunity

desc: Light carrier Independence reporting. Retrofitting complete. I'm ready to take on harder, more vital missions. Leave anything like that to me.
name: Independence (Retrofit)

desc: Independence-class light aircraft carrier – Princeton (CVL-23.)
name: Princeton

desc: Commander, are you also here to swim? ...Ah, this here? I brought it with me to the ocean to get some practice in.
name: Seaside Training

desc: You're finally here? ...Ah, well, I only just got here as well, so don't worry about it. Anyway, shall we get going?
name: Lolipop Paradise

desc: I'm done changing... Is this supposed to be a "reindeer" costume? It feels a bit too risqué... Oh, Commander, since you're already here, come get your Christmas present.
name: Gift-Wrapped Reindeer

desc: Independence-class light aircraft carrier – Cowpens, Hull Number CVL-25.
name: Cowpens

desc: Are you ready, Commander? You're about to get the most soothing infusion of nutrients in your life. Step one is to relax...
name: Milky Ministrations

desc: Independence-class light aircraft carrier – Langley II, Hull Number CVL-27.
name: Langley II

desc: Pheeew... Being able to kick back and relax on such a sunny day is just the best! Oh, Commander! If you'd like to come chill with me, I have watermelon and cold drinks!
name: On-the-Clock Vacation

desc: Independence-class light aircraft carrier – Bataan, Hull Number CVL-29.
name: Bataan

desc: Yaaaaawn... Huh!? Commander!? You scared me... I was just going to lie down and... Um, yes, with little Hellcat here... Goodnight...
name: Comfy Cotton Jammies

desc: Independence-class light aircraft carrier – San Jacinto, Hull Number CVL-30.
name: San Jacinto

desc: Would you like me to recommend a drink? Hmm... You're quite the drinker, Commander~ Let's see if you can handle my favorite♪ Heehee!
name: Flavor of the Day

desc: Essex-class aircraft carrier – Shangri-La, Hull Number CV-38.
name: Shangri-La

desc: Commander, welcome to my "Utopia." Here, you can find my prized collection. Now, where should we start our detailed tour?
name: Utopia's Collector

desc: This specimen looks to be fairly ancient... You could watch from behind me, or you could join me for an up-close examination; we can enjoy our time here however you wish.
name: Explorer of the Lost World

desc: Yorktown-class aircraft carrier – Enterprise, Hull Number CV-6.
name: Little Enterprise

desc: Gato-class submarine - Dace (SS-247)
name: Dace

desc: Gato-class submarine – Albacore, Hull Number SS-218.
name: Albacore

desc: Oopsie! I totally just dropped something by mistake~! I'd better pick it up quick! Hmm? Saw something you shouldn't have, Commander? Hehehe~ That makes you my partner in crime now!
name: Beneath the Black Dress

desc: Surpriiiise! I was in the box all along! ...Did I really freak you out that much? Heehee~ Here, have this voucher as an apology. Come see me later to use it~♪
name: A Catty Surprise!

desc: Gato-class submarine – Cavalla, Hull Number SS-244.
name: Cavalla

desc: You're late, Commander! ... What's all this? Heheh, it's loot I got from the stop n' rob's bargain bin! Here, have some bread!
name: Convenience Store Raid!

desc: Look at all the cute balloons and flowers, and the delicious food as well! Hehe! Parties are the best!
name: Colorful Ceremony

desc: Gato-class submarine – Bluegill, Hull Number SS-242.
name: Bluegill

desc: Look out for Bluegill's ultra-reliable defense, Intrepid! Hehehe, Commander, stay here and see the results of Bluegill's special training!
name: Up-And-Coming Infielder

desc: Lights! Camera! Albacore! Ahaha, don't worry about it, I'm just getting fired up over here! Oh, did you come up with a better idea? Tell me, tell me~
name: Albacore μ

desc: Balao-class submarine – Archerfish, Hull Number SS-311.
name: Archerfish

desc: You're our lucky guest today, Commander~ You get a taste of my secret concoction... Excuse me, I meant to say "cocktail!" Relax, it won't do anything weird to you~ Probably. Ahaha~
name: Coquettish Bunny

desc: Would you look at that – we're sat next to each other in class. Looking forward to doing some "extracurricular activities" with you this term. Hehehe~
name: The Devil Next Door

desc: Narwhal-class submarine-Nautilus, Hull number SS-168.
name: Nautilus

desc: Phew~ Standing for a long time really wears you out... Hwah?! Commander, when'd you get there? Um, if you'd like, would you like to come exercise with me?
name: Afternoon Stretches

desc: Commander~ Ehehe, can I introduce you to some of my new friends? Here's Miss Tropical Fish, and Mister Manta Ray... Oh, and Mister Dolphin too! Oh, umm, this friend here can be a bit mischievous at times, and often causes quite a bit of trouble...
name: Shining Blossom in the Deep Blue

desc: Gato-class submarine – Flasher, Hull Number SS-249.
name: Flasher

desc: W-welcome, Commander... I-I as the manager will be serving you today, so l-let's hear your order... *sniffle*... I'm so tense it's making me cry...
name: Tearjerking Service

desc: Gato-class submarine – Herring, Hull Number SS-233.
name: Herring

desc: Well, well. I was wondering who owns this polite little horsy – surprise, it's you! How about you trade me 'em for a blown kiss? And if you catch up with me, you can have the rest of me for free♪ Mwah♡
name: The Town With No Shade

desc: Repair ship ー Vestal, Hull Number AR-4!
name: Vestal

desc: Listen, everyone~! Playing by the beach is fun, but please keep safety in mind! If you begin to feel ill, come see me~!
name: Revigorating Hestia

desc: Alaska-class large cruiser – Guam, Hull Number CB-2.
name: Guam

desc: Bunny idol, on the stage♪ Commander! You're in for a banger performance, so just forget about everything else and keep your eyes on me!
name: Stage-Setting Charmer

desc: Kunoichi Guam, arriving in style! Brought to you live, this episode features a ninja with zero ninjutsu knowledge trying to enter the Commander's room to– Aaahhhh! Owch... This infiltration mechanism's so hard to use... No, wait, Commander, don't stop the camera! Little accidents are just part of a variety show♪
name: The Kunoichi's Dangerous Variety Show

desc: Welcome. Would you like to try a Teriyaki Twister? I could go for a nap right now inside a nice, warm tortilla... Probably.
name: Sleepy Teriyaki Twister

desc: Zzzzz... Good night... Laffey, is leveling up... Huh? Commander? Where'd all the monsters go...?
name: Sleepageddon

desc: Oh, Commander? I wasn't waiting for you here... Nope, totally wasn't. But now that you're here, how about we hang out...?
name: Lazy Days

desc: Set, okay! Outfit, okay! All righty, everything's perfect!! Today, Sister Sara is taking on a brand new role as a brand ambassador! How about a taste, Commander?
name: Cup Ramen Ambassador?

desc: Tadah! Make way for the ladylike Sara in a gorgeous dress! Heh, I'm really surprised you found my secret spot this quickly. For that, you get a special reward – a lovely one-on-one with the lovely Sara!
name: Morning Sun Over Azure Skies

desc: ...Hah! Think you can handle more, Commander? I'm not afraid of any fight on the water, but when it comes to diving, I'd be lying if I said I wasn't a little uneasy...
name: Diving Under Blue Skies

desc: Oh, Commander? Sorry you have to see me like this – I overheated a little in the bath... Hm? You smell like nature... It's nice.
name: Bathing Under Sunny Skies

desc: Light cruiser – Seattle.
name: Seattle

desc: Hey! Great to have you here, Commander! I've gotta ask, whaddya think of my dress? Looking real gorgeous, right? ...Phew, awesome! I was worried my dress didn't look nice and might be dragging down the party mood, that's all!
name: Gorgeous Party

desc: Meeeerry Christmas~! Even though the party is about to start, as you can see, I'm still getting ready~ Just gimme a moment, all righty~?
name: Christmas Party Prep!

desc: Supportive sorceress Seattle, comin' in hot! So, something got you down, my good pal? I'm up to talk about whatever's on your mind, but in return, you've gotta come to my party tonight!
name: Sunfish Spell!

desc: Battleship – Georgia.
name: Georgia

desc: Oh? Commander, did you need to get some fresh air as well? Me? Ahaha... It's a bit too stiff inside that venue, so I came out for a change of pace. Why don't we take a little stroll together?
name: South Town Pearl

desc: Heh heh, the warm sun and the sea breeze really hit the spot, don't they? Alright, let's get out there and enjoy ourselves! That's what you've been waiting for, right, Commander?
name: Lanier Swan

desc: Happy New Year, Commander! I guess you dress up all flashy like this for the Sakura New Year. Would you escort me...? What are you gawking like that for...? Haha, am I so dazzling? Hahaha!
name: Exalted Vibrance

desc: Heavy cruiser – Anchorage.
name: Anchorage

desc: Mm... There... Teacher? Is Anchorage doing it right? Is Anchorage... swimming? Thank goodness... Falling into the water would be bad, right...?
name: Dolphins and Swim Lessons

desc: Teacher... How are Anchorage's new clothes? Do you like them...? Yeah, I do, too!
name: Moonlit Boat Ride

desc: Teacher found me...! Anchorage can't sleep... I wanna drink sweet milk... Please?
name: Sweet Evening Milk

desc: Teacher... Anchorage loves you! Our oath... is special! We'll be together... forever!
name: Oath of Sunsets and Fireworks

desc: Aviation battleship – Kearsarge.
name: Kearsarge

desc: I am now the Hybrid Idealization given flesh and blood wearing a suit designed with my performance for you in mind. I am ready to receive orders at any time.
name: All-Night Charge

desc: This suit is a fusion of tradition and modernity. Your feedback would be appreciated... but first, a small issue must be dealt with. May I request your assistance in the matter, Commander?
name: Springtime Monitoring

desc: Fletcher-class destroyer – Halford.
name: Halford

desc: "Welcome, dear guest♪ Right this way~ I'm happy to join you for a treat and chat♪" ...It was good? Well, obviously. I take my work very seriously!
name: A Special Day with the Bunny Lord

desc: Battleship – Kansas.
name: Kansas

desc: *yawn*... That's enough rest. It's just you and me tonight... Whatever it is that you want from me, I've stored up enough energy to go all the way.
name: Late-Night Leisure

desc: A-class prototype destoryer ー Amazon, Hull Number D39!
name: Amazon

desc: No ball is complete without its orchestra! Here, as the leader of the Royal Destroyers Philharmonic, I'll be sure to liven up the night! Now to begin... woaaah! I stepped on my mantle?!
name: Little Orchestra

desc: Selecting me for a retrofit proves that you are a Commander of culture! Heheh, you'd better prepare yourself! From now on, I'll make sure to "take care" of you even more thoroughly!
name: Amazon (Retrofit)

desc: A-class destroyer – Acasta, Hull Number H09.
name: Acasta

desc: Hm? Guess we're both about to head out... Don't stare at me like that... Even I go outdoors sometimes... Since we're both, uh, headed the same way... maybe we could... walk there together?
name: Fashionable Outing

desc: I heard you're supposed to hang lanterns up everywhere during the Spring Festival... so Ardent and I gave it a try! What do you think? Pretty cute, right? Um... I was talking about the lanterns...
name: Lights of the Lantern Festival

desc: Come on, stop running around and behave already... Ah, Commander? Umm, I'm currently looking after these rabbits... Hm, you're thirsty? Um, give me a moment and I'll whip something up for you...
name: Monochromatic Marvel

desc: Ardent told me I "gotta stop looking so tired" and I "gotta be more girly," so I did it while I was retrofitting... Do you recognise me, Commander? ... Umm, I'm Acasta, okay?
name: Acasta (Retrofit)

desc: A-class destroyer – Ardent, Hull Number H41.
name: Ardent

desc: Ehehe~ What do you think, Commander? If you're just going to say "cute," I won't know if you're talking about my school uniform or the chocolate I made...
name: Ardent Valentine

desc: Welcome to Ardent's game house~! I'm here to provide fun and excitement for everyone as the GM– ...Ehehe, actually, I'm still learning as a play~♪
name: Master Ardent?

desc: New outfit, new rigging, same ardent spirit! Ahaha, I'm serious~! Commander, thanks a lot~!
name: Ardent (Retrofit)

desc: B-class destroyer ー Beagle, Hull Number H30!
name: Beagle

desc: B-class destroyer ー Bulldog, Hull Number H91!
name: Bulldog

desc: C-class destroyer ー Comet, Hull Number H00!
name: Comet

desc: Do ya reckon... I you think I've become more idol-like? Mhm! As a new idol, I'll show y'all... I'll show you how hard I work as a new idol!
name: Comet (Retrofit)

desc: C-class destroyer ー Crescent, Hull Number H48!
name: Crescent

desc: Cute? Pretty? Is that all? Can't you expand your vocabulary a little? Jeez... Commander, you really should learn to whisper sweet nothings into my ear!
name: Crescent (Retrofit)

desc: C-class destroyer ー Cygnet, Hull Number H83!
name: Cygnet

desc: Well, the swimsuit that Hood gave to me is a little tight, don't you think? Want to play beach volleyball? Do you think... can we win?
name: Sea Star on Shore

desc: H-happy Christmas! A-after that... umm... I have this present for ya, Commander...
name: Holy Night's Hymn

desc: Aww... it took me a while to get changed... Commander, did I keep you waiting long? Hehe... th-that's good. Let's get going, then~
name: Winter Date

desc: M-Master... good evening... C-Commander, don't stare at me so intently... *Whimper*... Saratoga told me that this is part of marketing yourself as an idol...
name: An Offer To Be Maid

desc: C-Commander? Erm... They picked me to be a cheerleader for the Royal Navy team at the sports thing, so I'm practicin' my cheers... D-don't stare at me like that... I'm shy enough... Already...
name: Royal Fanfare

desc: This outfit is a little tight... Yes, really? I understand. I've got to work harder for the Royal Navy!
name: Cygnet (Retrofit)

desc: F-class destroyer ー Foxhound, Hull Number H69!
name: Foxhound

desc: I've grown so much that I can't jump like I used to... Commander, are you surprised by my post-retrofit appearance? *Giggle*
name: Foxhound (Retrofit)

desc: F-class destroyer ー Fortune, Hull Number H70!
name: Fortune

desc: The weather is so nice and sunny, I'm sure whatever I do today will be a success. May everyone else have a good day today as well... Awauh! Little manjuu, are you okay? I can't believe I tripped...
name: Seraphic Sunshine

desc: Is this really going to help you, Commander? Ah? I doubt our destiny will change with this... Just kidding, Commander! Anything for you.
name: Fortune (Retrofit)

desc: G-class Destroyer - Grenville (H03)
name: Grenville

desc: G-class destroyer ー Glowworm, Hull Number H92!
name: Glowworm

desc: Ahahaha! It is I, Glowworm, the impartial and absolute judge! Any wrongdoers will have me to answer to! Guilty verdicts will result in headbutts!
name: Jokey Adjudicator

desc: Hullo! Royal Navy G-class destroyer, Glowworm, has finished retrofitting! Heheh! I'm ultra-super strong now! You ready to be overwhelmed by the sheer positive energy inside me, Commander?
name: Glowworm (Retrofit)

desc: H-class destroyer – Hardy (H87)
name: Hardy

desc: H-class destroyer – Hunter (H35)
name: Hunter

desc: J-class destroyer ー Javelin, Hull Number F61!
name: Javelin

desc: Everyone, hurry up! We rarely get to go out to play, so let's make every minute count! Javelin packed plenty of lunches, so let's have a picnic by the beach!
name: Beach Picnic!

desc: Tada! We’re all wearing the same uniform! It’s super cute, isn’t it? Heehee, I’ll be wearing it the entire time I’m on duty, so make sure to visit!
name: Let's Become Waitresses!

desc: Javelin, advancing very slowly! Heehee~♪
name: Slow Ahead!

desc: Laffey, Z23, Ayanami, and Unicorn - are you girls ready? Ehehe~ I'm not planning to lose to any of you today~!
name: Operation: Pillow Fight!

desc: "Hello, everyone~! I'm Javelin, the new idol who arrived from the Royal Navy! I hope that my songs will be able to bring a smile to everyone's faces, so please take good care of me!" Hehe, how was that for an introduction, Commander?
name: Energetic Idol @120% Motivation!

desc: *pant* *pant*... I finally got it! The legendary hero's... Ah, d-don't worry about it! This thing might look a bit weird, but my ATK stat has indeed gone up!
name: A Legend is Born?!

desc: Today, I must be the happiest girl in the world! Hehe~
name: Blissful Purity

desc: Heavy attack mode prepared, ready to use ultimate firepower! Check out the incredible glow on this new gun!
name: Javelin (Retrofit)

desc: J-class destroyer ー Juno, Hull Number F46!
name: Juno

desc: I love the bustle of a Sakura festival! Commander, care to try some of Akashi's takoyaki? I've heard their taste is out of this world!
name: Fairly Flavourful Festival

desc: V-class destroyer ー Vampire, Hull Number D68!
name: Vampire

desc: What do you think of my new outfit? You love it? Or just like it? Haha, your answer is written right on your face. Next... wait, wait, wait! I haven't put my socks on yet!
name: The Breath of Spring

desc: Commander, I am now a nurse, so thou hast no choice but to give me thy blood~! Hehe, just kidding~!
name: Little Devil in White

desc: Commander, thou promised to go to the festival with me, right? If thou forgot, I shall have to give thee a nibble upon the neck, ehehe~
name: Night Princess's Regalia

desc: Feast thine eyes upon Vampire's idol attire... is it not exquisite? Heheh, now thy gaze shall be fixed upon my performance alone~♪
name: Night Princess Idol

desc: Why do thee look so astonished? Thou promised to have this Christmas dinner with me. Is it that thou would rather offer me fresh blood than a feast? I certainly wouldn't object to that!
name: Night Princess's Festive Feast

desc: Those who fall in love with vampires are bound to suffer seven times more than their infatuation. After all, love is a poison which leads to death.
name: Eloi's Blessing

desc: J-class destroyer – Jupiter, Hull Number F85.
name: Jupiter

desc: Good evening, Commander. There's a new show on the telly. You want to watch with me?
name: Fanclub Sleepover

desc: J-class destroyer – Jersey, Hull Number F72!
name: Jersey

desc: M-class destroyer – Matchless (G52.)
name: Matchless

desc: Ah, Commander, over here! Hm, you're going to take care of all the plans for today's date? In that case, I look forward to seeing just how suave you can be! Hehe~
name: Escort Me Please!

desc: M-class destroyer – Musketeer (G86.)
name: Musketeer

desc: E-class destroyer – Echo.
name: Echo

desc: Eskimo, Tribal-class Destroyer, is here! Oi, this fleet's not half bad! Nice to meet you, Commander!
name: Eskimo

desc: Oh woe, nobody wants to play with me because they're all too busy~ ...Oh, hello little Manjuu... Heheh, maybe I'll play a prank on you instead!
name: Parkaless Prankster

desc: I-class destroyer – Icarus.
name: Icarus

desc: This is a special exercise for our on-site medical facilities! Well, that's what they said anyway, but isn't this kind of weird...? I feel like I'd rather be taking care of others, not the other way around...
name: One-Week Medical Experience?

desc: "Let's go explore the ocean together! What special things will we be able to find today~?" Hehe, how's that, Commander?
name: Nereid's Discovery

desc: I hope your work's going well, Commander! I've been here playing with these kitties since finishing my duties. Here, I brewed some fresh tea to help you recharge~
name: At Your Service

desc: J-class destroyer – Jervis.
name: Jervis

desc: Phew... That about does it. Next on the agenda is... Huh, Commander? What are you doing here?
name: Fluttering in the Fair Breeze

desc: J-class destroyer – Janus.
name: Janus

desc: D-don't worry, Janus... There's no such thing as Halloween ghouls... Hyeep?! A c-cat?! *whimper*... Jervis, Commander, please come save me...!
name: Fright-Night Scaredy-Cat

desc: It's okay, Janus. You're just getting dressed, so do it like usual, and everything will be fine... Hwuh? Commander? S-sorry! I'm the one who told you to keep your eyes closed, so why did I go and talk to you?!
name: Fear of Changing... Clothes
