desc: It'll be alright, Janus! Nothing bad's going to happen to you just because the light went out and you're all alone... Umm... Hyeep?! C-Commander? D-did you come to pick me up because you were worried...?
name: Don't Turn Off the Lights!

desc: Don't worry, Janus, they'll leave you alone soon... Hwah?! C-Commander? I-I'm sorry! I didn't come up here on purpose. These kitties just, umm, chased me...
name: A Lesson in Billiards

desc: Keep cool, Janus. Just smile... Today's the most important day of your life. I-it's just... Commander, I'm scared of heights...
name: Oath under the Morning Sun

desc: H-class destroyer – Hero.
name: Hero

desc: Morning, Commander. Looks like our desks are right next to each other~ Whee~☆ Hmm? What's up? Is there something on my skirt? Teehee~♪
name: The Devil Wears Knee-Highs

desc: Tribal-class destroyer – Nubian.
name: Nubian

desc: I'm Nubian, the master concocter of magic potions! What kind of potion do you want, Commander? ...Huh? It's been so long since you visited a normal potion maker who brews using a cauldron so you don't know what to order? ...Come again?
name: Normal Potion Maker

desc: Uh, teehee! I was trying to make chocolate, then I slipped for some reason! ...Hang on a minute! How did I slip? Even a modern clumsy maid wouldn't blunder like that... Would she?!
name: The Modern-Day Clumsy Maid Escapade

desc: Battle-class destroyer – Trafalgar.
name: Trafalgar

desc: The breeze is nice, isn't it? Do you want to have a drink with me? (This is exactly how my movies go, so this should work... Is my face too stiff?)
name: Sea Breeze, Moonlit Talks

desc: G-class destroyer – Gallant.
name: Gallant

desc: Can you see me, Commander? I'm here to deliver your takeaway and a parcel! I've already made sure there's no danger out here – oh, and look, my ID! Just like the staff regulations stipulate! Come on, it's safe to open the door!
name: Express-ive Delivery

desc: Leander-class light cruiser – Leander, Hull Number 75!
name: Leander

desc: Everything as you wish, Commander. Oh? Yes, I'm Leander!
name: Leander (Retrofit)

desc: Leander-class light cruiser – Achilles, Hull Number 70!
name: Achilles

desc: The cute and charming Achilles is Super☆Retro☆Fitted! Even my heel won't give me any problems now! Well, not like it really ever did before, ahaha~☆
name: Achilles (Retrofit)

desc: Leander-class light cruiser – Ajax, Hull Number 22!
name: Ajax

desc: Ahaha, that slovenly expression on your face proves I made the right wardrobe choice♪ Now then, Commander, can I offer you some wine?
name: Party Queen

desc: I have some special chocolate right here, just~ for~ you. Hehe, if you want it so badly... then come and get it~
name: Valentine's Reward?

desc: I'll allow you to lick my feet since I'm in such a good mood today. What? I can't believe you'd turn down such a great opportunity!
name: Ajax (Retrofit)

desc: Dido-class light cruiser – Dido (HMS Dido.)
name: Dido

desc: It is so audacious for a lowly maid to dress herself in such finery and stand at her master's side... Still, I will go to my master and... M-M-Master...?!
name: Anxious Bisque Doll

desc: Southampton-class light cruiser – Southampton.
name: Southampton

desc: Hello there~! Royal Knight Southampton is reporting for duty in a Sakura-style outfit! Hehe, don't you have something to tell me about my new look, like how cute it is? Come on, don't be shy. Speak up~
name: New Year's Little Knight

desc: Good day, Comm—Err, I guess it's "Master?" Ugh, I do prefer calling you Commander though... Anyway, I've been practicing the violin to help create better atmosphere around the shop. Did you come here because you were captivated by the sound of my music?
name: Afternoon Impromptu

desc: The Royal Knight, Southampton, makes her grand entrance in glorious wedding garb~! Oh, Commander, you look a bit on edge. Here, c'mere for a second~ Ehehe. *rub rub* Well? Feeling a bit less stiff?
name: A Dazzling Departure

desc: Sheffield-class Light Cruiser - HMS Sheffield
name: Sheffield

desc: ... Did you find out about my undercover identity? You leave me no choice. Master, I cannot allow you to leave this room... Of course I'm jesting, it's merely a hobby.
name: Cloak and Dagger

desc: The Sakura Empire's summer festivals... they're quite noisy. It will be difficult to keep things clean with so many people around... Despite that, I'm still having a good time. Is there a problem?
name: A Moment's Respite

desc: The fact that you're asking your own maid to be your partner at the ball shows a concerning lack of gumption as a human being... However, if you go and make a fool of yourself, it will reflect poorly upon my standing as a maid. Therefore, I have no choice but to accompany you.
name: Black Crow's Finery

desc: Allow me to warn you ahead of time, Master. I will not come to your rescue if you spring another trap, so please mind your step henceforth... Just kidding. It is a maid's duty to aid her master, after all.
name: Bulletborne

desc: (Bang!) As usual, you fail to guard your back. This may just be a game, but I won't abide carelessness, Master. Let's clean this zone and hurry to the next.
name: Occult Clash

desc: Gloucester-class light cruiser – Manchester.
name: Manchester

desc: Master, it's time for your injection! Hmm... Nowhere to be seen, eh... Then I guess I'll keep the sickbed warm until Master comes ba– Eep! M-M-Master?!
name: Midnight Devil in White

desc: Welcome to the beach, Master! Pretty hot today, innit. If you'll have me, I'm right okay with spending the day together.
name: A Moment in the Shade

desc: Gloucester-class light cruiser – Gloucester (HMS Gloucester.)
name: Gloucester

desc: Gloucester, light cruiser of the Royal Maids, at your service for the Spring Festival... You say I look displeased? I beg your pardon, it's just... Such holidays are in fact quite busy for the Maids. We have much on our minds. It is none of your concern.
name: Brilliance in Purple

desc: Commander, please sit properly when you're riding the carousel, and refrain from haphazardly bouncing up and down... Why am I holding a whip, you ask? Why, as a trainer, it is my duty to instruct you on the proper usage of fairgrounds equipment.
name: Violet Enrapturement

desc: Edinburgh-Class light cruiser ー Edinburgh, Hull number 16!
name: Edinburgh

desc: Why doesn't she have to go to school with me...she says she’s a maid for the Queen? Well, me too! You can be a maid and school girl at the same time...tsk tsk---
name: The Library Fairy

desc: Ahem! I made this special candy just for Halloween! Here, Commander, take some! Wooaaooah! Wh-who put this pumpkin here? It, it was me?!
name: Candy Maid

desc: Edinburgh-Class light cruiser ー Belfast, Hull number C35!
name: Belfast

desc: Hehe... Master, why are you so stunned from seeing me? I thought you perhaps wanted to see me in a qipao... was I mistaken?
name: Iridescent Rosa

desc: This is special cold-weather equipment inspired by Eagle Union designs. It was made for practical purposes such as special operations in frigid climates, and as such, was not designed with appearances in mind. Please do forgive me, Master.
name: Serene Steel

desc: Good evening. The Royal Maids will be chaperoning this event. It is my hope to prevent any inappropriate behaviour that might interfere with the enjoyment of the attendees. Please pardon any inconveniences this may cause.
name: The Noble Attendant

desc: Hehe~ Judging from your expression, Master, my outfit has not fallen short of your expectations. As time is precious, allow me to serve you to the utmost on this "date."
name: Shopping with the Head Maid

desc: Welcome, table for one? Of course, right this way. Oh? What is it? Ah... I'm filling in for the manager at the moment, so that makes you my customer rather than my master, no?
name: Piping-Hot Perfection

desc: It took me quite some time to prepare a suitable traditional Sakura Empire outfit. Terribly sorry. Master, won't you please allow this Belfast to serve you for another year?
name: Folded Fascination

desc: Heehee. How do you do, Master? The temperatures just won't go down this summer, so I brought cold, carbonated drinks for you to fend off heat stroke. Go on, have a drink.
name: Blissful Service

desc: Are you destined for me? Greetings Belfast, from this moment onwards, I will always be with you.
name: The Pledge of Claddagh

desc: Arethusa-class light cruiser – Arethusa, Hull Number 26!
name: Arethusa

desc: Arethusa-class light cruiser – Galatea, Hull Number 71!
name: Galatea

desc: Arethusa-class light cruiser - Aurora, pennant number 12
name: Aurora

desc: I've been preparing for this day for quite some time... Commander, would you like to hear the book I wrote for you?
name: The Tale of Spring

desc: I've always believed that music is unique in its power to touch one's heart, so I decided to learn the violin. Commander, please enjoy my performance.
name: Dawn's Paean

desc: "Next, Aurora will perform something you've never seen before - traditional Sichuan mask-changing opera!" Hehe... Commander, I look like the real deal, right?
name: Heritage of Yu City

desc: Commander, please relax and take a seat. This is a special place for just the two of us... Just kidding, did I get your heart racing just now? Ehehe~
name: Garb of Eternal Prosperity

desc: Fiji-class light cruiser – Fiji.
name: Fiji

desc: Did I keep you waiting, Commander? Ahaha... A girl's gotta take her time before stepping out onto the streets, remember? Come on, take my hand, and let's get going! Hehe~
name: Trendy and Vogue?

desc: Fiji-class light cruiser – Jamaica.
name: Jamaica

desc: Hey Boss, you talkin' about my sweet bike? Heh, I made it myself by scrounging up parts from Akashi's place. Pretty cool, huh?
name: Dark Bolt

desc: Look, Boss, this is the new bike that Akashi sent me. She said she wanted me to be her brand ambassador... Doesn't that job sound badass?
name: Highway Star

desc: Edinburgh-class light cruiser – Belfast.
name: Little Bel

desc: Southampton-class light cruiser – Newcastle (HMS Newcastle.)
name: Newcastle

desc: This outfit makes me stand out a bit too much... But, as long as it makes you happy, I'm just as pleased.
name: Hibiscus Garments

desc: I've got an all new outfit here. Does it please you...? Hehe, seeing you all giddy like that is going to rub off on me as well.
name: Newcastle (Retrofit)

desc: Dido-class light cruiser – Sirius.
name: Sirius

desc: My dear, I changed into the new outfit as per your request. I would be most grateful were you to offer me words of praise, Master.
name: White Rose

desc: I've received ample advice from my colleagues in the Maid Team regarding swimwear etiquette. My honourable Master, are you pleased with my appearance?
name: Scorching-Hot Seirios

desc: I have heard it is part of a maid's duties to dress to her honourable Master's liking over the holidays. Would this outfit happen to... satisfy the honourable Master's wishes?
name: Azure Horizons

desc: To you, Honourable Master, I dedicate this dance of paradise. It is something I have spent a great deal of time practicing... I do hope that it is to your liking.
name: Rabbit of Paradise

desc: Ceres-class light cruiser - Curacoa (D41)
name: Curacoa

desc: As I am but a maid, it is a great honor to be able to wear such a gorgeous outfit… How do I look, Commander? "Not sure where to start feasting your eyes?" Oh my... Commander...
name: Eastern Grace

desc: It is my honour to be of everyone's service. Light cruiser Curacoa takes it upon herself to continue serving you, Master.
name: Curacoa (Retrofit)

desc: Ceres-class light cruiser - Curlew (D42)
name: Curlew

desc: You can feel the profound heritage and culture of the Dragon Empery from all these customs and outfits for the Lunar New Year's Festival… It seems to be ever more necessary to study the traditions and etiquette of this wondrous culture.
name: Rhythm of the Dragon Empery

desc: I am now more capable than ever of demonstrating the Royal Maids' style. Though I am not as talented as my sister, Curacoa, I sincerely hope you will find my service satisfactory. It is a great honour to work for you.
name: Curlew (Retrofit)

desc: I am Swiftsure, a light cruiser of the Royal Navy... If it is not too much for one such as myself to ask, I would like to support your fleet in whatever way I can.
name: Swiftsure

desc: Commander, why are you here...? Me? Yes, as you can see, I'm still studying... I figured that acquiring knowledge would be the best way to make up for my lack of experience on the actual battlefield.
name: Study Hall Cyclamen

desc: I agreed to try on this outfit, but... I know these fancy outfits don't suit me... H-huh, I look gorgeous?! ...Thank you very much. Even if you're just trying to make me feel better, I appreciate it...
name: Beauty of White Jade

desc: W-welcome! ...Ugh, I'm still way too nervous... Ah, um! H-how may I serve you today, Commander...?
name: Midsummer Special Service

desc: Err, you're... the Commander, yes? You don't know who I am? Ah, right, I've yet to introduce myself... I'm Black Prince of the Royal Navy... Will that suffice?
name: Black Prince

desc: Sorry to keep you waiting, Commander. Thank you very much for taking me on vacation. Standing in front of you like this... is a little embarrassing... Nevertheless, what do you think of... my swimsuit?
name: White Princess

desc: A "qipao," is it? So this legendary dress from the Dragon Empery... Putting it on and enjoying some nostalgic music, makes me... Ahhh... Commander, might we relax like this a bit longer...?
name: Fair Maid Spring

desc: You can't have a party without champagne, right? Now, if I remember right, you're meant to give it a good shake before popping the cork... Oh no! Look out, Commander!
name: Pop the Cork

desc: Oh... Welcome, Commander. Can I take your order...? Or maybe, you just wanted to kick back and relax? ...Either way is fine with me.
name: Addled Attendant?

desc: Commander, today's the day we make our vows, so could you make me do something for you? It'll make me feel warm, and... I want to feel that warmth a lot, lot more.
name: Love's Greeting

desc: I am Sheffield, from the Royal Maids. I will explain how this transpired to you, so please stop looking like the world has turned upside down.
name: Sheffield μ

desc: Southampton-class light cruiser - Glasgow (C-21)
name: Glasgow

desc: Y-ye said ye wanted ta see me wear something different, so... But this is not "cosplay" or somesuch! I do actually go to school...! D-do ye like it?
name: A Maid in Class

desc: Dido-class light cruiser – Hermione (HMS Hermione.)
name: Hermione

desc: My, what brings you here, Commander? Are you feeling unwell? That's no good... Why don't you come sit over here first? I'll start by taking your temperature...
name: Pure White Angel

desc: Commander, I've brought the chair. If you don't want to get in the water, feel free to sit here. ...Hm, me? Of course, I will remain by your side.
name: Pure White Holiday

desc: Would you care for some afternoon tea, Commander? Heehee~ This is one of my little hobbies when I'm not performing my maid duties.
name: Graceful Afternoon Tea

desc: How are you feeling, Commander? Hehe, I'm not wearing my usual nurse's gown right now, but I suppose this isn't much different~
name: Pristine Herbalist

desc: Commander, umm... Happy Valentine's Day! What do you think of my outfit? Hehe, it's perfect for a date, isn't it?
name: Winter Dearest

desc: I'm so happy to have come this far with you, Commander. May this gorgeous sunrise watch over us for all time... I love you, Commander.
name: Dawn's Oath

desc: I am the light cruiser, Dido, currently taking part in idol activities as part of the experimental Muse System. I learned more or less what idols are supposed to do from the others, so p-please... keep a close eye on me!
name: Dido µ

desc: Arethusa-class light cruiser – Penelope.
name: Penelope

desc: Aurora chose this outfit for me because... the Spring Festival represents a time of celebration in the Dragon Empery, and red is the color that best symbolizes that. What do you think? Does this outfit... make you feel more festive?
name: Ruby-Red Boudoir

desc: Welcome, welcome. I've been working here as a maid, just as you told me to. Umm... Call for me only when you're ready to order.
name: Salty Maid

desc: Dido-class light cruiser – Charybdis.
name: Charybdis

desc: *Pats thighs* Master, you poor thing~ Look how hard you've been working~ Hehe, hurry and come here so that I can pamper you~
name: Red Chamber of Healing

desc: Tis a pleasure to see you, Master. I am delighted to be your partner for today. ...Oh, I was just trying to sound prim and proper! You don't need to look at me with such pity in your eyes!
name: Brilliant Belle

desc: As you can see, today's theme... is a seaside pampering, or something like that~ Heehee. I know you're no stranger to the sea, Commander, but today, we're here to play, not work. Just take it easy, and unwind~♪
name: Prim Sea Breeze

desc: Bellona-class light cruiser – Bellona.
name: Bellona

desc: My liege... No, excuse me, I should be calling you Master, right? Bellona of the Royal Maids, reporting in. My, you seem quite lost for words... I'll explain the situation to you later, so don't worry about it.
name: Armed to Clean

desc: Emerald-class light cruiser –Enterprise.
name: Enterprise

desc: Dido-class light cruiser – Scylla.
name: Scylla

desc: Did you come all this way just because I asked you to, Master? Or... would you prefer I call you "Senpai" here? If we're at school, then there's no reason for me to act maidly, now is there? Heeheehee♪
name: Femme Fatale Fresher

desc: Good evening, Master of mine. I hope I didn't make you wait long. Oh? That look on your face... Were you excited to walk on the red carpet with me, arm in arm?
name: Bathed in the Limelight

desc: Welcome, my dear Master – no, I suppose you're just a traveler at this moment? I'd like to say, "All who pass through here must be judged," but I wouldn't be against simply letting my Master through.
name: A Maid's Judgment

desc: Gloucester-class light cruiser – Liverpool.
name: Liverpool

desc: Holy Wind! Blow them away! ...Oh no! The wind's so strong it's lifting up my dress! Um, Master, y-you didn't... see anything, did you?
name: Breeze of Blessings

desc: Dido-class light cruiser – Cleopatra.
name: Cleopatra

desc: Ah, Master, welcome. How do you like the set I put together? Has your heart been stolen? This book describes how the gods arrange their rooms when they look upon the stars... It's not quite a perfect replica, but isn't it pretty?
name: Stars and Roses

desc: Fiji-class light cruiser – Trinidad.
name: Trinidad

desc: Oh dear... You found me already? Here I thought I'd surprise you with my swimsuit... Oh well, what's done is done. Wanna go swimming? And don't worry, I'm as gentle as they get when I play the instructor♪
name: Trapper in the Changing Room

desc: London-class heavy cruiser – London, Hull Number 69!
name: London

desc: Splendid work today, Your Excellency. Here are your documents for the next mission. It has everything you need to know, so please give it a read. Heehee, I'm happy to assist so that you may focus solely on achieving your goals.
name: The Sterling Secretary

desc: Why are you so astounded, Your Excellency? You expressly requested an unforgettable and elaborate ceremony. Heehee, you'll make it weird if you keep staring so much, so won't you please take my hand now?
name: Platinum Ceremony

desc: Um... Your Excellency, could you please stop staring at me like you don't recognise me? I didn't think that I'd get a new look for my retrofit, either... But, don't you think it's rather cute?
name: London (Retrofit)

desc: London-class heavy cruiser – Shropshire, Hull Number 73!
name: Shropshire

desc: As you know, I'm the youngest of London class, Shropshire~ I'm excited to work with you! Heheh, I look pretty capable now, don't I? Maybe I'll cause a little less trouble for you now, Commander!
name: Shropshire (Retrofit)

desc: Kent-class heavy cruiser - Kent, Hull Number 54!
name: Kent

desc: Kent-class heavy cruiser - Suffolk, Hull Number 55!
name: Suffolk

desc: Whew... At long last, after all that hard work, I get to wear this uniform as well. Even though all I did was... Huh? Lead by example? Be a role model? I don't get it...
name: Suffolk (Retrofit)

desc: Norfolk-class heavy cruiser - Norfolk, Hull Number 78!
name: Norfolk

desc:
Norfolk-class heavy cruiser, Dorsetshire, Hull Number 40
<color=#fad545>Unlock build after receiving</color>
name: Dorsetshire

desc: York-class heavy cruiser - York, Hull Number 90!
name: York

desc: The school has recently been consumed by a series of Mysteries... there must be some Mastermind lurking behind the scenes. Yes, another Tribulation awaits me! I shall part the veil and reveal all Truths!
name: Truth Seeker

desc: O Unfathomable King of the slumbering depths, hear the call of my Force and step into this world through the Azur Gate! ...Huh, Commander? Why did you show up?
name: Summoner from the Azure Depths

desc: Whoa... Is this my Uniform for the ceremony known as the Oath of Purity? Hohoho... This must be fate. Join me, Commander, and we shall make the world right once more!
name: Oath of Purity

desc: This is no mere Upgrade, this is an Awakening! I will alter the course of fate itself!
name: York (Retrofit)

desc: York-class heavy cruiser - Exeter, Hull Number 68!
name: Exeter

desc: Cheers, Commander. I'm glad that the party is a success. Well, I should take care as well to not sully the honour of the royal family with my actions.
name: A Glorious Toast

desc: Commander, what do you think? I look more mature than I did before... right?
name: Exeter (Retrofit)

desc: London-class heavy cruiser, Sussex. Hull Number 96.
name: Sussex

desc: What are you spacing out for? Have you not gotten tired of staring at all the swimsuits yet? Good grief... Are you able to help set up the parasol or the beach chairs at least?
name: Sunlit Tulips

desc: What are you staring at me for? I'm just the same as any of the others... Y-you have a few more hands to shake? Of course...
name: Wine and Red Roses

desc: Heavy cruiser – Cheshire.
name: Little Cheshire

desc: London-class heavy cruiser – Devonshire.
name: Devonshire

desc: Roleplay mode engaged. "I am Devonshire, the greater demon who controls this land. If you understand the difference in our power levels, you will leave and train yourself in a beginner dungeon for three hundred years. Adventurers such as you will never make it through here alive."
name: Sadistic Demon

desc: Renown-class battlecruiser - Renown
name: Renown

desc: This Dragon Empery dress is lovely and graceful, but the slit... Commander? I'm sorry if this is sudden, but... how do you like my dress?
name: Graceful Royal Pride

desc: Renown-class battlecruiser - Repulse
name: Repulse

desc: Hey there, Commander! Heheh, where do you think you're going? If you've got a minute, watch me rehearse my sword dance. It's my own original routine, a combination of Dragon Empery swordplay and my own ideas!
name: Dance of Spring Blooms

desc: Admiral-class battlecruiser - Hood, Hull Number 51!
name: Hood

desc: What a feast for sore eyes. I feel great~! Vacations really should be at the beach! Let's show Sara your beach ball, Cygnet!
name: Lady of the Shining Sun

desc: Thank you for inviting me on this wonderful trip. Now that I have donned this beautiful outfit, shall we partake of a Sakura Empire tea party– leisurely and elegantly?
name: Porcelain Grace

desc: Beauty is not always over the rainbow. Sometimes it is right in your backyard. Commander, how would you like to spend this quiet, lovely day right here with me?
name: Dawnlight's Dame

desc: Whoa, there... There you are, Commander. You could have waited at the clubhouse... Why yes, the view is just beautiful, isn't it? Hahaha, thank you for bringing me here today.
name: Gentlewoman and Stallion

desc: If the smooth path only allows one person to travel at a time, then I’ll gladly walk the path not taken with you hand-in-hand.
name: Rosey Love Poem

desc: Renown-Class Battlecruiser - HMS Renown
name: Little Renown

desc: Queen Elizabeth-class battleship - Queen Elizabeth, Hull Number 00!
name: Queen Elizabeth

desc: Hah haah! You're a lucky servant this evening! We shall allow you to accompany us to the party! ... B-but it's not like I chose you because I like you! I just... Yes! I just sort of chose randomly! Got it?!
name: The Queen's Ball

desc: Now this is a stage worthy of our majesty! You are not to leave our sight, servant! Let your passions burn for me!
name: One Night of the Queen

desc: Hehe, behold the new outfit that I had Akashi make for me! Impressive, no? Prostrate yourself before the elegant charm of my school uniform, servant~♪
name: Queen of the Campus

desc: Did I hear that you're supposed to give out red envelopes during the Dragon Empery's New Year? This is a fine chance to display the magnanimity of the Queen of the Royal Navy! ...Don't just run off with your gift! Spread the word of my glory, my servant!
name: Crown Jewel of the Royal Navy

desc: Warspite, what in the world is all this... The Maid Team has to sift through all this paperwork?! I'm tired already... I wish I never mentioned wanting to experience what it's like to be a maid... And you, stop staring and help me already, servant!
name: Yes, Your Maidness!

desc: Servant, what do you think you're doing?! Instead of wasting your life working, go have some fun in the sea for once! We went out of our way to come to the beach, so do not disappoint me!
name: Seaside Orders

desc: Queen Elizabeth-class battleship - Warspite, Hull Number 03!
name: Warspite

desc: This year, I am in charge of delivering presents to the children of the Royal Navy. Let's get going once I finish decorating this Christmas tree!
name: Christmas Warrior

desc: We have the finest equipment. Now to turn in a performance worthy of Her Majesty's beauty... Behold, the Royal Stage!
name: Under Pleasure

desc: Humph! Good, a perfectly halved watermelon. The Sakuran watermelon-splitting technique is surprisingly easy to master... Well met, Commander. Mind delivering these melons to the others for me?
name: The Grand Old Lady Sunders All

desc: Warspite, retrofitting complete. Mm, I rather like this feeling of being rejuvenated... Now, Commander, let us make our way towards new battlegrounds!
name: Warspite (Retrofit)

desc: Nelson-class battleship – Nelson, Hull Number 28!
name: Nelson

desc: This is such a weird costume… oh well, it’s Halloween after all. It cannot be so bad, this is a fun activity after all. First things first, I didn’t say that I would join from the very beginning!
name: Luna Witch

desc: Hey, are you even enjoying yourself? At least pretend to have fun when I went out of my way to invite you, or else I'm going to lose sleep over this! ...Look behind me? What are you– Oh...!
name: Azure & Gold Summer Night

desc: H-hey, are you sleeping all day, or what? My retrofit is all done. Hmph, you might've widened the gap between us, but... I'm gonna keep on pushing my limits! Got it?
name: Nelson (Retrofit)

desc: Nelson-class battleship – Rodney, Hull Number 29!
name: Rodney

desc: Although it's a gift from the Commander, it's still embarrassing to wear this....Commander, do you think you could teach me how to swim?
name: Future Seaside Admiral

desc: Miss Akashi, shall I look at the camera next? Understood. Oh, Commander, I did not expect you to grace us with your presence here as well! Yes, the photoshoot is proceeding smoothly. By the way, is there a favorite pose you'd like to see?
name: Immaculate Beauty

desc: I never imagined that this dreamlike situation would come to pass... Commander, have you also been looking forward to sharing this moment with me? Hehe~
name: Palace of Blessings

desc: King George V-class battleship – King George V.
name: King George V

desc: Sorry to keep you waiting, Commander... I don't get to wear a dress very often, so it took me a bit longer. Let's get going, then. Remember, you'll be the lead tonight. Haha~
name: Rose's Regalia

desc: King George V-class battleship – Prince of Wales, Hull Number 53!
name: Prince of Wales

desc: I'm not a big fan of beach volleyball, but Hood begged me... I swear, that girl! She just can't get enough of the sun! You've got to cheer for me!
name: Sun Shining Upon Windsor

desc: I've been wearing Royal attire my whole life, so a change in pace doesn't seem bad. Oh, Commander, good timing. Can you explain to me how to celebrate the New Year here?
name: Sakura Elegance

desc: Oh, Commander. Worry not. Since I've been given this job, I will see through it until the end. Besides, it's been a while since I've gotten this fired up. Haha!
name: The Laureate's Victory Lap

desc: I expected you sooner, Commander. I decided to practice the saxophone while I had some time alone... You shouldn't keep a lady waiting in the future. Heehee. Anyway, I suppose we could listen to a song before we set off, no?
name: A Knight's Song, a Lady's Night

desc: King George V-class battleship - HMS Duke of York.
name: Duke of York

desc: Ahh, this luscious scent... comes from thee. What dost thee feel when gazing upon my new dress? Hehe... your lips may lie but your eyes do not...
name: Eternal Night's Carola

desc: My beautiful Adonis, why dost thou refuseth to take refuge in the trove of everlasting love... Perhaps my outfit can finally pierce thy heart? Hehe~
name: Prestige of the Glorious Formula

desc: Thou hast come. Welcome to my Athenaeum, young Odysseus. Today, thou shalt receive Duke of York's instruction – now, come forth, take a seat, and hearken to my teachings.
name: The Chic Counselor

desc: King George V-class battleship – Howe (HMS Howe.)
name: Howe

desc: Sorry to keep you waiting, but now I'm ready to– Commander? What's the matter? It'll get dark soon if you keep standing around like that.
name: Noble Rouge

desc: "Please, Master, save meee." ...Ugh, I can't get into the role. What sort of tone should I be aiming for, love?
name: Pastry Princess

desc: Thanks for your patience, love. I've looked forward to this evening's party for a long, long time. Hopefully George, York, and company won't laugh at me after how much effort I've put into this ensemble... What do you think of it, Commander?
name: Evening Marvels

desc: Queen Elizabeth-class battleship – Valiant (HMS Valiant.)
name: Valiant

desc: Hehe~ As this medical facility training is crucially important, a charismatic leader such as myself would be best suited to instruct everyone on– Wait a moment, what's with this outfit?! You there, explain the meaning of this at once!
name: Mischievous Little Nurse

desc: Why the astonished look on your face? You heard me correctly! On this day, I am not merely Valiant, I am the regal and royal Queen Valiant!
name: Queen Valiant I

desc: R-class battleship – Revenge.
name: Revenge

desc: Hrmm... *sigh*... Looks like I bungled this one too... I sure hope the Commander doesn't see me like th– Hwuh?! C-Commander? P-please give me a moment! I'll straighten this out right away... Waaah!!
name: The Maid-Knight Charges Forth!

desc: Battleship – Vanguard.
name: Vanguard

desc: "Please let me know if you need anything, Master"... I'm starting to think you're making me wear this as a sick joke. The reason being, I am obviously NOT fit to be a Royal Maid... Even if I do adore their uniforms...
name: Half-Hearted Masquerade

desc: R-class battleship – Royal Oak.
name: Royal Oak

desc: Commander? Oh, what a coincidence... Were you slacking– err, I mean, taking a break, too? I can make some room for you if you'd like?
name: Bashful Oak

desc: Lion-class battleship – Lion.
name: Lion

desc: Heh. I hereby claim this beach as part of my territory. Whew... Say, Commander, since we've been afforded some time to relax, why don't we do so? Oh, and feel free to come a little closer.
name: The Reclining Dandelion

desc: Hermes-class aircraft carrier – Hermes, Hull Number 95!
name: Hermes

desc: Our glory coalesces into the bonds that forge a bright new future! Let's rev it up! Hermes, retrofit complete!
name: Hermes (Retrofit)

desc: Light aircraft carrier – Argus.
name: Argus

desc: Yaaawn... Umm, did I doze off again? Oh no... Organising school events gets so hectic I always end up working right up until curfew... Just give me one more minute, please...
name: A Hundred Sleepless Eyes

desc: "Gaze upon this glorious dress. Admire its brilliance, tremble, and..." If you don't mind, would you please take Argus' hand?
name: Cerulean Enthrallment

desc: Aircraft carrier – Unicorn, Hull Number I72!
name: Unicorn

desc: Unicorn... is now a songstress... *giggles* Unicorn's song has reached Onii-chan's heart.
name: Little Star Songstress

desc: This... present... is for you... I hope you like it... What? Me wearing this outfit is the best gift I can give you? Co... Commander!...
name: The Gift of Spring

desc: Ah, big brother, you're here... Ehehe, I only just got here as well. Um... shall we go then? I kind of... want to go to the amusement park...
name: Long-Awaited Date

desc: So this is a "kimono" from the Sakura Empire... Changing into it is difficult but... if you like it, then Unicorn is happy!
name: Prayer of Plum and Snow

desc: So I'm... an "idol" now... I'm not sure how well I'll do... But I'll give it my all...!
name: Angelic Night

desc: Oh, big brother... Unicorn is reading right now. Mm, yeah, while eating ice cream... Big brother, want to have a bite?
name: Icy-Sweet Storytime

desc: Unicorn... is now serving as a nurse. Umm... Big brother, would you mind being Unicorn's patient...?
name: Angelic Nurse

desc: This is... an important outfit for an important ceremony... yes! Unicorn and Yuni are both ready for this! Big brother... how do I look?
name: A Dream of Pure Vows

desc: Unicorn has finished her retrofit... Now she can do more for you and her friends!
name: Unicorn (Retrofit)

desc: Centaur-class light aircraft carrier – Centaur.
name: Centaur

desc: Even though I see the ocean every day, changing into this swimsuit gives me a totally new outlook on it. How about you, Commander? Don't you feel at ease?
name: Beachside Undine

desc: I never imagined you would give me such a splendid dress, Commander... I think it's called a "qipao..." is it? I'll try it, revealing though it is. Wh- what do you think...? Do I look... nice?
name: Sprightly Spring Wind

desc: Attacker-class escort carrier - Chaser (D32)
name: Chaser

desc: Does this dress from the Dragon Empery not suit me well? Though I was born in the Eagle Union and raised by the Royal Navy, my time in the Dragon Empery also left a deep impression upon me. Why don't we have a chat about their profound culture and tea? Hehe~
name: The Way of the Dragon Empery

desc: Heck yeah! Another achievement down! ...Huh? Good day, Commander. Is there something wrong with my appearance? Hehe, I'm from the Eagle Union after all, of course I'd know a thing or two about entertainment~♪
name: Gamer Style

desc: Colossus-class light aircraft carrier – Perseus (HMS Perseus.)
name: Perseus

desc: I'm Perseus, I will be your nurse today. Use this button to call for me if you need anything... Yes? Did you need something?
name: Unfamiliar Duties

desc: Whew. Lunar New Year... Easy to grasp in various ways. Both the holiday and your tastes, I mean. Heehee.
name: Spring's Lackadaisical Leisure

desc: Centaur-class light aircraft carrier – Albion.
name: Albion

desc: Ah, umm... If you keep staring at me like that... Oh, um, Commander, this is supposed to be a Royalty of the Night costume, right? In that case... Would you mind kneeling for me first?
name: Silvermoon Faerie Princess

desc: Hand brushing my hair behind my ear, eyes toward the camera... Mm, filming promotional material isn't easy... Commander, will this do?
name: Scent of Spring in the Red Pavilion

desc: Good morning, Commander. Umm... I was excited to prepare a perfect breakfast for you, but I made some mistakes. Please wait a moment. I'll remake it in no time!
name: A Fairy-Tale Breakfast

desc: Colossus-class light carrier – Theseus.
name: Theseus

desc: Steaming hot manjuu buns, ready to be served! Let us have a big feast then gather rosebuds, Commander. Oh, a "holiday gathering" doesn't involve literal gathering?
name: New Year's White Plumage

desc: Eagle-class light aircraft carrier – Eagle (HMS Eagle.)
name: Eagle

desc: This may be an exercise, but even so I will give it my all. Right now, I am not just a Royal Navy warrior, but a medical resident as well. If you ever feel ill, come see me, Commander.
name: Eagle's Clinic

desc: Aircraft carrier – Ark Royal, Hull Number 91!
name: Ark Royal

desc: Nothing says summer like the sun, the beach, and destroyers... Ahem! Th-that's right! Even though we're relaxing, we still have to keep an eye out for enemy destroyers! Commander, I may be in a swimsuit, but I'm ready to sortie at any time!
name: Coast Watcher

desc: One tends to let her guard down at a party like this, but worry not! Put the ball in my hands and let Ark Royal keep you safe!
name: Guardian of the Ball

desc: Commander, Happy New Year. Oh no, I'm not going hunting. I'm patrolling the port during the New Year's celebrations. Naturally, I volunteered for the job.
name: New Year's Protectress

desc: This is the place, Commander. What are you going to order? Me, I think I'll have the same as you... Yeah, so what? I just felt like grabbing a coffee with you for once.
name: Café Lookout

desc: Commander! Here to enjoy yourself? Me, I'm working tirelessly on keeping order around the amusement park! ...That sounds fun to you? Alright, then watch how it's done!
name: Order Amidst Amusement

desc: I never thought a day would come when even I don such attire... Ahem. Your Excellency, I shall protect your happiness, as well as that of my destroyer sisters!
name: Pure-White Protector

desc: Ark Royal retrofitting complete! Now I can protect you, my friends, and of course, the little destroyers, to the very end!
name: Ark Royal (Retrofit)

desc: Illustrious-class aircraft carrier – Illustrious, Hull Number 87!
name: Illustrious

desc: Sun kissed skin, scrumptious snacks and delicious black tea. It’s as if both my mind and body have been rejuvenated— Commander, care to join me for some leisurely chit-chat?
name: Never-Ending Tea Party

desc: An invitation to the ball? Hehe, I would be honored to go... as long as you don't decline, Commander~
name: Illustrious Ball

desc: This is my first time wearing such exotic fashion, hehe~. Commander, if you like how I look, how about showing me off a little~?
name: Resplendent Hibiscus

desc: It is my honour to get to wear another faction's garments. However... this traditional Dragon Empery dress feels rather tight around the chest area...
name: Maiden Lily's Radiance

desc: A gentle melody for a peaceful celebration. Today, Commander, I offer this tune to you and the people of the port. May my melody please your ears♪
name: Lambent Melody

desc: Oh, Commander? It's a pleasure to see you. Umm, I'm currently going over some... "extracurricular studies." If you have some time to spare, would you mind joining me?
name: Our Private "Study" Session

desc: The end of sorrow, the beginning of happiness, and the desire for eternity.
name: Morning Star of Love and Hope

desc: Illustrious-class aircraft carrier – Victorious.
name: Victorious

desc: Hum~ dee dum♪~ I'm all dressed up, and my hair is perfect! Commander, I'm ready to go! Don't keep me waiting on a holiday!
name: The Goddess' Day Off

desc: Are you preparing to hold an event for the port? Hehe, sounds like you could use my help. Don't worry, with someone as beautiful as me around, anything you do will surely be blessed with success!
name: Guidance of the Spring Goddess

desc: *Yaaawn*... Basking in the autumnal night's wind while gazing at the moon is the very definition of elegance, is it not? Heehee. Right now, I am not acting as a Lady of the Royal Navy, but rather as an "ojou" of the Sakura Empire elegantly enjoying her tea... Hyeep! Hot?!
name: Upon Nights Brisk and Beautiful

desc: Illustrious-class aircraft carrier – Formidable.
name: Formidable

desc: Good day, Commander. I am Formidable, third ship of the Illustrious class. Pleased to make your acquaintance.
name: The Lady of the Beach

desc: Yes, this will do wonderfully! Thank you, ladies. Phew... Getting dressed is so dreadfully time-consuming... Ahem! How silly of me. I must not whine in the presence of others.
name: Timeless Classics

desc: Good afternoon, Commander. Why am I still in class during lunch break? Heheh, as you can see, I'm on duty. Commander, won't you spend some time with me while I prepare for the next class?
name: The Lover's Heart Flutters On Duty

desc: Phew... Finally got the scissors... Wait, C-Commander?! Why are you here already?! Close the door quickly and look away... N-no, actually, come and help me untangle this ribbon!
name: Rockin' Encore

desc: To both express my eternal love and gratitude to you and celebrate the wonderful days we've spent together, I will be joining in the port's celebration. ...Ahem, Commander? Tell me the next part!
name: Anniversary Memories

desc: Courageous-class aircraft carrier – Glorious, Hull Number 77.
name: Glorious

desc: Being able to occasionally have a peaceful school life... is something I could get used to. Commander, look at the markings on this butterfly - aren't they lovely?
name: Glorious School Life

desc: I heard that the Sakura Empire's traditional attire was really hard to put on... but the Dragon's Empery's outfits are even more... Huh?! Commander, p-please look away!
name: Pungent Plum

desc: Implacable-class aircraft carrier – Implacable.
name: Implacable

desc: Oh my... It seems I've shown you a rather unseemly side of me. Would you help me clean up here, Commander? You know... before any of the other girls find out. Heehee~♥
name: Shepherd of the "Lost"

desc: Illustrious-class aircraft carrier – Illustrious, Hull Number 87.
name: Little Illustrious

desc: I am the newest addition to the Muse System, Illustrious. Through my songs, I shall spread the light of love and peace— Don't you think that's a wonderful thing?
name: Illustrious μ

desc: Illustrious-class aircraft carrier – Indomitable.
name: Indomitable

desc: *Sigh*... I thought changing into maid attire would break up the monotony, but just getting into these clothes has tired me out... Oh, Commander? You came at a good time. Shall we slack off together?
name: Ms. Motivationless Maid

desc: Illustrious-class aircraft carrier – Formidable.
name: Little Formidable

desc: Commander, third ship and idol of the Illustrious class, Formidable, humbly makes your acquaintance. Please do enjoy the show... Heehee, doesn't that just make you shudder with excitement?
name: Formidable μ

desc: Erebus-class monitor – Erebus, Hull Number I02!
name: Erebus

desc: Those who embrace the shadows will find only an illusory happiness... But for me, that much is sufficient.
name: Illusory Happiness

desc: "I am the witch of Hallow's Eve, here to guide your soul into the ever darkness"... that's what the concept of the Halloween witch is about, right?
name: Wardrobe Witchery

desc: Erebus-class monitor – Terror, Hull Number I03!
name: Terror

desc: I have to dress up as a ghost for Halloween, but I'm not very good at making complicated costumes... Is something like this okay?
name: Halloween Terror

desc: Roberts-class monitor - Abercrombie. Hull Number F109.
name: Abercrombie

desc: Kabooom! You thought it was a pumpkin, but it was me, Abercrombie, with my Mark I! Commander, did I scare you senseless? Muahaha!
name: Pumpkin Blast!

desc: Now for a ghost pepper while nobody's looking... Tee hee! Perfect! I wonder who'll be the lucky one to sip– C-Commander?! You didn't see anything suspicious... Right? Tee hee~
name: Mischief on the Rocks

desc: Found you! No criminals are escaping on my watch! You have the right to remain silent! Everything you say can and will be used against you in a court of law! Tee hee, now surrender peacefully, Commander!
name: Hot on Your Trail

desc: Tadah! I've got a banquet dress! Heehee~ I decided to go with something refined and voguish this time, as opposed to cute! I mean, it's a dress fit for a banquet, so I think it makes me look pretty grown-up.
name: A Different Dance

desc: Big brother...? I was just practicing my trumpet, if you were wondering... Umm, what do you think? I hope you like my trumpeting...
name: Blissful Movement

desc: Don't come any closer! Th-this is dangerous... Big brother?! Thank goodness... Please come save me!
name: Snow White Guardian Angel

desc: Phew... *pant*... Big brother! F-fight on! Seeing you try your very hardest reminds me... that I need to do my best to cheer you on, too!
name: Champion of Unicorn

desc: Commander, come and try this cake I made... Oh? Heehee, of course I know. That's the ring that symbolizes our eternal vow. I promise to cherish both you and the ring forever...
name: Sweet Afternoon Teatime

desc: Light cruiser – Neptune.
name: Neptune

desc: Hehe~ I usually let the other girls have all the glory, but even I must sometimes give you something to remember me by. Merry Christmas, Commander~
name: Princess of the Reindeers

desc: Welcome to our celebration, Commander. At this breathtaking venue, I, Neptune, shall be the one to show you around, rather than the Royal Maids. Heehee~♪
name: Nereid's Invitation

desc: Step aside, officer comin' through! Oh, here already, advisor? Did you find any good clues? ...No? Heheh, watch and see how the pros do it!
name: Officer Bunneptune Is on the Case!

desc: Battleship – Monarch.
name: Monarch

desc: Hmph. One's outfit is merely superficial. True nobility must come from within. Don't you agree, Commander?
name: White Warrick

desc: So, an Eastern outfit this time... Hmph. My nobility is evident regardless of what I wear. However, since you prepared this outfit especially for me, it would be unbecoming of me to not express my gratitude. Thank you.
name: Black Gerard

desc: This common thief – calls herself "PhantoM" – is running circles around the Metropolitan Police. Now they've come to me for help... Bet they never thought this day would come when they demoted me to the sticks. On the bright side, we get to detect side by side again.
name: Detective Arriving on the Scene

desc: Whew... Surely now one can argue that I'm "enjoying the beach," yes? ...Still not enough? I am laying my exposed self bare before you – what more is there I need to do?
name: Sovereign of the Beach

desc: Heavy cruiser – Cheshire.
name: Cheshire

desc: Cheer up, Owner! Jeez, why are you so bummed out when we're at the beach... Because it's just a normal playdate instead of a romantic date? What's the difference anyway? C'mon, let's go head down to where the others are~!
name: Summery Date!

desc: I'll sing a song for you, Owner~ Ahem... Wait, I'm not sure I know any Dragon Empery songs, actually...
name: Cait Sith Crooner

desc: "Owner~ I've come to take you to the ball~" ...That's exactly what you were going to do? Eh, doesn't matter who does it~ All that matters is we'll be there together~♪
name: The Cat and the White Steed

desc: Owneeer! Lookie! You'll be spending the night with a magician – me! What's the matter? Are you already head over paws for my new look? Don't think I didn't notice how you can't take your eyes off me!
name: The Cat in the Magic Hat

desc: Owneeer! Look, look! I've got my wedding dress on! Isn't it frilly and floaty and just so cute? I'll bet you love me so much right now you can't think straight! Heehee♡
name: White Seaside Melody

desc: Heavy cruiser – Drake.
name: Drake

desc: Phew... Swimming like this doesn't feel all that refreshing... Hey, how about you stop staring and come join me?
name: The Golden Hind's Respite

desc: Light Cruiser—Plymouth
name: Plymouth

desc: Rejoice, Commander. I have no doubt that this refreshing sensation will bring you the utmost satisfaction. Come, let us enjoy this experience together.
name: Heart-Throbbing Refreshment

desc: Special type I {namecode:2} Destroyer Class— {namecode:2}
name: Fubuki

desc: Oh no! I-I'm gonna be late for school! Y-you need to speed up too, doggy! *Pant*... *pant*... Why'd none of my sisters wake me up before they left?!
name: 5 Minutes Till I'm Late

desc: "C-come on in! We've got special offers for you!" ... W-wait, is this really what a "sexy mascot" would wear? It feels pretty different from what I was expecting... And boy, is it stuffy in this thing...
name: Mascot Bucky

desc: Check it out, Commander! What do you think? ... No, not my dress! I'm talking about the tuba! Want me to play a tune for you~?
name: Music Pixy

desc: The whole world's going to feel the tremors from my debut! I'm Fubuki, the Special-type idol!
name: Fubuki Halation!

desc: Welcome, welcome! Oh, Commander! I've actually started working here part-time, but I'm still learning— Wooah?! Phew... Th-that was a close one...
name: Stormy Waitress-in-Training!

desc: C-Commander?! Aw, shoot... I, uh, can't explain this in just one sentence... Please, just help me!
name: Caught Under the Lights

desc: Special Type I-class destroyer number two – Shirayuki.
name: Shirayuki

desc: Whoa now! There's enough food for everyone, so don't fight over it! ...Commander? Don't just stand there, give me a hand, please!
name: Bunny Breeder

desc: Special Type I Fubuki-class destroyer number four – Miyuki.
name: Miyuki

desc: Commander, I think the goods over here are a bit cheaper... Umm, I'm doing fine on my budget still, so we can pick out some more things to buy. A-also, I'll get to spend more time shopping with you... Ah, d-disregard that please... *blushes*
name: Shopping Rendezvous

desc: C-Commander, I'm ready any time... You think my outfit's cute...? Th-thank you... Heheh, I got it just for our date... Umm, I figured hiding my bandages might help ward off my bad luck...
name: Clear Skies and Crepes

desc: First ship of special Type II {namecode:6} class destroyers, {namecode:6}.
name: Ayanami

desc: I heard that... I need to wear a costume like this to participate in Halloween festivities. Commander... do I look cute?
name: Witch in Ambush

desc: Commander, want to listen to music together? Do you like... this non-combat-oriented Ayanami?
name: Rock 'n' Demon

desc: Compared to the way we celebrate New Year in the Sakura Empire, the festivities of the Dragon Empery have a completely different atmosphere... But, I don't really mind the liveliness... Commander, do you like festivals?
name: Lunar Demon

desc: "Welcome, Commander..." I should greet customers like this... yes?
name: Grade A Sailor Uniform

desc: Ayanami here. Successfully infiltrated Commander's office. Oh... Commander saw me. Operation failed...
name: Covert Ops Cloak

desc: I guess I'm making my idol debut? Um, Javelin and the others are making their debuts, so, I also had to... Commander, what are idols supposed to do normally?
name: Low-Key Idol @Confused

desc: This dress is... {namecode:6}’s. I'm not used to this dress yet... Commander, do you think it fits me?
name: Demon's Finest Dress

desc: Ayanami, retrofit complete. I feel stronger, yes... Having that said, Commander, can you pat my head? I want to be spoiled a bit...
name: Ayanami (Retrofit)

desc: Type III {namecode:11}-class destroyer number one - {namecode:11}.
name: Akatsuki

desc: Is this the place called the Northern Parliament?! It is colder than I thought... Th-thank goodness I brought gear for extreme environments! Hibiki, please wait a bit longer! Your sister is coming to see you!
name: Akatsuki Goes North

desc: What do you think, Commander? I have a brand new outfit and a brand new companion! I am no longer a plain old ninja... I am now a motoninja!
name: Motoninja Akatsuki

desc: Look out! Move, Commander! ...Phew. To explain, I am helping Santa give out Christmas presents! Now excuse me, I cannot tarry here or I'll be late... Wait, have I come to the wrong place? WHAT?!
name: Santa's Lost Helper!

desc: Welcome, Commander, to DesDiv 6's tent of entertainment! For our first act, I shall perform for you my most stunning ninjutsu! ..."Circus"? I've never heard of this word before!
name: Cirque de Ninjutsu!

desc: Type III Akatsuki-class destroyer number two – Hibiki.
name: Hibiki

desc: New Year's finally comes to port! I, Hibiki of the 6th DesDiv, will be marking my new arrival in my New Year's attire! Commander, don't you dare change the channel - you've gotta watch my every move~!
name: New Year's Little Imp

desc: Type III Akatsuki-class destroyer number three - Ikazuchi.
name: Ikazuchi

desc: {namecode:13}, {namecode:13} has been transformed into tea! What should we do! {namecode:14} and {namecode:13} will get slurped up by the Commander!
name: Sakura Tea

desc: Inazuma and I have been to a lot of festivals together, but this would be the first time that I've gone with you, Commander. Isn't this totally like a date?
name: Thunderous Festival

desc: I'm the fairy of thunder that shatters the night to herald the dawn! I see, I see! That is a good backstory! Commander, want to head to the party together?
name: Dawn's Thunder

desc: Commander, I've worn what you asked me to– Oh, I see, I see. So this is what they call a "maid kink," right? Is that what you're into now, Commander?
name: Courtyard Maid Ikazuchi

desc: Type III Akatsuki-class destroyer number four - Inazuma.
name: Inazuma

desc: It doesn’t matter if {namecode:14} becomes Mr. Commander's dessert… but if {namecode:14} cannot be found, Mr. Commander will feel so devastated, perhaps he won’t be able to command the fleet… so… please! Please convey {namecode:14}'s heartfelt wish to Mr. Commander——
name: Vanilla Pudding

desc: I usually go to festivals with Ikazuchi, but this would be my first time going with you. Hmm? Where should we visit first?
name: Flash of Fireworks

desc: I'm the fairy of lightning that illuminates the stars in the night sky... So that's what we're going with, huh. Commander, will you accompany me to the party?
name: Dusk's Lightning

desc: One, two... Mm. All done, Commander. Yep... I'll be your maid today. I don't know how to do much other than make flower arrangements, but I can stay by your side all day.
name: Maid's Flower Offering

desc: {namecode:15}-class destroyer number one - {namecode:15}.
name: Shiratsuyu

desc: H-here they come... Your order, and your cutesy dutesy maid... Whoaahh! I'm sorry! Look out!
name: Is The Order A Torpedo?

desc: Owwie, I fell again... Huh? You fell, too? Just because you wanted to help me up? *sniffle*... I'm sorry...
name: Thawing Snow, Fireworks Alight

desc: Shiratsuyu, the first ship of the Shiratsuyu-class... has been retrofitted. I feel like I've grown a lot, so I think I can meet your... Expectations? Hopes? Umm... I'm not sure how to word this best...
name: Shiratsuyu (Retrofit)

desc: {namecode:15}-class destroyer number four - {namecode:16}.
name: Yuudachi

desc: Come out of your office, Commander! You'll become lazy if you huddle up next to the heater all day! Let's go out and play in the snow!
name: Shogun of Snowballs

desc: Commander, look at me, look at me! What do you think of my new outfit? If you like it, wanna give it a feel?
name: Carnivore Carnival!

desc: Christmas! The day Santa Claus drops by and leaves presents, right? Hell yeah, I'm pumped! Aren't you pumped too, Commander?
name: Woofy Floofy Christmas Night

desc: Commander, look! Look at this new dress. Red and white, I really really like it! But what's the occasion?
name: The Bride of Solomon

desc: Woof...? Am I imagining it, or did you get shorter, Commander? Unless... it's me who's gotten bigger? Seriously?! Nobody told me retrofitting makes you taller!
name: Yuudachi (Retrofit)

desc: {namecode:15}-class destroyer number two - {namecode:17}.
name: Shigure

desc: Stupid Commander, I'm not a damn submarine! Do you wanna get hit in the face with an oxygen torpedo?
name: Attack, I-490!

desc: Oh my. Commander, you must be pretty lucky to bump into me here, hehe~ Since you're here, you can have the privilege of being my escort tonight. Now, be grateful~♪
name: The Ballroom's Lucky Star

desc: All right, that should be good... Hey, stupid Commander standing around aimlessly. Yeah, you. Stick your hand out. You're gonna be the first person to get MY chocolate, so I'd better see some tears of gratitude.
name: Lucky Chocolate

desc: Heheh~ Retrofitting the mighty Shigure proves that you are quite perceptive! Aren't you glad that you get to rely on me more, you lucky idiot of a commander~♪
name: Shigure (Retrofit)

desc: Kagerou-class Destroyer no. 8 - Yukikaze
name: Yukikaze

desc: Wa ha ha! My "universal-as-long-as-there-is-a-ceiling" swing set is finally complete! Commander, are you jealous? Want to give it a try? Too~ bad~! This seat is reserved only for the noble and elegant Yukikaze!
name: Sovereign of the Swing

desc: Wa ha ha~! Did your heart skip a beat from seeing the charming Yukikaze? Hmph... Well, looks like the Dragon Empery girls are setting off firecrackers... let's go join them! Here, make sure to hold on to my hand!
name: Winter's Snowy Wind

desc: This outfit is sooo cute~ ehehe... Ack!! *cough* *cough*! Ahem! From now on, you are the faithful companion of Yukikaze the Great! As such, you will not be permitted to leave my side, understood?
name: The Warmth of Spring

desc: {namecode:19}-class destroyer number one - {namecode:19}.
name: Kagerou

desc: Commander, trick or treat! I expect you to give some candy to my sisters as well! These will-o'-wisps? Hahaha~ I tried imitating that gloomy sister of mine!
name: Pumpkins and Festivities!

desc: The newly-retrofitted Kagerou has arrived~ I won't let that sister of mine pass me up anymore! Commander, lead us forward towards distant shores!
name: Kagerou (Retrofit)

desc: {namecode:19}-class destroyer number two - {namecode:20}.
name: Shiranui

desc: I see a chance... to capitalize on the Dragon Empery's famous mooncakes... Commander, would you like to have a taste of the Moon Palace's delicacies? If you buy them in bulk, I'll give you a special discount.
name: Mooncake Merchant

desc: If you have this much money remaining... then you may visit me and spend it with confidence... A discount, you say...? Of course... Someday, I shall give you one...
name: Shiranui (Retrofit)

desc: {namecode:19}-class destroyer number fifteen - {namecode:24}.
name: Nowaki

desc: {namecode:30}-class destroyer number one – {namecode:30}.
name: Hatsuharu

desc: Everyone's playing together...? I-I think I'll pass... Y-you want me to join them? Ugh, well, if you say so, then I-I-I'll try to socialize with them...!
name: Snow Day Hatsuharu

desc: C-Commander, I will be your partner for the party tonight. Let's see, umm... I believe this is proper Royal Navy etiquette... D-did I do it correctly?
name: Hatsuharu in the Limelight

desc: U-umm... In order to conquer shyness, umm, I've come to serve you... I just hope I don't get in everyone's way... Y-yeah! Thank you for your encouraging words! I'll do my best...!
name: Hatsuharu's Cat Café Caper

desc: Hatsuharu, retrofit complete... H-hopefully I'm a little bit stronger now...
name: Hatsuharu (Retrofit)

desc: Hatsuharu-class destroyer number three – Wakaba.
name: Wakaba

desc: Yaho~ Good morning, Commander! For a limited time only, Wakaba Claus will be delivering Christmas presents! Huh? My bag? Aaahhh! C-Commander, help me pick everything up!
name: Holiday Special Wakaba!

desc: Hmmgh! Oh yeah... Ah, there you are, Commander! Care to join me? Come bask in the afternoon sunshine, it feels great!
name: A Healthy Dose of Sunshine!

desc: Hatsuharu-class Destroyer, number 4 - Hatsushimo
name: Hatsushimo

desc: Cheers, Commander~ C'mere, you've got to enjoy the party too! If you're thinking of doing something tactless like running off to go back to work, people are going to get upset with you~
name: Perennial Joy

desc: Hatsushimo's retrofitting is complete. You don't think I look all that different? Oh, Commander, you're still as simple as ever~ I've changed in tons of ways beyond what's just on the surface. Heheheh~
name: Hatsushimo (Retrofit)

desc: Hatsuharu-class destroyer no. 5 - Ariake
name: Ariake

desc: Hope everyone enjoys the oodles of balloons I made for this party! Yeah, I'm sure the little girls will love 'em!
name: Unending Friendship

desc: Ah... So this is what it feels like to be retrofitted. I'll work harder for your sake, and for everyone in the 27th Destroyer Division~
name: Ariake (Retrofit)

desc: Sixth ship of {namecode:30} class Destroyer— {namecode:32}
name: Yuugure

desc: "I, Yuugure the maid, shall dedicate myself to Ariake, my sister, and you, Commander!"... Eek?! M-my skirt...!
name: Maid-In-Training!

desc: The Dragon Empery's New Year celebrations and new outfits are sure to lift everyone's spirits~ My sister will probably love this new dress as well. Commander, what do you think?
name: Twilight Blossom

desc: I finished changing, Commander. This dress is very pretty, but... isn't it missing something up top?
name: Evening Flower

desc: Woah... These stalls have all sorts of amazing things~ Commander, will you help me pick a gift out for Ariake? Hm, let's see... How about this Daruma doll?
name: Summer Festival Shopping

desc: I was really looking forward to playing with you at the beach, Commander, so I changed into this swimsuit. Umm... Ariake told me that I had to choose something that was easy to move around in, and cute enough to make you lose your mind... Was she pulling my leg?
name: Fun in the Sun

desc: Ariake-class destroyer, Yuugure, has completed retrofitting. Ehehe, from now on... Ariake and I will be in your care once more, Commander.
name: Yuugure (Retrofit)

desc: Kagerou-class destroyer number three – Kuroshio.
name: Kuroshio

desc: Kagerou-class destroyer number four – Oyashio.
name: Oyashio

desc: Shimakaze-class destroyer – Shimakaze.
name: Shimakaze

desc: Hippity hoppity! Grab a glass and have a sippity! Whew, I must say, this outfit was tricky to get into. Still, you made an exquisite pick, Commander!
name: World's Speediest Bunny Waitress

desc: Whoa-whoa-whoa! Why'd I end up here again?! Even though I've been running for a whole hour! ...Commander?! Waaaah, I'm so glad to see you! Please, help me get out of heeeeeeere!
name: The White Rabbit of Wonderland

desc: You can't keep sprinting across the sea forever. Sometimes, you need to rest and recover your strength. Speaking of, you may use my parasol if you like, Commander!
name: The Island Wind Rests

desc: Oh no! Commander, look out! ...Phew. That was really close. Apologies for my clear lack of attentiveness! I shouldn't have been in such a rush to deliver all these mooncakes...
name: Clumsy Moon Rabbit

desc: So I need only lie down and stay still in order to win? Alright... Then allow me to demonstrate my persistence to you!
name: The Unmoving Rabbit

desc: {namecode:124}-class destroyer number one – {namecode:124}.
name: Kamikaze

desc: Ohohoho, you must have a sharp eye if you've decided to retrofit me~ Now that I've been chosen, I cannot afford to embarrass you. Now, take a good and thorough look at this veteran's aspirations~
name: Kamikaze (Retrofit)

desc: Kamikaze-class destroyer number four – Matsukaze.
name: Matsukaze

desc: There we go... My fan is too big, and I'm not used to carrying it around yet... Ah, right, come here for a sec, Commander~ I'll fan you with some cool air~ Come on now, no need to be shy~
name: Matsukaze (Retrofit)

desc: {namecode:33}-class destroyer number one – {namecode:33}.
name: Mutsuki

desc: Commander, Merry Christmas~! I am on my best behavior today as well! Uuu... when is Santa Claus going to come? I'm sleepy...
name: Mr. Reindeer, Depart!

desc: Comainder, I put on my yukata just like you said! Ehehe, you should take me to the festival so I can get lots and lots of candy!
name: Candy Festival!

desc: I heard that if I go around telling people "Happy New Year," I can get lots of goodies! Ehehe, I hope they'll give me a bunch of candy!
name: Spring Festival Sweets

desc: Comainder, you gotta keep up! We still have to eat cake and hot dogs, ride the teacups, go to the haunted house, and... what else was there? Hehe, anyway, let's hold hands and get going!♪
name: Cotton Candy Dreams

desc: Comainder, I'm done retrofitting! Have some candy! Hm? You're always nice to me, so I'm giving you some candy!
name: Mutsuki (Retrofit)

desc: {namecode:33}-class destroyer number two – {namecode:34}.
name: Kisaragi

desc: Co... commander, {namecode:34}'s new outfit... How does it look? It's a new year... {namecode:34} wants to keep improving...
name: New Year's Wish

desc: Kisaragi... retrofitting complete... I want to be able to help everyone out more...
name: Kisaragi (Retrofit)

desc: The fourth ship of {namecode:33} class destroyer — {namecode:137}
name: Uzuki

desc: Ah... Big sis {namecode:34}, big sis {namecode:33}, let's sleep together... Commander? You want to come too?
name: Sleepy Uzuki

desc: Mutsuki-class destroyer number six – Minazuki.
name: Minazuki

desc: Mutsuki-class Destroyer number seven – Fumizuki.
name: Fumizuki

desc: Huh...? Where am I...? What time is it...?
name: Sleepy Fairy

desc: Mutsuki-class destroyer number eight – Nagatsuki.
name: Nagatsuki

desc: Nagatsuki the kitty maid is at your service~ Do your best to not fall madly in love with my cute looks~! Hehe~
name: Dangerous Kitty Maid?

desc: Mutsuki-class destroyer number ten – Mikazuki.
name: Mikazuki

desc: Mikazuki is supposed to be... a jiangshi? Um... hip... hop... Commander, trick or treaaaaat~
name: Sweet Zombie

desc: Shiratsuyu-class destroyer number seven – Umikaze.
name: Umikaze

desc: What's the matter, Commander? Oh, this outfit? ...Um, I heard that this outfit would bring you therapeutic benefits and hoped to try it on... Wh-what do you think? Does it feel therapeutic to you?
name: Soft and Fluffy Therapy

desc: Commander, it is my pleasure to accompany you today. Umm... What do you think? I decided to go for a different outfit this time... D-do you think it's cute?
name: Baby Steps

desc: Shiratsuyu-class destroyer number eight – Yamakaze.
name: Yamakaze

desc: Voilà! Don't go anywhere, Commander! My magic show will start in just a sec! To start with, let's hear a roar! Roooaar!
name: Now for a Magic Trick!

desc: Shiratsuyu-class destroyer number nine – Kawakaze.
name: Kawakaze

desc: Mhm. Lightweight clothing makes it easier to fight. Thanks, Commander... "It looks cute on me"? W-well, thanks...
name: Monochromatic Interlude

desc: ...Oh, it's you. This is a forbidden area, so even you can't... Okay, and you're coming in anyway. Hmm. Not sure what to do about this...
name: Guardian Fox, Forever Loyal

desc: This must be the dream you've awaited so eagerly... Of course, I vowed to be with you until the end of our days. I shall take my rightful place beside you and your ideals. We are... together.
name: Unsullied White Fox

desc: Yuugumo-class destroyer – Kiyonami.
name: Kiyonami

desc: S-sorry to keep you waiting... Yuugure and I picked out this outfit together. She said it "looked very Christmassy," but it doesn't look weird, right? ... Ugh...
name: Festive Riding Hood?

desc: {namecode:26}-class destroyer number five – {namecode:125}.
name: Niizuki

desc: Akizuki-class destroyer number nine – Harutsuki.
name: Harutsuki

desc: Happy New Year, Commander! I am currently on my way to give a Kagura dance at the shrine. If you have time... would you like to come see it?
name: A Dance for the Coming Spring

desc: C-Commander! Over here! Take a seat right here, please! Breathe in, relax... Okay, you're all ready! I'll cleanse you right away!
name: Little Steamy Sprite

desc: Akizuki-class destroyer number ten – Yoizuki.
name: Yoizuki

desc: It's my turn? Hold on... Umm, could you please not stare at me like that? It's... making me feel uncomfortable.
name: Sports Festival Preparations

desc: Mmh... Happy New Year. I'm working on hooking my friends up with these firecrackers... The bun I'm eating? I received it as a thank-you for my efforts.
name: Firecrackers and Steamed Buns

desc: The 11th Destroyer of {namecode:19} class — {namecode:142}
name: Urakaze

desc: Before you raise a fuss about it, let me just tell you this - the concept of "Christmas" already existed during the Sengoku period, so there's nothing weird about putting on a Christmas outfit!
name: Seasonal Shogun

desc: Ugh... Even though we finally got all our gear, we still need more band members... Commander! Stop complaining and come hither! From now on, you're a member of the Sengoku Shredders!
name: Sengoku☆Shredder!

desc: Kagerou-class destroyer number twelve – Isokaze.
name: Isokaze

desc: General, General, look! It's my New Year's outfit! Urakaze made it for me! Let's play a bunch of Sengoku wargames this year as well!
name: New Year's Campaign

desc: General! I, Isokaze, have done my utmost to prepare the equipment! Now, with Lord Urakaze's presence, our Sengoku☆War-Band is complete! Of course, you are more than welcome to join our ranks, General!
name: Sengoku☆Smasher!

desc: Tenth ship of {namecode:19} class destroyers, {namecode:128}.
name: {namecode:128}

desc: Learning is exciting. The joy of acquiring new knowledge, the sense of achievement from solving difficult problems... you'll understand once you try it. So, shall we study together, Commander?
name: The Honors Student

desc: I'm experimenting with different flavors since we're running a pop-up café... Alright! I think I'll go with this one! Strap in, Commander, because you're about to do a lot of taste-testing!
name: The Secret Ingredient is Love?!

desc: Commander, have you been having more fun since I arrived? ... I see, that's great! Ehehe... Hamakaze, getting hyped!
name: Hamakaze (Retrofit)

desc: Kagerou-class destroyer number fourteen – Tanikaze.
name: Tanikaze

desc: Little butterfly, little butterfly... Ya! It flew away... {namecode:128}~ {namecode:128}~ Where are you? {namecode:142}? {namecode:143}? We said we were going to play at the seaside. Where is everyone?
name: Lost Girl and Labyrinth Butterfly

desc: Commander, I'm mopping the floor right now. Please watch your step, as it's quite slippery over there... Eek! Owch... I suppose I should've watched my own step... Ahaha...
name: Sparkly-Clean

desc: I'm {namecode:127}, blowing and blustering from the mountaintop! Whoa! Butterflies? Butterflies?! Look, butterflies! For me? Thanks, Commander!
name: {namecode:127} (Retrofit)

desc: Asashio-class destroyer number one – Asashio.
name: Asashio

desc: My name is Asashio, and I just transferred here today. Pleased to meet you... Even though I might not be able to get caught up with the course work, Mr. Kitty and I will do our best.
name: The Transfer Student Underneath the Dancing Petals

desc: Happy New Year, Commander. I am here to spend the New Year with you. Would you be so kind as to first help me down from here?
name: Snow-Dusted Lynx Tips

desc: Commander, thank you for coming to see me. I'm currently rehearsing my program for the Spring Festival performance. I do hope it is to your liking.
name: Robes of Dancing Clouds

desc: Asashio-class destroyer number two – Ooshio.
name: Ooshio

desc: Merry Christmas~ Commander, we gotta go hand out presents to them destroyers~ You be Santa, I'll be yer reindeer~
name: The Reindeer's Present

desc: Happy anniversary~ Today's a day to enjoy to yer heart's content, ya know? I'm just havin' fun in my own way, checkin' out cute girls from afar~ I appreciate yer concern though, Commander~
name: Woozy Party

desc: Should I hang this "fortune" poster here...? Oh, Commander, did ya also want a Spring Festival present from Ooshio here? Just kiddin'~ Hehe, anyway, happy Lunar New Year~
name: Bringer of Fortunes

desc: Finally we're through with them mornin' classes~ Commander, would ya fancy havin' lunch with me? Heheh, yer wonderin' what I done made? You'll see for yerself soon 'nuff~
name: Let's 'ave Lunch

desc: Third ship of {namecode:145} class destroyers, {namecode:147}.
name: Michishio

desc: Hello, Commander. Oh, you think I look good in this fluttery dress~? Thank you very much!
name: Fluttering Fanfare

desc: Asashio-class destroyer number four – Arashio.
name: Arashio

desc: Looks like you found me, Commander. Hehe, want to light some fireworks with me? Spending time together should be more fun than being alone, right?
name: The Gentlest Firework

desc: Special Type I-class destroyer number 10 – Uranami.
name: Uranami

desc: It's snowing...! I've finished rallying the forces... so let us advance!
name: Snow Vanguard

desc: Kamikaze-class destroyer number five – Hatakaze.
name: Hatakaze

desc: Yuugumo-class destroyer number five – Makinami.
name: Makinami

desc: All right, everything looks good! I'm super excited and my batteries are fully charged! I'm heading out~!
name: Time for School!

desc: Asashio-class destroyer number 10 – Kasumi.
name: Kasumi

desc: Warm and comforting clothes... Warm and comforting red bean soup... Ahh, I love New Year's.
name: New Year's Comfort

desc: Kasumi and Foo are excited about the new semester. Are you too, Commander?
name: At School with Foo

desc: Kasumi thinks that her outfit has gotten a bit breezier. Foo said the same thing.
name: Kasumi (Retrofit)

desc: Akizuki-class destroyer number thirteen – Hanazuki.
name: Hanazuki

desc: I've heard some say that summer is the season of cherry blossoms, lotus petals, and sunflowers, but... If you ask me, being able to leisurely enjoy the breeze with you feels pretty good too. Hehe~
name: Morning Moon, Beachside Flower

desc: What kinds of flowers should I decorate the office with for the Lunar New Year...? Ugh, I just can't decide! Um, Commander, will you be inspecting the interior? I'll show you around! Phew...
name: Blossoming Spring, Resplendent Moon

desc: Yuugumo-class destroyer number four – Naganami.
name: Naganami

desc: Akashi pushed me into getting this outfit, saying that it would surely make you happy, but... What do you think...?
name: Long Waves of Happiness

desc: There's still some time before the banquet begins, and I'm afraid I'm feeling a little sleepy... W-would you mind if I took a nap? Thank you...
name: Long-Awaited Warmth

desc: I wanted to help you relieve some stress, so I thought I would read some folk tales to you... When I mentioned that, Akashi suggested these clothes to me... Wh-what do you think?
name: Nestling Up for the Long Nights

desc: Commander? You stopped eating. Does it taste too bitter...? Oh no, if you don't like the chocolate I made, I... I-I can still make you happy in other ways!
name: Heartmelting Warmth

desc: Now that the big day is here, I'm awfully nervous... I-I'll be in your care now and forever, okay?
name: Waves of Eternal Love

desc: Akizuki-class destroyer number three – Suzutsuki.
name: Suzutsuki

desc: Commander, over here! We're about to start without you! Ahaha, what would you like to do, Commander? Beach volleyball? Sandcastle building? We can also go relax in the water if you'd like!
name: Suzutsuki, Beachside Attendant!

desc: I, Akizuki-class destroyer, Suzutsuki, shall not allow you to pass through these arches! Hwuh?! I missed the return again...!
name: Suzutsuki, Hanetsuki Adept!

desc: Kamikaze-class destroyer number six – Oite.
name: Oite

desc: Commander, have you also come to play on the beach? You're telling me to be careful? Hmph, what misfortune could possibly befall me from a game of watermelon splitting... Gwaah?!
name: Summer Dedication

desc: Happy New Year to you, Commander. To celebrate the season, I had these garments tailor-made for me, using traditional Dragon Empery clothes as a basis. I don't look... childish, do I?
name: Jet Ink, Silver Quills

desc: Yuugumo-class destroyer number three – Kazagumo.
name: Kazagumo

desc: Toot~♪ Oh, Commander, did you hear me practicing my recorder? Umm, I'd appreciate it if you didn't tell the others.
name: After-School Melody

desc: *lick*... Oh, Commander, y-you're here for the fireworks? ...Want to watch them with me, then? I've got drinks. My ice cream? Umm... You can't have it.
name: Placid Waves, Passionate Heart

desc: I'm doing lots of training. Gardening, making tea, stuff like that. Here's an example... Umm, do you want dinner, or a bath, or... Hm? I shouldn't practice that one?
name: Diligent Domestic Discipline

desc: Akizuki-class destroyer number six – Wakatsuki.
name: Wakatsuki

desc: Oh nooo! Look out, Commander! ...Oh, phew... I'm glad I didn't mess up your clothes because of my carelessness! Please forgive me for my blunder! I'll clean the floor up right away!
name: Slapdash Blue Sparrow

desc: Blue Sparrow Wakatsuki is here! ...Commander, why are you just staring—Oh, no! I'm caught on the curtain... Aaaah!
name: Blue Sparrow Heralding Spring

desc: Akizuki-class destroyer – Hatsuzuki.
name: Hatsuzuki

desc: Peace~♪ Do I look good in the pic? Don't I look so adorable you'll never wanna delete the photo, and have to stare at it every day to feel at ease? Heehee♪
name: August's First Romance

desc: You said anything's fine as long as I think it's good, right? Well, tadah! I'm going to give you a delectable, delicious drink! Watch closely now!
name: Luxurious Celebration Time

desc: Kamikaze-class destroyer – Asanagi.
name: Asanagi

desc: *yaaawn*... Goodness me, there I go falling asleep. You understand how pleasant the sea breeze is, don't you? YOU calling ME a slacker!
name: Lulled by Rough Seas

desc: Yuugumo-class destroyer – Suzunami
name: Suzunami

desc: Sorry for calling you here this early, Commander... I was just hoping you could check if I'm wearing my dress right. I'm not a dress person, so...
name: Winter Beauty's Ball Gown

desc: Yuugumo-class destroyer – Taekaze.
name: Taekaze

desc: Aaah, I'm gonna faaall! H-heheh... Morning, Commander... I-I'm just, uh, training right now! I wasn't trying to surprise you, or anything.
name: Kunoichi's Emergency Landing

desc: Yuugumo-class destroyer – Fujinami.
name: Fujinami

desc: Welcome to Fujinami's secret fashion lab~ Look, I put together a special ensemble just for you. So, what do you think? Pretty eye-popping, isn't it?
name: Secret Fashion Show For You

desc: Yuubari-class light cruiser – Yuubari.
name: Yuubari

desc: I've finally finished developing my new equipment! Since we still have time, let's go and try it out in live combat right now, Master!
name: Yuubari (Retrofit)

desc: First ship of the {namecode:46}-class light cruisers, {namecode:46}.
name: Nagara

desc: Good evening, Commander. This room...? Ah, it's a special Dragon Empery-themed set I bought from Akashi's. It looks pretty snazzy and was on sale, so I picked it up. Ehehe~
name: Spring Breeze Leisure

desc: Second ship of the {namecode:46}-class light cruisers, {namecode:48}.
name: Isuzu

desc: There will be lots and lots of ghosts and spirits during Halloween... I, I’m not afraid!... say, can, can you hold my hand?
name: Night of Fairy Tale

desc: Commander? I only came here to help wrap up all the presents for tomorrow, n-not because the fireplace is too cozy and I don't want to get up...
name: Cozy Christmas Eve

desc: Wooah! ...I fell down again... But at least it's cooler now... Huh? A photoshoot? Noo, don't take a picture of me~
name: Accidental Overheat?
