desc: W-w-woah! W-wait up! You guys are going too fast! I'm gonna fall! I'm gonna faaaaall! You're supposed to carry me in a way that doesn't give me a heart attack!! Commander, something crazy seems to have happened with my cavalry~!!
name: Charge, My Trusty Steeds!

desc: Retrofit complete! ...Umm, Commander? ...Wh-what's the matter? Do I really look that different...?!
name: Isuzu (Retrofit)

desc: Nagara-class light cruiser – Natori.
name: Natori

desc: Mmfhuhu~♡ What's the matter, Commander? Enraptured by my charms? Heehee, you're frozen in place! You can't begin to think of how to compliment me, can you? "Enough staring, out with the compliments!"
name: Beach Paradise

desc: Heheh♪ The brightest star in the venue, she with the power to shake the earth – none other than Natori, of course! Go on, Commander, and kneel before me~ "Nuo ho ho, even the whippersnapper is amazed!"
name: Boisterous Night on the Cruise

desc: Nagara-class light cruiser number four – Yura.
name: Yura

desc: Uh... I think these clothes are a bit too much... Commander, I... don't look out of place in these, do I...?
name: We are Succubi?

desc: I'm Kinu. If you want this demon to do your bidding, then you'd better show me what you're capable of!
name: Kinu

desc: Grr! What are you here for? Speak up. ...Oh, you just wanted to take a tour of the club activities? Sorry 'bout that, I don't like getting disturbed in the middle of this kind of training.
name: New Year's Blade Demon

desc: Well? I've still got one card in my hand. If you want to win, then show me everything you've got! I will not have you disrespect me just for wearing a silly costume!
name: Token and Ghost

desc: Retrofit complete... Look forward to commanding the might of the demon ascended. I shall not disappoint you!
name: Kinu (Retrofit)

desc: Sixth ship of the {namecode:46}-class light cruisers, {namecode:47}.
name: Abukuma

desc: Combat retrofit complete! First Torpedo Squadron flagship, Abukuma, ready to sortie any time!
name: Abukuma (Retrofit)

desc: Mogami-class Heavy Cruiser no. 1 - Mogami
name: Mogami

desc: Are you sure this is a retrofit and not some weird hazing ritual? I look... Well, I suppose I do feel stronger. Guess I'll try to work a bit harder. Wouldn't hurt for you to look forward to it a little.
name: Mogami (Retrofit)

desc: Mogami-class heavy cruiser number two – Mikuma.
name: Mikuma

desc: Commander, may you and all our friends enjoy peace and good health... Alright, what did you think? That was a ceremonial dance I'd like to offer to everyone at the main event.
name: Offerings of Floral Grace

desc: Sendai-class light cruiser number one – Sendai.
name: Sendai

desc: Hmh. Guess I won't be needin' these bandages anymore. Commander, how about we find out how strong I've gotten... by having you take one of my punches?
name: Sendai (Retrofit)

desc: Sendai-class No. 2 light cruiser, Jintsuu.
name: Jintsuu

desc: Hmm? Is it unusual? Hah. Even I require a change of pace to clear my mind every so often. Commander, why don’t you come out and get some fresh air as well?
name: The Tactician's Vacation

desc: "Where do you think you're going so early in the morning, Little Red Riding Hood?" ...Oh, if it isn't the Commander. This might be my own little whim, but I often find myself thinking the same way as this character... If you don't mind, I'd like to hear your feedback about my acting.
name: The Gray Wolf's Ploy

desc: Since I've gotten used to living with you, Commander, I've decided to be more laid-back after receiving my remodel. My dance? Hehe... I can't show that to just anyone so easily.
name: Jintsuu (Retrofit)

desc: Sendai-class light cruiser number three – Naka.
name: Naka

desc: Ahaha! Another big one's coming~! Phew~ that felt amazing~! Ah, Commander, let's hit the waves together, shall we?
name: Foxy Summer Surfer

desc: Agano-class light cruiser number one – Agano.
name: Agano

desc: Even though I'm not really into this whole "Christmas" thing, if it means I get to toy around with your heart by wearing this cute outfit of mine, then I suppose I would be interested. Hehe~
name: Christmas Eve Tease

desc: "Oh my, you're also out for a stroll? Hehe, my name's Agano. And what might yours be?" ...Jeez, Commander, take this more seriously. According to the setting, we just met for the first time.
name: Dating Game?

desc: The blunt approach is not my style, but I cannot have Noshiro think I only inch my way to success... Oh, I was just talking to myself, Commander. Hehe, so anyway, would you mind being my partner for tonight's party?
name: Blue Butterfly's Confession

desc: Agano-class light cruiser number two – Noshiro.
name: Noshiro

desc: Just as I thought, this is the perfect place for watching fireworks. You came here thinking that too, didn't you?
name: Uncharted Festival Grounds?

desc: Commander, what are you standing around for? Did you also need a change of pace? That makes two of us— Come, there's nothing to be afraid of here.
name: Xanadu's Eventide

desc: Whew... Oh, are you cold by any chance? I have some hot tea for you if you'd like. If you want someone to chat with, I'd be glad to keep you company.
name: Fragrance of the Eastern Snow

desc: Why don't you unwind for a bit before you start reflecting on the day's happenings? I'm sure it'll be far more efficient that way.
name: Cozy Enclave

desc: Welcom...?! What are you doing here? Wait, don't leave—I was just surprised, that's all... Well, what would you like to order?
name: Hold the Ice

desc: ...Take that! Heehee... Ahaha! Phew... I know you don't like admitting defeat, but I got you pretty good there. I might have tried a bit too hard, but I'm pretty sure you were the one who told me to give it my all.
name: Unwinding in the Sunshine

desc: Commander, what do you have planned next...? You want to just relax and enjoy the date? Understood. Umm, let me just try and get a feel for it... Hmm...
name: Dressed-Up Date

desc: Receiving everyone's blessings is truly a deeply moving experience. But for now, let's set everything else aside and partake of our sweet bliss. After all, you're not just a spectator anymore– we're in this ride together, hehe~
name: A Tale of Two Lovers

desc: Agano-class light cruiser number four – Sakawa.
name: Sakawa

desc: Welcome! Heehee, you came because you were just so keen to see me, am I right? Then I've got to make you feel real welcome♪
name: The Colors of Love

desc: Wow, look how far you pursued me. You must have really, reeeally wanted to see me, huh, Commander~? Heheh, want a popsicle?
name: Icy Indulgence

desc: Laaa la-laaa♪ Oh, Commander. Here to see me again? I know you're madly in love and want to watch me practice, but people will think you're weird if you keep coming and going constantly. Heehee♪
name: The Keys of Love

desc: Agano-class ship number two, Noshiro, will now begin the Muse System test. I'll put my all into both my idol work and my mission, so you have no reason to worry.
name: Noshiro μ

desc: Type C44 light cruiser – Watarase.
name: Watarase

desc: Commander! Oh... Umm, perhaps it would be more fitting to address you as "Milord" for this occasion? Since, you know, the two of us have the evening together... Now, if you don't mind, your hand please — Heehee, make sure to sit tight!
name: Garments of Everlasting Magic

desc: Sendai-class light cruiser – Ayase.
name: Ayase

desc: C-Commander?! ...H-huh? It's already p-past the scheduled time? Awawa... B-but, I still haven't finished changing yet... I, umm... P-please give me just a minute!
name: A Glimpse of the Moon Rabbit

desc: Sendai-class light cruiser – Minase.
name: Minase

desc: Mmmm... That was a nice nap. *sniff*... Oh, Commander? I was just practicing meditation. This is the best place for it. Come and join me, if you'd like.
name: Maidenly Meditation

desc: First ship of the {namecode:53}-class heavy cruisers, {namecode:53}.
name: Furutaka

desc: What's wrong, Commander? Why are you staring at me like that? My body? Yes, some things seem to have gotten bigger... Want to take a look?
name: Furutaka (Retrofit)

desc: Second ship of {namecode:53}-class heavy cruisers, {namecode:54}.
name: Kako

desc: Performance upgraded, improvements complete. This way I can finally... *cough* Oh, it's nothing, Commander. I must simply be more strict with you in the future. Are you ready for your psychological examination?
name: Kako (Retrofit)

desc: First ship of the {namecode:55}-class heavy cruisers, {namecode:55}.
name: Aoba

desc: Second ship of the {namecode:55}-class heavy cruisers, {namecode:56}.
name: Kinugasa

desc: Tone-class heavy cruiser number two – Chikuma.
name: Chikuma

desc: Commander, would you like to share a drink... or play a game together? If you win, I'll share some secret intel that you're sure to love.
name: Premium Prize on the Table

desc: First ship of the {namecode:63}-class heavy cruisers, {namecode:63}.
name: Myoukou

desc: Second ship of the {namecode:63}-class heavy cruisers, {namecode:64}.
name: Nachi

desc: Howzit? Now that my retrofit's all done, don't I look even more perfect than before? Maybe now, our ever-so-reserved Commander here will be super impressed by my new abilities~ Wh-what do you mean I've been staying up too late training with my rigging? W-we're not gonna talk about that!
name: Nachi (Retrofit)

desc: Myoukou-class heavy cruiser number three - Ashigara
name: Ashigara

desc: Phew... I finally managed to fix my dress... but I just can't seem to get used to it. Commander, how does my dress look? It's not strange, is it?
name: Brief Intermission

desc: This whole "fashion coordination" concept is still a bit hard for me to wrap my head around, so I'm glad Nachi helped me pick out a swimsuit. Now, I just need to... Hey, Commander! Open your mouth! H-huh?! But this is what Nachi told me to do... is there some sort of problem?!
name: Kaleidoscopic Summer

desc: Myoukou-class heavy cruiser number four – Haguro.
name: Haguro

desc: Ow! That freakin' stings... Can't believe I actually slipped on the stairs and hit my foot. Just how clumsy am I? ...Oh, Commander? Uh, welcome?
name: A Blessing in Disguise?

desc: H-hey, help me out! ...No, I didn't come in here for fun. When I finished my security duty last night, I got to thinking about how I was going to give you chocolate for Valentine's and fell asleep. When I woke up, I was stuffed in this thing...
name: Caught By Nightfall

desc: First ship of the {namecode:66}-class heavy cruisers, {namecode:66}.
name: Takao

desc: Commander, even I’ll get embarrassed if you keep staring at me like that... Eh? Why did I bring a volleyball? Did you not order me to bring it?
name: Beach Rhapsody

desc: Practicing writing is a type of training, isn't it? Commander... do you want to sit down and write with me?
name: The Lessons of Spring

desc: Hmm... school life, huh? It's a fairly fresh experience for me. Would it be fine to pin my hair up like this? What do you think, Commander?
name: School Romanza

desc: Ugh... S-such shameless attire... If not for Atago saying that it would benefit me to experience different things...! It looks good on me?! I, I see...
name: Full Throttle Charmer

desc: My five senses are sharper than ever, perhaps even TOO sharp. No matter what trap awaits, my only way forward is to pierce through and focus on overcoming this trial... Haaah!
name: Divine Exorcist's Blade

desc: Is this not supposed to be for the sake of self-cultivation? I've never seen training methods such as this... However, now that it's come to this, fleeing is not an option. I must lead by example by adapting to these strange circumstances!
name: Inner Cultivation

desc: Commander, I've been undertaking countless bride training sessions in order to prepare for this day. As your bride, I won't let you down.
name: Sakura Hanami

desc: Second ship of the {namecode:66}-class heavy cruisers, {namecode:67}.
name: Atago

desc: The warm breeze that gently wraps around your skin, and delicate footsteps across the white sand... isn’t this the essence of summer? Commander, what does summer mean to you?
name: Summer March

desc: Oh my, it's begun to snow. Commander, should we find a nice, quiet place to enjoy the view?
name: Hallmarks of Winter

desc: Student handbook, textbooks... twin guns, torpedoes... and what else... Huh? Commander, I'm just packing my bags for school... is there anything I'm missing?
name: School Traumerei

desc: So, you want big sister to be your "fleet queen"? You got it. But you'd better give it your all out there, or else I'll be upset with you!
name: Stunning Speedster

desc: Awooo! Tonight is a full moon, so you'll want to be extra careful so I won't eat you up! ...Just kidding. Even if I were a werewolf, I'd still protect and keep you safe.
name: Full Moon's Feral Wolf

desc: Commander... Ahh, from now on, shouldn't I call you "darling?" Come and hold my hand... Ah, at times like these, I just can't help but to want to eat you up, dar~ling~
name: Lily-White Vow

desc: Third ship of the {namecode:66}-class heavy cruisers, {namecode:68}.
name: Maya

desc: Takao-class heavy cruiser number four – Choukai.
name: Choukai

desc: There, that's it for the entrance... Oh welcome, Commander! I've been cleaning, so give me a moment... I'll be right with you!
name: Tidy Store, Tidy Mind

desc: Mogami-class heavy cruiser number three – Suzuya.
name: Suzuya

desc: Suzuya, the Mogami-class heavy cruiser, will be the nurse taking care of you today. Heehee, let's have fun with this nighttime examination, shall we?
name: Midnight Care

desc: Mogami-class heavy cruiser number four – Kumano.
name: Kumano

desc: It's time for Kumano's sexy swimsuit debut~! Just kidding~☆ Hey Commander, just where~ are~ you~ staring~? Ahaha~♡
name: Fancy Waves

desc: Now it's your turn, Commander! Which one's it gonna be~? You suuuure you wanna pick this card? ...I hear you, Suzuya! Stop tellin' the Commander what the cards are!
name: PJ Poker Party

desc: Tadah! Get a load of my... dancer outfit! So, whaddya think? Ahaha~♡ Hey, Commander, where are those eyes wandering? Did ya see something ya like?
name: One Thousand and One Nights' Wishes

desc: Heavy cruiser – Unzen.
name: Unzen

desc: Commander~ Come over here~♥ Heehee, you look surprised... I don't think I'm dressed strangely at all. Or... is this swimsuit not enough to satisfy you, Commander?
name: Sojourn Through Clear Seas

desc: Ah, Commander... What a predicament you've discovered me in. Hoping to put my skills to the test, I attempted to imitate so-called "ninjutsu." No, not the temporary paralysis one – I was trying to use the transformation jutsu.
name: Arcane Ninja Knowledge

desc: Improved Suzuya-class heavy cruiser – Asama.
name: Asama

desc: Commander? Your expression seems to signal that you are not content with just ghost stories, yes? Ashamed am I to admit that I am still afraid... May I ask you to remain with me? There is something I wish to tell you.
name: Blooming Upon a Bewitching Night

desc: Kongou-class fast battleship number one – Kongou.
name: Kongou

desc: We must fully live in the present, whether during work or during leisure - this is my mantra. Commander, shall we go for an outing together?
name: The Beauties of Nature

desc: "Celebrity Endorsement of the Port Medical Facilities"... Hehehe, you've made a wise decision picking me. Commander, I can leave the ad shoot to you, right?
name: Hospital Talent

desc: It would be a shame to pass on this lovely weather, Commander. Why have a dull commute by train when you can enjoy a leisurely bicycle ride in the sunlight, hm? Heehee♪
name: Breezy Commute

desc: That was a big wave... I need to balance better on my board, or else... Commander, can I take your hand – Hm? What's slippery? I have no idea what you're... Hyah?! My swimsuit?!
name: Troubled Seas

desc: Kongou-class fast battleship number two – Hiei.
name: Hiei

desc: Look how late it is... Commander, shall we embark on a dreamy voyage together?
name: Moonlit Cruise

desc: I have to admit, these qipaos from the Dragon Empery are quite elegant... I might sound arrogant saying this, but I feel like this outfit really brings out my charm. Hehe, wouldn't you agree, Commander?
name: Fragrant Red Plum

desc: We're headed for the white sands of the beach today. We all could use a breather every now and then, so let's just enjoy the sea breeze today. Hehe~
name: Beauty of the White Sands

desc: Kongou-class fast battleship number four – Haruna.
name: Haruna

desc: I think it's fine to enjoy school life once in a while... Hm? You wanna know what I'm listening to? Sure, if you're okay with just one earbud.
name: Free Time Before Class

desc: I guess that looks right... Since Kongou chose this for me, I must trust her judgment... Um, C-Commander, would you mind helping me out? ...It's a bit hard to walk in this outfit...
name: Scarlet Innocence

desc: "My dear Commander, is this dress that my sisters tailored for me to your liking?" ...Okay, no, I can't do polite Hiei-speak like she can... So, anyway, h-how do I look?
name: The Elegant Lotus

desc: Kongou-class fast battleship number four – Kirishima.
name: Kirishima

desc: Commander, enjoying school life is all fine and well, but we must not forget our duty... That said, what missions are waiting for us today?
name: After-School Cannon Time

desc: Being in front of my sisters in this outfit is one thing, but it really is embarrassing to be wearing it in front of you, Commander. Um... ahem! What do you think? Since you're here, want to walk down to the beach together?
name: Summery Audacity

desc: "Commander, bad luck for you, but you're just going to become another notch on my blade." Haha, just kidding, it's a joke! So, what do you think? My New Year's attire is pretty snazzy, isn't it?
name: Casual Dazzle

desc: The Lunar New Year is known for its hustle and bustle, but it's nice to just sit down with a brush and take in the smell of ink. Hey Commander, got any words you want to see rendered in calligraphy?
name: Graceful Ink Incense

desc: 1st Ship of the Amagi-class Battlecruisers, Amagi
name: Amagi

desc: Commander, are you here to pay me a visit? ...Ah, there is no need to be concerned about me. I made a promise to both you and Akagi that I would be mindful of my health.
name: Wending Waters, Serene Lotus

desc: *munch*... Ah. Commander, the banquet isn't over yet. What brings you here? When a host sneaks out, that causes trouble for the person cleaning up after them... Heehee, I didn't say NOT to, now, did I?
name: Red Kite Respite

desc: Fast Battleship, second ship of the Kongou-class Hiei.
name: Hiei-chan

desc: 1st Ship of the Amagi-class Battlecruisers, Amagi
name: Amagi-chan

desc: I'm Kongou, with the Muse System unit Cyanidin. You'll witness my elegance and idol charms, Commander. Heheh, get ready, because you'll never forget the sight of me on stage.
name: Kongou μ

desc: First ship of the {namecode:78}-class battleships, {namecode:78}.
name: Fusou

desc: {namecode:79} said always dressing like a witch can be a bit old-fashioned, so she gave me a new outfit. That kid... Do you think it looks good on me, Commander?
name: The Celebration of Spring

desc: Changing into leisure clothes, and waiting for the return of my beloved... Milord, I too have changed since meeting you.
name: Perfect Partner?

desc: For richer, for poorer, in sickness and in health, to love and to cherish... May we be together forever, Milord.
name: United in Heart and Soul

desc: Milord! Thank you~ Not just for the retrofit, but for many many things. Hehe, it was the greatest of fortune for me and {namecode:79} to meet you.
name: Fusou (Retrofit)

desc: Second ship of the {namecode:78}-class battleships, {namecode:79}.
name: Yamashiro

desc: It’s just not summer without beach volleyball! Ah... Milord, you’re not playing? But I went through all this effort to pick out a swimsuit...
name: Summer Offensive?

desc: Merry Christmas! Milord, milord, how do I look? Is my Christmas outfit pretty? Ehehe~ Big sis also praised me today!
name: Holiday Offensive

desc: Fusou told me that I have to wear a Western-style dress to the banquet, so she got one for me! Milord, Milord, isn't this dress pretty?
name: Dressy Black Cat

desc: Milord, Milord, welcome to the store! Yamashiro is a sales clerk today! Mhm, I'll do my best!
name: Sales Clerk Offensive?!

desc: Woah, even the air tastes totally different at this vacation spot! Milord, Milord, um, Akashi asked me to bottle up some of the air here for her! Want to give me a hand?
name: Vacation Offensive!

desc: Uwaah! M-Milord?! I'm so, so sorry... You didn't get hurt, did you? Um... This is my school uniform. Fusou tailored it for me, hehe~ ... Awawa! I should head off to class now! See you later!
name: Street Corner Offensive!

desc: Milord, Milord, I've finished changing! What do you think, what do you think? Milord, do you like Yamashiro's dress~?
name: Bridal Attack!

desc: Milord! I can do anything now~ bombardment or aerial strikes! So, the thing is, you can totally count on me, much much more, Milord! Milord~!
name: Yamashiro (Retrofit)

desc: First ship of the {namecode:76}-class battleships, {namecode:76}.
name: Ise

desc: Planes: check! Main guns: check! Nobody can stop me now! Let's sortie right now, Commander! I'm fired up and wanna wreak some havoc on the battlefield!
name: Ise (Retrofit)

desc: Second ship of the {namecode:76}-class battleships, {namecode:77}.
name: Hyuuga

desc: Aviation battleship Hyuuga, sporting new powers, reporting in! Rest easy, Commander, I'll show you my true post-retrofit power!
name: Hyuuga (Retrofit)

desc: Nagato-class battleship number one – Nagato.
name: Nagato

desc: I shall be hosting the commander today. Manjuus, I beseech you to help me look my best. I am... *yawn* a bit sleepy... Urghh... what is that ruckus out there? C-Commander! When did you arrive?
name: Great Fox's Respite

desc: Perfect, you have arrived. As long as you are here, the usual moon-watching will prove to be much more enjoyable... Why don't you stay here today and rest for a while?
name: Guardian Fox's Shining Furisode

desc: I heard that it is custom to play a "sport" at this kind of event, involving throwing pillows at others. Heheh, then I shall put the might of the Big Seven on display!
name: Guardian Fox's Vacation

desc: Though this is a splendorous dress befitting the occasion, it is too different from my usual attire... Mutsu and Mikasa have nothing but praise for it? If you say so, then perhaps... I can take your word. Hehe.
name: Guardian Fox's Procession

desc: C-Commander? What brings you here at such a time? I was just... trying to help everyone prepare for the New Year's celebrations... Ngh, why isn't this red string... coming loose at all?
name: Guardian Fox's Blessed Bonds

desc: It may be presumptuous of me, but please take care of me from now on... Is that acceptable? S-Somehow, it feels a little embarrassing... Ahaha...
name: Great Fox's White Gown

desc: Nagato-class battleship number two – Mutsu.
name: Mutsu

desc: Commander, check it out! "Nothing can stop me!" Urakaze made it for me! Now I can play warring states with her! Heheh, you should know I'm a force to be reckoned with! Can't you come play with us? Why?
name: Warring States Warship

desc: Hmh? If fah foo, Fummamuh? ...*gulp*. I'm not lazing around! I'm just checking on the pastries that just came in! What are you doing here anyway? To "taste-test?" Or is there something wrong with the pastries? Why?
name: A Maid's Mis-service?

desc: Tosa-class battleship number two – Kaga.
name: Kaga(BB)

desc: Tosa-class battleship number one – Tosa.
name: Tosa

desc: An inspection? ...You're awfully gung-ho about your work considering how hot it is outside... Surely you wouldn't have some sort of ulterior motive?
name: Hometown Zest

desc: Commander? ...You were looking for me? Hah, you have the most atrocious luck. I've just started getting comfortable and I'm not leaving anytime soon. Besides, the banquet will be done in time even without my help... You seem to be enjoying yourself. How about you join me instead of merely staring?
name: A Glimpse of Greatness

desc: Yamato-class battleship number two – Musashi.
name: Musashi

desc: "Welcome back, Master." Rather, that's what all the children at the café were saying to you when they greeted you at the door. Hehe, is this some new custom?
name: Violet Moonglow

desc: ...Hmph. Hitting such a target is but an easy feat for me... Commander, tell me which prize you want. I'll win it, along with all the other ones I've been asked to get.
name: The Purple Rabbit's Marksmanship

desc: Commander, the contract has been made according to your wishes. From now on, I will be your new refuge. Now, beloved Commander, are you prepared to live up to MY expectations?
name: Purest Wisteria

desc: Shikishima-class battleship number four – Mikasa.
name: Mikasa

desc: I found quite the nostalgic outfit when I was cleaning my wardrobe. Let's see... "Prepare to come with me on a new journey!" How do I look, Commander?
name: Style of the Sakura Capital

desc: It's about time for the flowers to bloom once more. Alas, how the time flies by... Ahem, Commander, let's see, would you like to go blossom-viewing with me?
name: Blossom-Viewing Season

desc: Even I like to dress down and unwind from time to time. Oh? This is new and exciting for you? Well, you are welcome to come see more of it from now on! Hahaha!
name: Reverence for Rest and Relaxation

desc: Welcome to the Sakura Empire's pop-up café... Oh, Commander! Everyone's waiting for you. Now get your butt in here and experience the full extent of our fleet's hospitality! Don't be nervous, now! Hahaha!
name: A Romantic Respite

desc: I was worried when you said you wanted to go on a trip with me, but... I do like getting to go sight-seeing and try on new threads. Commander, let's enjoy this to the fullest! Hahaha!
name: Beauty in Indigo

desc: I, battleship Mikasa, from now until eternity, pledge to you my undying love and devotion. May we help each other, encourage each other, and walk side-by-side on the same path. I hope to meet your expectations, as unworthy as I may be.
name: Untarnished Splendor

desc: Kii-class battleship – Kii.
name: Kii

desc: Refreshing drinks, delicious food, warm sunshine... and a pool to beat the heat? Heh, isn't this the essence of summer?
name: Poolside Persuasion

desc: Kii-class battleship – Owari.
name: Owari

desc: I love hammocks and water beds 'cause they make you feel like you're floating on waves. It's the most relaxing thing ever~♪ You oughta hop on and try for yourself, Commander~
name: Shimmering Forsythia

desc: Welcome, guest, to the Dwelling of Demons. I own this place. I will grant you any wish in exchange for a suitable price... Yeah! Recited it all in one go! I'm so goated!
name: My Wish is For Love

desc: Battleship Suruga, reporting for duty. It would seem that some threads of fate connect me to this port... No, don't mind my rambling. Please disregard that.
name: Suruga

desc: Good morning, Commander. Everyone else seems to be dressed up on this day of celebration, so this shouldn't be a problem, right?
name: Hundred Flowers' Auspice

desc: Oh. Fancy meeting you here... Walk to school together? Uh, sure! I know the way, so please just follow me.
name: Straightfaced Model Student

desc: This should do it. With how unremarkable my present is, I doubt it'll make any waves when the... Ack! Commander?! Why are you here?!
name: Uneventful Holiday Greetings

desc: Kii-class battleship – Oumi.
name: Oumi

desc: Ngh... Hah... Commander, can you help me for a moment? ...Why don't you say anything? Don't tell me... you prefer me this way?
name: A Failed Escape?

desc: Hiyou-class aircraft carrier number one – Hiyou.
name: Hiyou

desc: Hiyou-class aircraft carrier number two – Junyou.
name: Junyou

desc: Aircraft carrier, {namecode:89}.
name: {namecode:89}

desc: While everyone slips into sweet dreams from the night's festivities, the sound of gossamer sliding off of smooth skin reaches your ears... Hehe, would you like to spend this night under the stars with me, Master~?
name: The Dream of the Autumn Pillow

desc: Zuihou-class aircraft carrier – Zuihou.
name: Zuihou

desc: Commaaaaander~! Over here, over here! I'm right here! Chirp, chirp! Commander, come hand out balloons with me! Did you know these balloons can bring you good fortune? Here you go, the first one's for you!
name: Joy Comes on Fledgling Wings

desc: First ship of the {namecode:87}-class aircraft carriers, {namecode:87}.
name: {namecode:87}

desc: Waaaah! My candy! Candy is spillin’ everywhere! ...Wh-why are y’all chasin’ me? Commander, help me catch the pumpkin!
name: Patrolling Witch

desc: Commander, how do I look now that I've grown up? Are ya fallin' in love with me already? Mhm, ye definitely are~
name: Shouhou (Retrofit)

desc: Ryuujou-class Light Carrier - Ryuujou
name: Ryuujou

desc: *yawn*... Finally, a good night's rest... Now, to pick up where I left off on that RPG... M-m-m-milord, why are you here?! I wasn't slacking off or anything, I w-w-was just... Ughh....
name: Slacking Samurai

desc: All right! Steady! Steadyyy! Gottem! Hahahah! Now I'll– M-Milord?! I-I'm just, umm... enjoying an after-school break!
name: Dragon Hunter: Ryuujou's Rise

desc: Milooord! *splash*... Heheh, behold the amusement park's crown jewel – the Meandering Megamanjuu Dragon Slide! If that's too long, it's also known as the Manjuu Octopus Slide. Personally, though, I think the former name is cooler!
name: The Dragon Slides In!

desc: Ryuuhou-class light aircraft carrier – Ryuuhou.
name: Ryuuhou

desc: Commander, everyone seems to be busy with end-of-year preparations. If there is anything I can do to help, please let me know.
name: Firebird's New Year Dance

desc: Zuihou-class aircraft carrier – Chitose.
name: Chitose

desc: An order of coconut milk... and grilled sausage. Mm, that should do it. ...Hm? Commander? Are you here to place an order, or to get away from the heat?
name: Summer Shine

desc: I had this outfit custom-made just for today... Do you like it, Commander? Um, that's good then... (*whispers*) Booyah.
name: Mosaic of Blending Colors

desc: Zuihou-class aircraft carrier – Chiyoda.
name: Chiyoda

desc: Hehe~ If you don't have any other plans, then your only task... is to enjoy a holiday by the sea! Commander, have you switched into vacation mode yet?
name: Shimmering Surf

desc: Aircraft carrier, {namecode:91}.
name: Akagi

desc: "When you gaze long into the abyss, the abyss also gazes into you." Commander, please do not forget that when you gaze at Akagi~ *giggles*
name: Paradise Amaryllis

desc: Commander will always remain by Akagi's side... Right, "Gods?" Of course... Akagi will deal with the pests.... Ahaha...
name: Plum and Snow

desc: Commander, I've been waiting for you~ What a sinful one you are, to tempt Akagi like this for so long... But at long last, nobody will ever get between us again...♡
name: Ruby-Laced Beauty

desc: This banquet is my present to you... and your attendance is the greatest reward I could hope for~ Indeed, I shall not grant you leave tonight until you pass out. Ehehe... Ahahaha~♡
name: Dawn-Phoenix's Summons

desc: Commander, open up. Say ahh... Heehee, heheheheh... You're like a little baby♪ Receiving a lovely new outfit and seeing a different side of you... How blessed am I?
name: Precipice of Sweetness

desc: We should send out even more invites... This is the best way to rid ourselves of those pesky vixens all at once!
name: Deep Crimson Poppy

desc: Aircraft carrier, {namecode:92}.
name: Kaga

desc: "You only live once?" Where have I heard that saying before... Commander, are you getting excited?
name: Everlasting Killing Stone

desc: One must wear appropriate attire for the New Year. What do you think, Commander? Let me hear your opinion.
name: White Fox's New Year

desc: This statue seems to have been inspired by the teachings of the Iris Orthodoxy. Though I am unfamiliar with this kind of art, gazing upon such majesty... fills one with a sense of piety. Commander, can you feel it as well?
name: Exalted White Wings

desc: I never thought you'd end up taking such a long trip with me just to pick up a dress... Though I'm worried about leaving my sister behind at port, I suppose I should take your advice and relax a bit.
name: Gentle Blossom's Sigh

desc: What are you doing up here?! Oh, it's you. I thought you went to see my sister? ...You needed a breath of fresh air? That's all fine, but you should return to my sister soon before she does something mad.
name: Dusk-Simurgh's Vigil

desc: I came in expecting to play an assassin, but instead I'm a dancer. Did Akashi come up with this setting? Well, whatever... As long as I get to fight, there's nothing worth complaining about. Commander, hide behind me if you ever encounter a monster.
name: Snowsilk Fox Dance

desc: "To hold one's hand and grow old together with him"... If it is to be with you, then it won't so bad.
name: Sacred Blue Lily

desc: Aircraft carrier, {namecode:93}.
name: Souryuu

desc: I tried wearing something a bit different from usual, but I'm not sure it suits me... Commander, what do you think?
name: The Crane Amidst the Pines

desc: Counselor girl {namecode:93}! Remedy the school atmosphere and correct your learning attitude, and...well, in short, I protect the discipline of the school.
name: The Counselor Girl

desc: If I can become stronger through this... Commander, what are you staring at? Don't you still have work to do?
name: Souryuu (Retrofit)

desc: Aircraft carrier, {namecode:94}.
name: Hiryuu

desc: Without girl bullies, there would be no disciplinary girl. So...before sister catches me, let’s cause some mischief at school.
name: After School Bullies

desc: Retrofit complete! Aircraft Carrier Hiryuu, reporting for duty! Hahaha! I finally got the chance to use that line! I'll be counting on you once more!
name: Hiryuu (Retrofit)

desc: First ship of the {namecode:95}-class aircraft carriers, {namecode:95}.
name: Shoukaku

desc: I prepared this outfit just for the occasion, so... Commander, you're not going to disappoint me, are you? Hehe~♪
name: The Crane that Dances With the Wind

desc: Hehe, this kind of work is a simple matter for me. Commander, please look forward to my performance~
name: Sororal Wings

desc: Through building this relationship with you, I've made so many happy memories. Now I think it's time to work toward a new goal! Heehee, I was serious about that, you know. Commander, I look forward to many long years together with you♡
name: White Crane of Domestic Bliss

desc: Second ship of the {namecode:95}-class aircraft carriers, {namecode:96}.
name: Zuikaku

desc: New Elite 1st CarDiv, Zuikaku, reporting for duty! Ahh, I've always wanted to give such a cool introduction! Shoukaku would definitely make fun of me if she heard it, but I wanted to try it while everyone is in a festive mood... Commander, what'd you think?
name: Ceremonial Crane

desc: Commander, I volunteered to take this job in order to help you out, but this outfit... did it always require such a high degree of exposure...?
name: The Wind's True Name

desc: Sis, how's my car lookin'? "All clear, ready to go at any time." Alrighty, just leave the rest to me! Commander, you're about to witness what I can accomplish from the cockpit!
name: Zoom Like the Wind

desc: Taihou-class aircraft carrier – Taihou.
name: Taihou

desc: You're taking so long to dress yourself, my Commander. Are you struggling to find something to match my dress? Hehe, it doesn't matter what you wear, you're always perfect to me♡
name: Forbidden Fruit

desc: Hehehe, I let Christmas and New Year's slip right by me, that I might use the Dragon Empery's Lunar New Year to capture my Commander's attentions... Oh, My Commander, won't you please enjoy the show I've prepared for you♡
name: Phoenix's Spring Song

desc: Do I make a nice race queen, my Commander...? Hehe. With these proportions, and my fantastic outfit~♡ The others couldn't hope to compare with me!
name: Enraptured Companion

desc: Ehehe~ There is no greater bliss than being with you after classes are over, my Commander~ The kitty here seems to agree♡
name: Sweet Time After School

desc: A beach date, just me and my Commander... I could walk by your side forever—No, I can't be satisfied by this alone. And neither can you... Right, my Commander?♥
name: Seaside Daydreams

desc: Aah... I didn't think you'd agree to my offer for some extra "entertainment" together♡ Just the thought of you using your body to guide mine now... Heehee♡ I'm all yours to command.
name: Fun on the Baize

desc: My Commander~ Do you like the location that I've chosen~? We have the entire evening to ourselves, free from the disturbance of anyone else...! Ahhh, my heart is throbbing even more vigorously than the ocean's waves~♡
name: Temptation on the Sea Breeze

desc: Yamato-class ship number three – Shinano.
name: Shinano

desc: The moonlight dims beneath hazy clouds, and the lights of the night sky begin to shine... The moon, and this sake, are both intoxicating... Will you not enjoy this fine evening with me...?
name: Dreams of the Hazy Moon

desc: Hnnh... Such clamors of merriment... Would this one be welcome amidst these festivities? Alas... If you so desire, how can this one refuse...?
name: Moonlit Chrome

desc: This world of pristine sand that you have envisioned, a mirage that fits only within the confines of a dream and a reverie... No matter how many times we meet here, this one finds herself drawn to this place again and again...
name: Dreamy White Sands

desc: As a flickering, quivering phantasm... Welcome to the dream this one made for you, Commander. Do you like this magic, in which this one appears in an instant?
name: Visions of Fantasy

desc: Aircraft carrier Akagi.
name: Akagi-chan

desc: With the magicks of the Sakura Empire, changing my form like this is a trifle... Hehehe, Commander? Does this Akagi please you?
name: Akagi μ

desc: With these clothes, and upon this stage... Ahaha... Ahahaha... Fate has ordained that my Commander shall fall for me here... Commander, please listen to the song of my love until the very end~♡
name: Taihou μ

desc: Unryuu-class aircraft carrier – Katsuragi.
name: Katsuragi

desc: It's– summer– festival– time–!! Uhh, well, maybe it's a bit too late for a "summer" festival, so maybe a regular festival is fine? Well, the important thing is that you have lots of fun, Commander! Because I sure as heck will!
name: Night-Illuminating Festival

desc: Mmmh~ When it gets real hot, whether you're a shipgirl or an ordinary person, the place to go to cool down is always either the mountains or the beach, right? But what if I told you, that when you're at a rooftop pool, you not only get the great views of climbing up a mountain, but also the refreshing coolness of splashing around in the water? Am I right or am I right, Commander? ...Heeeey, are you even listening?!
name: Shallow-Water Leisure

desc: Taihou-class aircraft carrier – Taihou.
name: Taihou-chan

desc: You... are the one this one has seen in my dreams. Wonderful... This one feels relaxed around you... But it seems you need this one's guidance, don't you?
name: Shinano-chan

desc: Aircraft carrier – Amagi.
name: Amagi(CV)

desc: So you've finally come, Commander. I have been waiting for you— Ahem. Heehee, please step forward. In this castle of dreams, this throne... belongs to you and me equally.
name: Throne of Fallen Petals

desc: "In joy and in sorrow, in sickness and in health..." Commander? Heehee, this isn't foreshadowing. You don't need to worry about your beloved Amagi anymore.
name: Moonlit Blossom on Placid Seas

desc: Project G14 aircraft carrier – Hakuhou.
name: Hakuhou

desc: You amaze me, my lord. Not only have you foiled this kunoichi's assassination plot, but you've also repaid my treachery with kindness and mercy... Heehee, you wouldn't reject my desire to remain here and serve you, would you? My lord...
name: Floral Ninja Roleplay

desc: Type B1 cruiser submarine – I-19.
name: I-19

desc: Aww, do I have to go to school? ... Oh, Commander! Are you here to see me off?
name: Departure's Gentle Breeze

desc: So sleepy... Hey, Commandeeer? Do you wanna nap with me and my torpedo?
name: Pillowy Paradise

desc: I thought I'd try on this bunny costume! Hehehe, do you like it? If you think it's cute, I wanna hear you say it~
name: Blossoming Bunny

desc: Type B1 cruiser submarine – I-26.
name: I-26

desc: Many secrets lie at the bottom of the ocean! Commander, let's go looking for them next time! It'll be like a field trip~ Heheh!
name: Deep-Sea Rabbit

desc: Commander, are you also waiting for the fireworks to start? There's still some time, so let's have a little chat!
name: Shortly Before the Fireworks

desc: Type-B Mod 2 cruiser submarine – I-58.
name: I-58

desc: Type B1 cruiser submarine – I-25.
name: I-25

desc: Hi there, Commander. Oh, this outfit? I'll be wearing it to school today. By the way, did you want to come sit in on my class?
name: Coral Reef Bunny

desc: Commander, Happy Lunar New Year. Would you like some sweet wine to celebrate? Oh, be careful not to drink too much~
name: Sweet Wine of Celebration

desc: Type B3 Mod. 2 cruiser submarine – I-56.
name: I-56

desc: School... is pretty nice. I can quietly stay in this corner and mind my own business...
name: Wallflower in the Corner

desc: Kaidai Type VIa submarine – I-168.
name: I-168

desc: I look different from usual? That's obvious, isn't it... All right, all right, I was just giving you a hard time. We're at a festival, so we might as well enjoy ourselves!
name: Festive Mood!

desc:
Repair ship {namecode:98}
<color=#fad545>Can be built after unlocking</color>
name: Akashi

desc: Commander, how does Akashi's new outfit look, nya? Isn't it cute? If you like it, then put a ring on it. I mean, everyone's gone out to play... if you don't help empty my inventory, I'll go broke, nya!
name: Akashi's in the Red, Nya!

desc: Heheh, this is what I've been saving up for, nya~♪ A special dress that combines Gothic fashion with Sakura charm! Commander, how about those gems, nya?
name: The Black Cat Cometh!

desc: Ohh, it's Commander, nya. Have you come to buy Akashi's new work, nya? Today's a holiday, so go ahead and enjoy yourself, nya~
name: Welcome to AzurCon!

desc: Hehehe, come on in, nya! Can I help you find something, nya? Your genial and knowledgeable staff, Akashi, will gladly provide her detailed recommendations, nya!
name: Welcome to Sofmap!

desc: Commander, because of your continued patronage of my shop, I have no choice but to return the favor with my body, nya~! ...Just kidding, nya. Having that said, I really do love you, Commander. Even more than I love gems, nya~
name: White Cat's Repayment

desc: Type A Mod. 2 cruiser submarine – I-13.
name: I-13

desc: So high up... But it's okay, Commander – I have a good sense of balance. Anyway, wanna see what's down there?
name: After-School Observations

desc: I-400-class large submarine aircraft carrier – I-404.
name: I-404

desc: Commander! Help me out here! Can't believe I walked into a trap while trying to beat this place... Ugh! This suuucks!
name: Dance of Crimson Strings

desc: Mmf! Mmfmmf! Mmmgghh... Mmmff!
name: Dance of Crimson Strings

desc: Munition ship – Kashino.
name: Kashino

desc: Ack... Owww... My apologies, Commander, I seem to have slipped on something... At times, it's hard to notice things I'm about to step on... Ugh...
name: Hot Springs Relaxation

desc: Hyah?! U-Umm, I can't get out... Oh, Commander?! I'm sorry! I tripped while I was cleaning, and I ended up stuck in here! Umm... What do I do now...
name: Maid for Mayhem

desc: ♪~ Commander, how'd that sound? Hmm... I just started learning last minute, so I guess things aren't coming together after all... But, why do I sound off-pitch even though I'm playing everything exactly the way I was taught...?
name: Robust Floral Strings

desc: W-welcome... A bottle of milk is just as good after swimming in the pool as it is after bathing in a hot spring... Umm, should I really be wearing this? You seem to be blushing, Commander...
name: Fresh and Sweet

desc: Commander, Happy New Year's. In this coming year, please continue to look after me...
name: Pulse of the New Year

desc: Commander, thank you for coming to the party. Ayanami... has been waiting for you. ...I look a bit scary? I'm not sure I get it... I guess.
name: Nightfall Raiment

desc: No, Ryuujou! Samurai builds should stay back during the boss! ...Oh, welcome, Commander. I'm busy with this game right now, so just make yourself at home or something.
name: Off-Duty Battle Station Gear

desc: Rigging, activate!
name: Dynasty Shipgirl

desc: Welcome. Ayanami will be taking your order, yes. Will this be dine-in, or to-go? I would personally recommend the cola.
name: Cola Fills You With Determination

desc: Ultimate Ability: Dynamic Kick! ...Oh, I used my skill on the wrong target. Sorry, can we try that again?
name: Dynamic Kick!

desc: *fidget, fidget*... Oh, how's the party? Yes, I get a little angsty when I'm without a weapon... I envy your ability to stay calm no matter what.
name: Disarming Deep Blue

desc: Basking in the summer night's air and chatting with someone I love, all under the moonlight... Now this is a nice bath. By the way... did you know you dropped your towel?
name: A Dip in the Moonlight

desc: Heavy cruiser – Ibuki.
name: Ibuki

desc: Milord, it's starting to snow... If it suits you, please take shelter under Ibuki's umbrella.
name: Winter Sylph's Reverie

desc: This is my first time wearing Western clothes... Um, Milord! Does this outfit... suit Ibuki well...?
name: Snow on the Wind

desc: The Dragon Empery's "Spring Festival" is... filled with fun, liveliness, and pure jubilation. I can feel my true feelings welling up... Maybe, an environment like this would suit me pretty well...
name: Arrival of Spring

desc: I'm glad you've returned, Milord. I've changed my attire in order to better carry out your order–for us to "relax together." Now then... could you please instruct me on how to proceed?
name: Tranquil Sunya

desc: Battleship – Izumo.
name: Izumo

desc: You'd like to see my classical dance? Your tastes are quite refined, Commander... In that case, I'll show you the finest performance in the land!
name: Izumo's Thousand Cherry Trees

desc: Finally realized I'm the bartender here? This isn't any ordinary wine, you know. Give it a try, if you're interested. Heheheh...
name: Tail-Stirred Cocktail

desc: Destroyer – Kitakaze.
name: Kitakaze

desc: All the preparations are now complete... Commander, let us sally forth and conquer these festival grounds! ...But before that, can we get something to eat first?
name: Celebration Conquest!

desc: Mm, preparations complete. If I keep it up, the production will surely be a great success. The doves have been on their best behavior too. Commander, what do you think about Kitakaze's magic show?
name: Night of Doves and Magic

desc: Large cruiser – Azuma.
name: Azuma

desc: Commander? Oh, I haven't quite finished changing. My hair still needs work... Sorry, would you mind waiting a bit longer?
name: Soft Voice of Spring

desc: Graduation is approaching, and that means it's time for career counseling. Do you want to be a great general who wins with impossible tactics, or a leader beloved by all the port? Which will it be, Commander? Or... Heehee, I already know your plan.
name: Career Counseling for the Groom

desc: I must be dreaming, to be able to don this white veil... Haha, though, what's more important is our life together afterwards! Commander, please look forward to the rich fruit of my bridal training~
name: Lily-White Longing

desc: Aircraft carrier – Hakuryuu.
name: Hakuryuu

desc: All righty, one freshly-sliced plate of sashimi coming right up! ...Huh? I'm coming across too aggressive? Even after I went through all this trouble for you, you still have something to nitpick about? ...Well, whatever. Enjoy your meal!
name: Slice, Dice, and Serve

desc: Katana... at the ready. Hmph, you again? Never expected you to know anything about music, the way you've been out there conquering the waves with us this whole time. Come then, let me test how good your tastes are with this song!
name: Flash of Silk and Strings

desc: Hahahaha! Now THIS is a sword worthy of my hands! Perfect blade, perfect hilt, perfect cut – only a master of their craft could make such a beauty! Come on, let's see what this blade can do!
name: Folded Over a Thousand Times

desc: Y-you! How dare you make me wear... "I thought it would look good on you, and your current outfit is too breezy"?! What nonsense! I can wear whatever I want in my room! ...Achoo?!
name: Four Fine Layers

desc: Light cruiser - Shimanto.
name: Shimanto

desc: You couldn't have picked a better time to come. Allow me to treat you to a cup of the Dragon God's benevolence– Uhh, I'll go boil some water right now, so sit tight. After you finish the tea, shall we kick back and relax awhile?
name: The Comfy Dragon God

desc: Well, Commander, are you ready? I'm going to teach you the Dragon God's sacred training method. First, you scoop up some water, like... Achoo! Th-that one didn't count!
name: The Relaxing Dragon God

desc: Whew... So refreshing. Nothing beats lounging around indoors after a bath. Commander, there's plenty of time before dinner, so how about we... do something to kill the time?
name: The Relaxing Dragon God

desc: Battleship – Daisen.
name: Daisen

desc: Oh, Commander! You're here earlier than I expected. Ah, I finally get to serve you in this specially made attire, stuffed full of such fantasy and dreams... I'm ever so honored.
name: Bunny Priestess in Prayer

desc: Type 1934 destroyer – Z1 Leberecht Maass.
name: Leberecht Maass (Z1)

desc: Because she’s the Z1, her results will of course be NO.1! Hehe, no matter where she goes, Z1-sama will always be the best!
name: "Rebellious" Top Student

desc: Hmm... So this is a retrofit, huh? Not bad! Rejoice once more, Commander, for no task or enemy is too daunting for the new and improved Z1!
name: Z1 (Retrofit)

desc: Type 1934 destroyer – Z2 Georg Thiele.
name: Z2

desc: Commander, I do wonder if your order to "come dressed in new clothes" was simply your way of saying "I want to see you in a casual outfit." No matter the case, I'm happy to oblige.
name: High-Rise, High-Style

desc: Being able to see you all flabbergasted makes changing into this outfit worth it. Are you going to keep standing there like a scarecrow? Come over here~ Who knows, we might even be able to see the fireworks from this spot.
name: Of Koi and Evening Hues

desc: Type 1934A destroyer – Z9 Wolfgang Zenker.
name: Z9

desc: Commander, umm... Would you like to try our new drink? It's very sweet and tasty... Ahh, why am I so nervous? I need to do better...
name: Teary Cocktail

desc: Type 1934A destroyer – Z11 Bernd von Arnim.
name: Z11

desc: I wanted to help at the pop-up shop so I could buy a special-edition game, but I ended up in debt somehow. Commander, help... I'll do anything...
name: Service, Sincerity, and Insolvency

desc: Type 1934A destroyer – Z13.
name: Z13

desc: ...Yes, I know I'm on the clock, but taking productive breaks helps raise your working efficiency afterward! You should take one, too – come sit and kill time wi– Ahem! I mean, come sit and have a break with me!
name: Strategic Date Solution

desc: Type 1934A destroyer – Z16 Friedrich Eckoldt.
name: Z16

desc: Heh heh! Count your lucky stars, Commander, because you're just in time – to witness the one-and-only Z16 knock this thing right outta the ballpark!
name: Guaranteed Grand Slam!

desc: Type 1936 destroyer – Z18 Hans Lüdemann.
name: Z18

desc: Type 1936 destroyer – Z19 Hermann Künne.
name: Hermann Künne (Z19)

desc: Type 1936 destroyer – Z20 Karl Galster.
name: Karl Galster (Z20)

desc: Type 1936 destroyer – Z21 Wilheim Heidkamp.
name: Wilhelm Heidkamp (Z21)

desc: Type 1936A "Narvik-class" destroyer – Z23.
name: Z23

desc: This is going to be on the exam! If you don't take thorough notes, I am going to punish you!
name: Philosophy Sensei

desc: Haiyaaah! It's up to you, Ayanami! Oh, Commander! Are you actually keeping score? We might not be having a serious match, but that's no excuse for you to stand around and do nothing.
name: Breezy Doubles

desc: Welcome! A table for one today? Um... Commander, my smile doesn’t look stiff... right?
name: Perfect Smile?

desc: Oh, good evening, Commander. I was just looking for Javelin and the others... Say, would you like to keep me company for a bit?
name: The Banquet's Honor Student

desc: Hi, welcome! How may I serve y– It's you, Commander?! Err, well, I'm working as a trainee at this Sakura Empire-style café, you see... What do you think of this outfit?
name: Café Trainee @New Base

desc: Jeez... Javelin's got what it takes, but I'm really concerned about Laffey and Ayanami. Oh well, I guess it's up to me to manage them... Commander, please don't forget to support me too.
name: Serious Idol @Acting Manager?!

desc: Commander, please help hold onto the ladder. I've almost got the book... Just a little more... All right... C-Commander?! Please don't look up!
name: The Eyecatch in the Rye?

desc: Whew... Sorry to keep you waiting. I was having a hard time deciding which outfit to wear... Ah, um... how do I look?
name: Schwarze Hochzeit

desc: My efficiency should be upgraded along with my performance. Paperwork, battle plans... I can handle them all! Commander, be prepared, we’ll be very busy~
name: Z23 (Retrofit)

desc: Type 1936A "Narvik-class" destroyer – Z24.
name: Z24

desc: Come, human! The rite of festivities is upon us! Come hither, and let us revel in this foreign holiday together!
name: Festival-going Fiend

desc: Heh heh... As expected, you couldn't even last for a second! Winning too easily takes all the fun out of it... You, the mortal over there, I'll give you the honor of being my next opponent!
name: The Devil on the Court

desc: "Sing your praises to the Fiend of Crimson Darkness, Z24!" ... Hmm, maybe I should go with "Bow down in astonishment!"... Ah, yes! Mortal, you've come at a most opportune time! Hurry and tell me what you think of my new catchphrase! ...Actually, get me down from here first!
name: Blood-Red Dance Beneath the Moon

desc: Type 1936A "Narvik-class" destroyer – Z25
name: Z25

desc: Even at the beach, we cannot afford to be careless! Commander, have you adequately prepared for today's activities?
name: Hot Summer's Cool Breeze

desc: Type 1936A "Narvik-class" destroyer – Z26.
name: Z26

desc: Commander, welcome to my pad! Ah, give me a sec, let me go grab all the snacks and drinks and games!
name: Sharing is Caring

desc: Type 1936A "Narvik-class" destroyer – Z28.
name: Z28

desc: Commander, Happy New Year! Is there anything you'd like to do on New Year's Day? Say, why don't we try doing all of that stuff, all at once~?
name: New Year Smorgasbord!

desc: Prosit, Commander! I think these wild animals were attracted by the champagne's aroma. But they're well-behaved and like being petted. Do you want to be petted too, Commander?
name: Sylvan Celebration

desc: Type 1936B destroyer – Z35.
name: Z35

desc: Commander, and all my fellow friends of the fleet, Happy New Year's! This time, your favorite idol Z35 will be presenting a brand new Sakura-themed collaboration, "Projekt Kirschblüte!" Everyone, thank you for your continued support!
name: Projekt Kirschblüte

desc: "Welcome, my beloved Master♡ Heehee, I've been waiting here for you for sooo long!" Heheh, did you get good pics this time? My beloved Master♪
name: Liebender Engel

desc: In pursuit of being an even greater idol, I prepared this new outfit! "With my magic and passionate heart, I'll bring you joy☆" Heheh, did you like that one, Commander?
name: Himmel: Beyond Love's Boundaries

desc: Type 1936B destroyer – Z36.
name: Z36

desc: Type 1936B destroyer – Z43.
name: Z43

desc: Why can't I wrap this damn bandage... Hnnngh! Ow, ow, ouch! ...Huh? Comma–A-Augur of Destiny, help me! My magic-suppressing bandages have taken on a mind of their own...!
name: A Secret Base For Two

desc: Type 1936C destroyer – Z46.
name: Z46

desc: The bustling beach, clamoring with waves of joyfulness... experiencing this kind of summer is a first for me, but I don't dislike it...
name: Her First Summer

desc: Through the sweat and tears, striving for your goals. Rejoice in victory, sink within defeat... How fascinating, this "sports meet" may be.
name: Girls' Relay

desc: Dancing beams of light, shimmering on-stage; uplifted voices, joined as one by song... Upon this unknown stage, my heart doth flutter... Yet this sensation, is quite refreshing.
name: Star-Lit★Chocolate

desc: "Jianzhi," the art of breathing life into works of cut paper... is a world beyond my imagination. If these decorations are said to usher in blessings... are they akin to a coat-of-arms or a holy seal?
name: Jianzhi Fantasia

desc: Cast your eyes upon this bit of dust. As I was entrusted with the cleaning, I shall not allow this dust to remain. Will you also join me in this battle?
name: Chronicles of the Dust Wars

desc: Hm? You are following us because you're drawn to the sound of my flute? Ah... Then in exchange for accompanying you on this journey, tell me your story.
name: The Bard of Hamelin

desc: Type 1936C destroyer – Z47.
name: Z47

desc: Mandy, you getting distracted? No looking around on my watch. I've put down my phone for once, and I want you to only look at me while we're on the see-saw.
name: Young-Again Filter

desc: Type 1944 destroyer – Z52.
name: Z52

desc: Let's see... Where's the shop again? It should be... Oh, Commander! I'm not late, am I? I ran here as fast as I could!
name: The Rapid Rabbit

desc: Type 1937J destroyer – Otto von Alvensleben.
name: Otto von Alvensleben

desc: Hmph! You really think this brainless trap can keep me entangled forever? I don't need your help! I can break free by myself! ...Umm, what the hell? Why can't I do it?!
name: Hunter Becomes Hunted

desc: Urgh... I can't get them off... Huh?! C-Commander?! When did you get here?! This just, um... It just kind of happened! Help me get loose!
name: The Clumsy Maid is in a Bind!

desc: Königsberg class light cruiser, Königsberg.
name: Königsberg

desc: Königsberg class light cruiser, Karlsruhe.
name: Karlsruhe

desc: Königsberg-class light cruiser – Karlsruhe.
name: Karlsruhe (Retrofit)

desc: Königsberg-class light cruiser, Köln.
name: Köln

desc: Hmm... I feel like I can work even more efficiently than before. Commander, please rest assured, I will never betray your expectations.
name: Köln (Retrofit)

desc:
Leipzig-class light cruiser, Leipzig.
<color=#fad545>Can be built after unlocking</color>
name: Leipzig

desc: Commander, ah, um... We have all new items on the menu, and they're on sale for a limited time only... P-please give them a try! Phew... Th-thank goodness, I managed to not flub it...
name: Storefront Training

desc: I feel like Fishy is a lot more capable than before, but I don't feel much different... M-maybe Fishy was the one to get a retrofit instead of me?!
name: Leipzig (Retrofit)

desc: Leipzig-class light cruiser – Nürnberg.
name: Nürnberg

desc: Since you so readily accepted my invitation to go on a vacation together, you must be planning to... Ahh, what I meant is, we can leave at any time if you're ready...!
name: Spring Wanderer

desc: M-class light cruiser – Magdeburg
name: Magdeburg

desc: You little...! Look what a damn mess you made! And I'm the one who's gotta clean it up now! ...Oh. Perfect timing, Commander. Could use a hand with the floor here, after what this little turd did.
name: Cat Café Cleanup

desc: Here's an idea – how 'bout putting down the camera and actually enjoyin' the open sea? I'll move the swim ring so you can chill in the breeze with me!
name: Gone Fishing

desc: Dresden-class light cruiser – Emden.
name: Emden

desc: Raise your head, my darling human. O lost soul, you have three options – become Emden's meal, become Emden's prisoner... "Or become Emden's vassal. Our vassal♥"
name: White-Black Partita

desc: Welcome, my darling human. Are you looking for something? If it is Emden you seek, you have already found her. "We, Emden, are before your very eyes."
name: Moonsilver Union

desc: Welcome, my darling human. We are Emden, the receptionists that shall guide your way. You can go anywhere you'd like... as long as you give us an offering♡ "Even to an unsullied paradise that is not of this world"♥
name: Duet of Guiding Stars

desc: Pillau-class light cruiser – Elbing.
name: Elbing

desc: As the mistress of this manor, I c-command thee to kneel... No, of course. I mean, what authority do I have to issue commands? I'm better suited to be a maid than a mistress...
name: The Throne of Misfortune

desc: Are you also having trouble sleeping, Commander? I-I thought so... It must be because I was praying for you to have sweet dreams... Look what I've done – now, neither of us can fall asleep... Urgh...
name: Sleepless Night's Wishes

desc: G-good day, Commander. I'm ready to be your model... Ugh, there's probably going to be an accident if I wish that you'll take cute photos... Better clear my head just to be sure.
name: Beauty Beneath the Spring Limelight

desc: M-class light cruiser – Regensburg.
name: Regensburg

desc: Wanted to feast your eyes on this, didn't you? Haha, there's no point trying to deny it. All your petty desires are clear as day to me, so why not just be honest about it?
name: Dark Dragon, Brilliant Beach

desc: Hmm... Who knew this stuff was in a warehouse, of all places? Heh, I think this will help quite a bit with disciplining that rigging that gave you so much trouble.
name: The Dark Dragon's Dungeon

desc: M-class light cruiser – Duisburg.
name: Duisburg

desc: C-Commander... Huh? If we're training, I should call you Master...? M-Master... You don't have to stare. Let's just get started, please...
name: Endurance Training (Gone Wrong)

desc: Admiral Hipper-class Heavy Cruiser, Admiral Hipper
name: Admiral Hipper

desc: W-well? Does this kimono look good on me? ...R-really? Duh, I know it looks GREAT on me! Who really cares what you think... C-can't be me... No, I didn't say anything!
name: Sunshine by the Hot Spring

desc: Admiral Hipper-class heavy cruiser – Blücher.
name: Blücher

desc: Heheheh☆ You're lagging behind, Commander! Pick up the pace or you'll be left behind! Just kidding~ I'll slow down for you so we can stick together!
name: High-Altitude Head Over Heels

desc: Heheh☆ I'm Blücher, dragon knight of the Demon King's army! ...Not riding the dragon so much as being dragged along by it? Well, I guess... Whoaaah! The dragon won't obey me! Commander, heeelp!
name: Skyward Burning Love

desc: Heheh☆ I KNEW you'd come to see me, Commander! Next time, you don't need to rush to my side after getting my message, okay? I'll give you as much time as you need, because the last thing I wanna do is tire you out, my super-duper mega sweetheart!
name: The After-School Wait

desc: Admiral Hipper-class Heavy Cruiser, Prinz Eugen
name: Prinz Eugen

desc: Relaxing on a float, gently licking my lips... is this really the most popular photo pose for the beach? Wales, you’re not teasing me again, are you?
name: Unfading Smile

desc: So this is the Sakura Empire's New Year? Hehe, how interesting~ Commander, since it's the New Year, why don't you put aside all those papers and have a drink with me?
name: Profusion of Flowers

desc: ... Huh? Commander, is that you? Me, drunk? No way... *hic*... If I was, Commander, then what are you planning to do to me? Hehe...
name: Cordial Cornflower

desc: Viel Glück~ Are you having a good time, Commander? Just know that the only person I'm cheering for... is you~
name: Final Lap

desc: Guten Abend~ So, what do you think? Pretty great view, right? Hehe, I was talking about the night scenery outside, you know~?
name: Kindred Evening Spirits

desc: *pant*... Quarterback Prinz Eugen scores a touchdown. I can't believe I'm the one charging in now... Commander, can you bring me water and a towel? I'm getting a little sticky from all this sweat...
name: Brilliant Touchdown

desc: You sure seem to be enjoying yourself, Commander. Heehee – what amusing thing will you do next, I wonder? ...Me? Don't pay me any mind. I just want to see what you're like when you're drunk!
name: Between Tipsiness and a Wager

desc: If fate brought us together, then it has my thanks… I look forward to our future together~
name: Symphonic Fate

desc: Deutschland-class armored cruiser, Deutschland.
name: Deutschland

desc: For a servant, your eyes are good... *coughs*... I'm an Ironblood Princess, the Queen of Night, Deutschland! Servant? No. I am the first of my family. Come, kiss the ring of royalty!
name: Dark Demon Princess

desc: One must not neglect sunscreen during the summer... Plebeian, if you wish to serve your master, prostrate yourself and yell "I beg of you, Queen Deutschland" three times, and I might consider giving you an opportunity. Ahahaha~
name: Service Time?!

desc: I seem pleased? Of course I am. Why wouldn't I be when my sweet little sister will be joining us at the party? Now shape up and entertain your master, you lowly animal! Ahahahaha!
name: Demon Princess' Dark Hour Banquet

desc: Why are so many people out and about during a holiday? ...That's it! Lowly animal, was it your idea to prepare all this to surprise me...?! Heh... Hehe, that's right, don't you dare disappoint me!
name: Lantern-Lit Ruler

desc: Deutschland-class armored cruiser number three – Admiral Graf Spee.
name: Admiral Graf Spee

desc: I sailed alone, fought alone, and then I was sunk while being alone. Now I found a new beginning... Hmm? Commander, you've been staring and laughing at me since the beginning… do you want to eat this?
name: Girl's Sunday

desc: I never dreamt that I'd be able to don this outfit and live a normal, peaceful life... Thank you, Commander...
name: Peaceful Daily Life

desc: It's so fancy, so formal... Is this a "party"? I'm not sure I'll be able to fit in... But if you'll go with me, Commander, I'll give it a try!
name: A Novel Anniversary

desc: My sister just wouldn't stop bugging me, so I finally caved and agreed to do this... Anyways, all I have to do is get up on stage and sing, right?
name: World's♥Cutest

desc: Huh? Why are you staring at me like I'm some weirdo? I'll have you know, it's not like I wanted to do this or anything!
name: Admiral Hipper μ

desc: Heavy cruiser Roon, reporting for idol activities and associated experimental equipment testing. Today, we fight not with fire and sword, but with the power of song.
name: Roon μ

desc: P-class armored ship – Prinz Heinrich.
name: Prinz Heinrich

desc: Phew... Changing into these clothes took quite a long time~ So, how does it look? A fine mixing of different cultures, wouldn't you agree? Ahaha, Happy New Year, Commander!
name: Fireworks and Tapestries

desc: *ptwee*! Remember: safety first! Commander, you've got to do your stretches before going in the pool! Be thorough, or I'll get mad at you!
name: Rabbit on Watch

desc: Listen up, Commander! I'm the one in charge of this school's seedy underbelly here at this port, so you'd better do what I tell you to! In return, I'll offer you my protection! Ahaha~♪
name: Secret Boss o' the Underworld?

desc: Alrighty, I'm gonna sing a song for you now! Surprised by how jazzy and womanly I can be, are you? Ahahah!
name: Heinrich on Stage

desc: P-class armored ship – Prinz Adalbert
name: Prinz Adalbert

desc: Zzz... Huh? Did I doze off? I just meant to rest my eyes for a sec after closing up, but look how long I slept... Hang on, why are you still here, Commander?
name: After-Hours Service

desc: Oh, good timing. Pass me the shampoo bottle over– Whooooaaaa! Ow, oww... Hey, uh, Commander, could you help me get back up on my feet?
name: Bathroom Slip-Up

desc: Roon-class armored cruiser – Yorck.
name: Yorck

desc: "Foolish, pitiable creature. Kneel before your Goddess!" Heehee! Hahahah, ahahahaha♥ You're the Commander, silly. You don't need to play along unless you want to.
name: Breaker under the Blood Moon

desc: This is armored cruiser Yorck, and I'm ready for a night with you, Commander. My "armor" today – my outfit, if you'd prefer – is made to be enticingly light AND stimulate your desire... Heehee, don't expect to get away from me easily tonight♥
name: Late-Night Companion

desc: Admiral Hipper-class heavy cruiser – Prinz Eugen.
name: Little Prinz Eugen

desc: Deutschland-class armored cruiser – Admiral Graf Spee.
name: Little Spee

desc: I am Friedrich Carl, P-class armored cruiser and the embodiment of love. Come, little one – let us get to the core truth of love and bring happiness to the whole world.
name: Friedrich Carl

desc: Alright, little one! Now that we have some time off, why don't we play a game? If you win, I might just give you... the reward of love♥
name: A Game of Love

desc: Are you ready, my beloved little one? I'm giving you all of me, so apply your love – the sunscreen – ever so thoroughly, so gently, please.
name: Tender Summer Care

desc: I am heavy cruiser idol Prinz Eugen, a participant in the Muse System experiment. You look interested in my outfit, Commander. Heheheh... You can expect my usual exploits and more!
name: Prinz Eugen μ

desc: Large cruiser – Ägir.
name: Little Ägir

desc: Scharnhorst-class battlecruiser, Scharnhorst.
name: Scharnhorst

desc: A festival, huh? Going for days without fighting is boring, not to mention not my style. C'mon, Commander, isn't there *something* exciting I can do during this "Lunar New Year" festival?
name: Panther und Pflaume

desc: Scharnhorst-class battlecruiser, Gneisenau.
name: Gneisenau

desc: These Halloween festivities are quite interesting, in a good way. Getting dressed up in these costumes isn't such a bad experience either. Commander, what do you think of my costume?
name: Nightmarish Succubus

desc: Battlecruiser – Seydlitz.
name: Seydlitz

desc: There it is – Dracula's Castle, brought into this world by chaos itself... On my honor, I swear I will put an end to the divine bloodline!
name: Heir of the Vampire Killer

desc: How do I look, Commandant? I thought you may like seeing me in a dress, however I don't know if this is what you desired or not...
name: Floral Liberation

desc: Salutations, Commandant! ...You think I look like a totally different person? Haha! You're right – I decided to change up my look for once. Oh, today looks like a hot day, so I brought drinks. Take one!
name: An Officer's Streetwear

desc: Derfflinger-class battlecruiser – Lützow.
name: Lützow

desc: "Have you come to accept your fate, human? Heehee~" ...Don't just stand there, Commander. Say something!
name: Everlasting Blood Banquet

desc: Om, nom... Hmm. Hey! This is pretty good! I mean, of course it's good – it's Empery cuisine! Commander, open wide and I'll give you a dumpling alley oop. Say "aah"!
name: Steaming-Hot Treat

desc: *yawn*, finally, I get to lie down. Tell you what, I'm gonna have a nap... Hm? The ceremony's still not over? Hrmh... Look, it's not important. You should just come lie next to me, Commander!
name: Sleeping White Beauty

desc: O-class battlecruiser – Brünhilde.
name: Brünhilde

desc: Hah! This donut now belongs to Brünhilde! Alright, now for the finish line... C-Commander? Sorry, but there's no time for chit-chat... I'll be going now!
name: Grain-Seizing Grani

desc: O-class battlecruiser – Alvitr.
name: Alvitr

desc: Oh, Commander. You may have noticed that the air conditioner is busted. I surmised from its volume levels that it was at its limit, but now that it's broken... life has become a struggle.
name: Muspel's Torrid Secrets

desc: Type 1928 battlecruiser – Admiral Zenker.
name: Admiral Zenker

desc: You want me to spill the beans? Heh. Hate to disappoint you... Phew... Did that sound good? I thought up other responses I could try, too.
name: Fun with...Interrogations?

desc: Bismarck-class battleship – Bismarck.
name: Bismarck

desc: My sincerest apologies for the delay, Commander. Ah, excuse me... as the fleet leader of the Iron Blood, I'm expected to wear this outfit to various formal occasions. Just putting it on seems to make me inadvertently change the way I speak...
name: Beacon of the Iron Blood

desc: Welcome, what would you like to order? ...If you want, we can drop this charade. I'm not used to being a waiter anyway, so I prefer it this way. Hehe.
name: Iron-Black Elysium

desc: C-Commander? Well, as you see, I was wrapping your Christmas present, but now the surprise has been spoiled. I suppose this moment calls for a "Merry Christmas," hmm?
name: Unpacked Surprise

desc: You've arrived, Commander – or rather, my sweetheart in eternal vow. I know I can't wear a stiff expression forever, but when I think about the days to come under your guidance, I feel so needy all of a sudden. Yes, it's like you say... just keep smiling.
name: Wedding Dominion

desc: Bismarck-class battleship, Tirpitz.
name: Tirpitz

desc: Summer... In the past, it was always just a hot and stifling season... But now...? Doesn't my outfit tell the whole story? Let's get going, there's bound to be a lot of people on the beach.
name: Snow-Melting Summer

desc: I bet Bismarck must've been thinking about how to invite me to the party, but ended up asking you to do it, Commander. Hehe... Let's get going soon. It's best not to keep her waiting.
name: Iron Blood Snowstorm

desc: They have a peculiar way of wishing a happy New Year in the Sakura Empire. In line with their traditions, I've put on this new outfit. I hope it doesn't... look strange on me. ...You like it? I see... That being the case, I'll keep wearing it for the time
name: Seasonal Pine and the Frost Flower

desc: It's all right, I just got here myself. I will say, it's strangely reassuring to know I'm not the only one nervous on this day.
name: A Vase for the Frost Flower

desc: Congratulations on your new record, Commander. This glory alone has given meaning to my time spent waiting. Now, rest assured while I do maintenance on your car.
name: Pit Stop Standby

desc: H-class battleship – Ulrich von Hutten
name: Ulrich von Hutten

desc: *sigh* Do you really have to bother me during my break? ...It's a joke, no need to take it so seriously. I was looking for someone to kill some time with anyway.
name: Mayhem Maid

desc: That was a pretty good race – reckon you'll get first place next time, though? ...Hmh. Easier said than done. You know they won't settle for second place – and hopefully neither will you, Commander.
name: Ignition Matrician

desc: Hm? You look like you've seen a ghost... Oh, you thought I'd have gone home by now? Heh... Who cares? It's not like I've got anything better to do.
name: What Comes After the Bell

desc: Hmph, so the day has finally come... I'm not surprised. I knew from the day we met that this would happen. After all... the poison called love is both a blessing and a curse.
name: Liebestrank

desc: Helgoland-class battleship – Thüringen.
name: Thüringen

desc: You, mop the floor. You, take care of the windows. Once that's done... Ah, Commander. Excuse us, we're in the middle of cleaning the area. If you have need of me, I must ask you to wait.
name: Tidying in the Moonlight

desc: Bismarck-class battleship – Bismarck.
name: Bismarck Zwei

desc: Ah, you've already gotten changed, Commander? I'm just... Well, I need to do something about my hair before I go back in the water.
name: Crystal-Clear Holiday

desc: This necklace's glimmer and texture in the steam is truly splendid... Oh, Commander. Would you care to come in and share in this scene you've gifted me?
name: Bathed in Brightness and Spirit

desc: Battleship – Friedrich der Große.
name: Little Friedrich

desc: Aircraft carrier – Weser.
name: Weser

desc: I've been waiting for you, Comander. As per my sister's recommendation, I've put on this Sakura Empire kimono. It was very tricky to get into, I might add... That aside, how do I look? ...Good enough, I hope?
name: Obsidian Elegance

desc: Ah, I've kept you waiting. I do apologize that it took so long to get changed into this outfit. Now, Commander, won't you come show me your chivalry and escort me down these stairs?
name: Urbane Onyx

desc: I've been waiting forever for this season to arrive. It's a perfect time, the waves wait for nobody, so I'm off for now. I'll make sure to teach you how to surf later, so look forward to it.
name: Wave-Washed Paradise

desc: Oh, welcome, Commander. As you can see, I'm just taking a break. Nobody thought you'd come right now. So... How would you like to be served?
name: Offtime Cafe

desc: Jade-class aircraft carrier – Elbe
name: Elbe

desc: Thank you all for waiting! Large mugs of Iron Blood beer, just as ord–– W-waaah?! Nnngh...! Phew, somehow managed to not spill anything... Wh-what's your deal?!
name: Time to Show Off?

desc: Still not here yet...? Geez, I'll give the Commander what-for for coming later than me... Huh? C-Commander? N-no, I happened to come an hour early, is all...
name: Pure-Hearted Bad Girl

desc: Jade-class aircraft carrier – Jade.
name: Jade

desc: *lick*... Hmm. The fact that you can just stand there must mean that you don't mind the heat. It's okay, though. If you don't come in, I'm more than happy to have this pool all to myself~♪
name: A Lick of Summer

desc: That's right, I'm the witch Jade, the most famous idol in all the world! Did you come running when you heard my name, hero? I was just about to broadcast my new song, so you'll be the perfect helper. Heheh♪
name: A Good Girl's Magic

desc: Aircraft carrier, Graf Zeppelin.
name: Graf Zeppelin

desc: So the Second Movement is a Lento of the summer and the sea? So be it... Since we will arrive at the Finale eventually, I suppose I can enjoy this moment of fleeting peace with you.
name: Beachside Urd

desc: Aircraft carrier Graf Zeppelin
name: Zeppy

desc: Graf Zeppelin-class aircraft carrier – Peter Strasser.
name: Peter Strasser

desc: Eugen, you said that this was is a ceremonial outfit from the Sakura Empire? Surprisingly, it does seem to suit me rather well. Oh, I'm supposed to offer my well-wishes for the New Year at this time, yes?
name: Chronos's Kalendae

desc: You already know, don't you? Since I spent so much of my precious time changing into a dress for your sake... Heh, I'll be taking plenty of your time in return. Hehehe.
name: A Moment Frozen in Pure White

desc: Heheheh, it may be a new year, but don't forget to be punctual. Just as you've refurnished this study into a Dragon Empery style, I've changed clothes to match. This little book club is just for the two of us, and I mean to suit the mood.
name: Lustrous Jade of the Golden House

desc: Grossflugzeugkreuzer (large aviation cruiser) A Type II – Fritz Rumey.
name: Fritz Rumey

desc: Hm? It's you. Surprised by my appearance? Hmm... My apologies. I was thinking about how to rectify discipline inside the shop. At any rate, welcome.
name: Schwarzes Kaninchen

desc: Iron Blood Type VIIC submarine – U-81.
name: U-81

desc: *Ugh*... I figured this bulky dress would be hard to move in... Huh? I look pretty? Aha, ahaha... You're makin' me blush...
name: Soft Serenade

desc: Over here, Commander! I came because you said we were going to go moon-viewing together! I even brought tea and mooncakes.
name: Lantern-Lit Full Moon

desc: Iron Blood Type VIIB submarine – U-47.
name: U-47

desc: I haven't seen much of the world on land... Commander, want to explore it with me?
name: Rookie Rider
