desc: Sigh... I'd much rather be in a nice, quiet place like this over the din and clamor of the venue... Wouldn't you agree, Commander? I see. Well, come sit here then.
name: Eigenen Raum

desc: Coming through! Steer clear! Oh, it's you, Commander. Talk to you later – I've got coffee to deliver.
name: Urban Maid

desc: An empty study with a cushy couch. The perfect place to relax. Whew... Go ahead and read a book if you want, Commander. If that'll be all then I'm gonna take a nap.
name: Sanguine Moon Sojourn

desc: Nice. I've found a legendary luck-bringing carp, like... Oh. I almost had it, too... Sorry, Commander.
name: Hook, Line, and Sinker

desc: Iron Blood Type VIIC submarine – U-557.
name: U-557

desc: Iron Blood Type VIIC submarine – U-556.
name: U-556

desc: It's me, U-556, all prettied up! Eheheheh, we're gonna have lots of fun at this party, Commander! Come on, let's go!
name: Party Knight!

desc: I'm still Parzival of the Seas, even on land! Lord Bismarck entrusted me with these goods and I'm gonna keep them safe! Now step up and try your luck, hooligans!
name: Prairie Knight

desc: Iron Blood Type VIIB submarine – U-73.
name: U-73

desc: It's time for science class with U-73! Now, Commander, let's try out an exhilarating and positively fascinating experiment!
name: Science Rules!

desc: In today's chemistry lesson, we'll learn how to make a warming cup of tea and an optional concoction to enhance its flavor! Will you do the honor of taste-testing it, Commander?
name: New Year's Chemistry

desc: Iron Blood Type VIIC submarine – U-101.
name: U-101

desc: Commander, welcome to the school band! Why'd I join the band? The reason's simple - there's no Motorbike Club at school, haha! Just kidding~! Actually, I'm quite fond of music as well, heh.
name: Ironbrass Trombonist

desc: Iron Blood Type IXC submarine – U-522.
name: U-522

desc: Raaaawr. U-110 is a shaaaark. Fear meeee. Mess with me and I'll bite yooouuu.
name: U-110

desc: Whenever I play games with Bulldog, I always end up losing. Frustratinggg. That's why... I'll study hard. One day, I'll winnnn.
name: Kleiner Hai

desc: I have to wear beautiful clothes to a party, or so Bulldog said. So, I had everyone help me pick out beautiful clothes. Commander, I'm beautiful, right? Eh... cute?
name: A Cute, Sharky Reverie

desc: The horned idol U-110 splashes onto the staaage. I'll sing all the baddies to obliviooon. I'm scaaary. Raaawr. Raaawr♪
name: Garnished Supershark

desc: Commander, happy new yeeear. I'm no bunny, I'm a shaaark. Not a cute shark, but a crimson, scaaary shark. Raaawr.
name: New Year, Small Shark

desc: I'm gathering mushrooms, not garlic cloooves. The edible ones are gonna go in a hearty hot pot that'll warm me and my frieeends. Raaawr.
name: Springtime Shark

desc: Iron Blood Type VIIC submarine – U-96.
name: U-96

desc: Nice timing. I just finished an intense battle. The result...? Of course I won. What? Did you want to have a match against me?
name: Secret Gaming Session

desc: Mmgh... Guh... Ahhh! These things are heavier than they look... Oh, there you are. You work out too, do ya? Feel free to join me if you've not just come to tease me.
name: How Heavy Are Those Barbells?

desc: Sup. If it isn't our Commander. Got bored already because you shattered all your previous records? Or, did you run into some mechanical issues? ...Huh, you're here to ask for my support? Did the butterscotch get to your brain or what? Despite the way I look, I've been on the sidelines cheering you on this whole time.
name: Wolfen Dolly

desc: Iron Blood Type IXA submarine – U-37.
name: U-37

desc: Now then, please lend your ears to this song I shall offer you... Wait, Commander, are you spacing out again? Even though I went through all this trouble to learn this song from my friends in the Sakura fleet... Please pay attention, okay? I'm starting ov
name: New Year's Nightingale

desc: There ya are, Partner! I'm tellin' ya, these punks running around the port are getting bolder and bolder. It's time someone cracked down on 'em! Anyway, I'll handle this stuff like usual – you go and do your thing, Partner.
name: Keeping Peace in the Streets

desc: Iron Blood Type VIIC submarine – U-410.
name: U-410

desc: Happy Lunar New Year. Have you cooked up a scheme for this year's festival? Hehehe~ I'm of course talking about giving out New Year's gifts and hanging up decorations. I've devised a master plan of my own.
name: Spring Festival Scheme

desc: And for my finishing move... maybe something like this? Heehee. What do your eyes think, Commander?
name: Practice Makes Perfect

desc: Iron Blood Type VIIC submarine – U-1206
name: U-1206

desc: Welcome! Oh, Hey, Commander! Heheh, so how do you like my maid getup? Looks pretty nice, if I do say so myself!
name: Maid Just for You

desc: Type VIIA submarine – U-31.
name: U-31

desc: Why I didn't leave after classes were over? 'Cause I wanted to wait for you to come pick me up, duh! And I waited a looong time! Heehee, now that we're alone... maybe we could do something fun together!
name: Let's Go Home

desc: Type VIIC submarine – U-552.
name: U-552

desc: Ahem... Excuse me, since you've come aboard on our special sightseeing tour, please do try to keep up with me. Rest assured, this bus is perfectly safe and I can promise you a good time.
name: Special Sightseeing Service

desc: *sigh*... Taking care of Meowfficers is more work than you'd think... They're awfully needy for support units. Commander, make absolute sure you don't turn out like them.
name: Keeper of the Comf-Fort

desc: N-no way... I lost the gear I worked so hard for because the upgrade failed, and now I'm completely out of gold... Ugh, I'm going to have to go farm the dungeon all over again...
name: Upgrade Failure?!

desc: Sure, I've worn black dresses in the past, but this time I decided to incorporate a bit of red and white, per Eugen's suggestion. This is sure to invite the Commander to dance wi– C-Commander?! Did you just get here? I see. Uhh... How do you like my dress?
name: Tanz der Blumen

desc: Heavy cruiser – Roon.
name: Roon

desc: Such a delightful party with our wonderful friends in this peaceful harbor... It's wonderful, really... But, it's all so boring...
name: Dark Red Grin

desc: It's so nice getting away from the bustling party hall and being alone with you, Commander. I'm eager to see what we'll do now as your idea of a... "break"~
name: Viridescent Lullaby

desc: Commander? You've not only filled the void in my heart, but also wholly embraced my fervid feelings... Ah, you really make me want to do things... Unforgivable things, like opening my heart for you.
name: The Abyssal Embrace

desc: Battleship – Friedrich der Große.
name: Friedrich der Große

desc: I see, so this is a "kimono" from the Sakura Empire. Exquisitely crafted, comfortable to the touch, and elegantly designed... How to wear it? ...My child, what are you talking about?
name: Dark Raiments of Gagaku

desc: Welcome, my child. What do you desire tonight? That which ripples in my cup? This sweet, red fruit? Or to sate the desires sleeping deep, deep in your heart?
name: One Summer Night's Intimacy

desc: Ahh, the dreamlike beauty of this variation... let us write down this movement so that it may continue forever, my sweet child.
name: Zeremonie of the Cradle

desc: Light cruiser – Mainz.
name: Mainz

desc: Ah! Changed already? Just wait a minute... No, you don't have to leave. I'm almost done.
name: The Silkiest Brew

desc: Commander, come join me in rest. ...Hm? I look unusually relaxed? This is a rare break, and I don't plan to waste it by being stuffy.
name: A Blend of Serenity

desc: Battlecruiser – Odin.
name: Odin

desc: I thought I would never have time to pursue the fine arts, and yet here I am now. Your thoughts, Commander? Eastern as this calligraphy may be, does it not suit the connotations of my name?
name: Black Strokes upon Blank Snow

desc: Large cruiser – Ägir.
name: Ägir

desc: Hmph. They think being a maid is so difficult, do they? I could do this with my eyes clo– What?! H-how long have YOU been here?!
name: Iron Blood's Dragon Maid

desc: New decorations, new outfits, and countless preparations to make... Lunar New Year is quite the busy time of year. Go on, see to your duties. I'm well aware how essential you are to this holiday's smooth operation. Just don't keep me waiting all day. Heehee.
name: Golden Dragon Among Auspicious Clouds

desc: Well, I'm pleasantly surprised. A comfortable seat, high-quality beverages, and a nice private room... Hm? Are you going to stand there the whole day? Don't just stare at me like that...
name: One-on-One Leisure Time

desc: Aircraft carrier – August von Parseval.
name: August von Parseval

desc: My hair is a mess... There we go. No, I don't need a hand. I am here to serve you in this fleeting dream of yours. Enjoy it while it lasts. Hehehe.
name: The Conquered Unhulde

desc: You've come, my familiar. I wondered when you'd awake from your... Hm? A little nicer than usual? Yes, because even I have my moments of placidness. Would you prefer that I was more harsh to you?
name: The Unhulde's Midday Respite

desc: Battlecruiser – Prinz Rupprecht.
name: Prinz Rupprecht

desc: Woah, so this is the Dragon Empery's "Spring Festival" that I've heard so much about. But, why are they celebrating it in the middle of winter? And you, Commander – why are you helping with such a grandiose... Whuah?! What was that noise?!
name: The Gate Dragon's Advent

desc: You're late! I've been waiting ages for you! ...We never agreed to meet tonight? If I say we did, then we did! Anyway, you should feel bad! That's obvious!
name: Midnight Pearl

desc: Destroyer – Felix Schultz.
name: Felix Schultz

desc: My, my. I'm quite surprised you're still able to stay awake. As expected of the Commander– even a dose of Felix Schultz's special concoction isn't enough to put you under... but that ends here. It's your fault for peeping on me slacking off in the first place, so be nice and obedient and succumb to me already~♪
name: Sweet, Sleepy "Revenge"

desc: Heavy cruiser – Hindenburg.
name: Hindenburg

desc: It's just the two of us now, Contract Binder. Come – play a game with me and immerse yourself in the pleasures this place offers. The loser of this game, of course, must accept a punishment tonight♡
name: Delirious Duel

desc: Battleship – Mecklenburg.
name: Mecklenburg

desc: Commander – I mean – Imperator! You've been seeing me far too little as of late, which has left me in a very sour mood. I will punish you by inscribing my seal on your body, so that you'll remember me! Um... How do I do this, again?
name: Branding Witchcraft

desc: An Shan-class destroyer, No. 1 - Anshan (101)
name: An Shan

desc: "Boundless is the beauty of evening's glow, but alas––" ...Oh, that doesn't have any special meaning, I've just been hanging around Hai Tien too much. (*whispers*) But, it's true... Our time together is far too short, just like the evening light...
name: Setting Sun, Hearts as One

desc: An Shan, retrofitting complete! With this new power, Commander, I'll protect both you and my sisters! But first... Umm, I need to double-check how these missiles work...!
name: An Shan (Retrofit)

desc: An Shan-class destroyer No.2 - Fu Shun (102)
name: Fu Shun

desc: Heh-hey! Just hooked us another baozi~! We're in for one heckuva haul today! ...Eh? Huh, Commander?! Th-this is, uhh... yeah, we're just playing a normal game... totally...
name: The Unbreakable Baozi Heist

desc: Fu Shun – retrofitting complete! Reporting in! Commander, if something happens and you need someone reliable, I'm your girl!
name: Fu Shun (Retrofit)

desc: An Shan-class destroyer No. 3 - Chang Chun (103)
name: Chang Chun

desc: Ta-da! My pajamas are finally finished! Now to snuggle up until I'm all warm! Eh~ Ehhh? But sis, I don't want to get out! Ack, did Tai Yuan purposely make this tail big and thick to make it easier for you?
name: The Joy of Spring

desc: Commander, hurry up and plug your ears! Th-this isn't a joke! Um... Seriously, that big ol' doozy over there is about to blow!
name: Fortune Arrives in Red

desc: All done with my retrofit~ Now, time to test out my new toys... Err, I mean, time to test the firepower of my new armaments! Oh, watch your head, Commander! Wouldn't want one of the missiles to lock onto you.
name: Chang Chun (Retrofit)

desc: An Shan-class destroyer No. 4 - Tai Yuan (104)
name: Tai Yuan

desc: O-on behalf of the An Shan class, we wish a prosperous, happy, and healthy new year to Commander, and to everyone here at port... Umm... even though I made this outfit, I feel a bit embarrassed wearing it... Eh? It looks good on me? Um... th-thank you...
name: The Golden Dragon's Festivities

desc: Commander? Did Ting An tell you to try out this ergonomic cushion, too? Okay, I'll make room... There, okay! Come lie down with me!
name: Two Hearts, One Cushion

desc: Phew... Tai Yuan, retrofit complete. Thanks for supporting me this whole time, Commander. With this new equipment, I'll be able to get one step closer to catching up to my sisters.
name: Tai Yuan (Retrofit)

desc: Vulcan Stettin 1,000-ton torpedo destroyer – Lung Wu.
name: Lung Wu

desc: Happy New Year, Commander... Having that said, the others said they had a surprise for me, but then ended up banning me from the kitchen... I didn't do anything bad, did I? I'm real worried... Can't I at least take a look at what's going on there? Ugh... How about you go check it out in my stead? P-pretty please, Commander!
name: Ascendant Dragon's Spring Feast

desc: Woah, the corals look so pretty as they swish and sway... There's a whole world of color underneath the sea... I can come visit again any time I'd like? Thank you so much, Commander!
name: Invitation to Jade Seas

desc: Vulcan Stettin 1,000-ton torpedo destroyer – Hu Pen.
name: Hu Pen

desc: Let's usher in the New Year with the sound of gongs and firecrackers~! Whaddya think? Lion dances are pretty awesome, aren't they? So, Commander, who's got more oomph in their dance steps? Me, or Lung Wu? C'mon, hurry up and decide~!
name: Prancing Tiger Welcomes the Spring

desc: Chang Feng-class destroyer – Fei Yuen.
name: Fei Yuen

desc: H-Happy New Year, Commander... Umm, uhh... C-could you please help me down first? ....Waah, I promise I won't have any more "adventures" in the kitchen...
name: Flying Clouds, Flailing Pranks

desc: Chang Feng-class destroyer – Chang Feng.
name: Chang Feng

desc: Oh, Commander~ Please give me a moment; Fei Yuen, Fu Po, and I are still finishing up our spring cleaning. Why don't you come inside for now and have some warm tea?
name: Cozy Spring Cleaning

desc: Commander, this is the new Ru-ware tea set I just purchased. Absolutely beautiful, isn't it? We have a custom to bring out the best things for those you care about, which is why I decided to invite you~♪
name: A Sky Blue Eclipsing Jade

desc: Chang Feng-class destroyer – Fu Po.
name: Fu Po

desc: Oh... Well, shoot, you found me... Shhhhh! Don't tell anyone that I'm here though! Seriously, Commander, I'm begging you!
name: Mischievous Tidings

desc: Cruiser, Yat Sen.
name: Yat Sen

desc: I am truly honored to be able to share this wondrous scenery with you on such a festive occasion, Commander. Umm... I'm not just saying that out of courtesy. We rarely get opportunities like this, so I'm somewhat flattered...
name: Paragon of Celestial Grace

desc: I am honored that you could make time in your busy schedule to accept my invitation... Hmm? There's no need to be so formal? Heehee. Well, the tea happens to be ready now, so please sit down next to me~
name: Pristine Leaves, Rich Warmth

desc: Commander, thank you for waiting for me. Though I am unworthy of this honor, thank you so much...
name: Coronal Afterglow

desc: There's no need to worry, Commander. I will be fine now. Please allow me to serve you once more in this new form.
name: Yat Sen (Retrofit)

desc: Ning Hai-class Light Cruiser, Ning Hai
name: Ning Hai

desc: Summer’s all about the beach! And the beach is all about good food! Commander, let’s find something delicious to eat!
name: Summer Hunger

desc: Happy Mid-Autumn Festival! I heard that if you pray to the moon today, you’ll become as pretty as the Goddess of the Moon! ...Eh? You’re gonna pray too?
name: Moon Palace Rabbit

desc: We haven't had to worry as much about things like food since we joined the fleet, but that doesn't mean we can just throw money around...! Anyway, I'm the older of the "Dragon Sisters," Ning Hai! Great to be here!
name: Dragon Sisters! -N

desc: Commander, what are you spacing out for? Over here! They say that you'll have good fortune if you give this thing a shake!
name: Springtime Sojourn

desc: Yat Sen said this look would be best for a party, but, is it really okay? I'm not used to having my hair down like this...
name: Gorgeous Violet

desc: Good boy. Chew thoroughly before you swallow. I never thought I'd help with a charity event for nature, but Da Bao's made a lot of new friends because of it. Keep up the good work, Commander and Ping!
name: Da Bao's Friend!

desc: Woah! Da Bao, lend me a hand here! Don't let that octopus get away! ...Oh, Commander, Happy Lunar New Year! Uhh, the kitchen prep's going fine... Huh? You're gonna help? Heheh~ don't worry about us! Just leave everything here to me 'n Ping!
name: Hectic Kitchen

desc: Yes! … this feels good. Thank you, Commander. In order to live up to your expectations, from now on, I will be more serious around you, Commander. Hey, don't run!
name: Ning Hai (Retrofit)

desc: Ning Hai-class Light Cruser, Ping Hai
name: Ping Hai

desc: Compared to pork buns, shaved ice is tastier. Compared to shaved ice, fireworks are prettier. Compared to fireworks, what I care for the most is...
name: Summer Vacation

desc: Happy Mid-Autumn Festival, Commander! Mooncakes, pomegranates, and osmanthus cakes... what a wonderful holiday!
name: Osmanthus Moon Rabbit

desc: Big sister says that even though we have some money now, we still have to save as much as we can. Um... Anyway, I'm the younger "Dragon Sister," Ping Hai. Erm... I'm kind of hungry. Do you maybe have something to eat?
name: Dragon Sisters! -P

desc: The Sakura Empire has lots of delicious food that I've never tried before! Yeah! It's a great place!
name: Great Gourmet Expedition

desc: There's always a lot of delicious food at these parties! But, my sister said I'm not allowed to have any cake until everyone's gotten their slice... Baobao, let's be on our best behavior!
name: Delicious Crimson

desc: Cheese! That came out looking good! Hehehe~ I'm really glad to be a part of this charity event for nature, along with you and my sister! Baobao is really glad too!
name: Baobao's Buddy!

desc: You can't have a hearty banquet without crab meat! Which is why... I'm not letting you get away! Oh, Commander, did you want to lend a hand? It's okay though, my sister and I have got things under wrap here.
name: Lively Banquet Preparations

desc: Hi~ya! Hmm... this feels... nothing special. Baobao looks happy though... Never mind, Commander, Ping Hai is hungry!
name: Ping Hai (Retrofit)

desc: Chao Ho-class protected cruiser – Ying Swei.
name: Ying Swei

desc: Happy New Year, Commander. I've come to deliver you blessings for this coming year... Next, you're going to ask for a red envelope, right? Hehe, just teasing~
name: Snowy Pine's Warmth

desc: Commander, Happy New Year! Chao Ho and I are preparing for this year's Spring Festival, and as you can see... we're in the middle of a little "intermission." Hehe, don't worry, there's nothing you need to help out with. Just take a seat over there and enjoy the show~
name: Frolicking Flowers, Verse I

desc: Heehee, if it isn't the Commander. Your timing is perfect~ I was thinking I might take a break here... While you're here, why don't you rest in the pool with me?
name: Blue Waves, Limpid Summer

desc: Chao Ho-class protected cruiser – Chao Ho.
name: Chao Ho

desc: Happy New Year, Commander! This red envelope is my gift to you... after all, that's my responsibility as a big sister! Anyway, hurry up and take it!
name: Plum Blossom's Illumination

desc: Happy... New Year... Commander... Gah, this isn't the time for pleasantries! And you, help me catch the dumb fluffball that ran off with our ornaments! Jeez, why is this happening when I'm in the middle of getting ready for the Spring Festival?!
name: Frolicking Flowers, Verse II

desc: H-hey, you, warn me before you come in next time! I was just looking for my swimsuit... F-forget it, okay? I'm not trying to chase you out! If you're coming in, then come in already!
name: Azure Ripples, Shimmering Sun

desc: Hai Tien-class protected cruiser – Hai Tien.
name: Hai Tien

desc: What a serendipitous meeting this is, Commander. I was simply searching for a place where I could leisurely enjoy my poetry manuscript. Since fate has brought both of us here, why don't we accompany each other for a while?
name: Verse-Weaver at the Water's Edge

desc: Through dance of gossamer silk, the apsaras' grace soars... Oh, I'm simply reciting something I just happened to pick up on. What do you think, Commander? If I've captured your attention, I suppose this was worth our while~
name: Soaring Apsaras

desc: Sorry to keep you waiting. It took quite some time to prepare my dress as well as this lantern... Yes, when you said we would go on a "night stroll," I made some preparations in accordance to what my ancestors once did. Now then, shall we set off?
name: Autumn Night of Wandering Spirits

desc: Welcome back, Commander. I made some tasty pastries for you. ...Huh? You want the one in my chest? Th-that doesn't count.
name: Baker of Heart into Sweets

desc: "Dragon-shaped jade comb in hand, tied is her hair with gold ribbons and phoenix's hairpin" ...Thank you for waiting for me, Commander. Long have I dreamt for this moment to come true... Please allow me to remain by your side forevermore. N-now then, I believe the next thing for us to do is... c-consumate... *blushes*
name: Luan-Feng's Everlasting Duet

desc: Hai Tien-class protected cruiser – Hai Chi.
name: Hai Chi

desc: Look, Commander! I've become a goddess from the Dragon Empery's folklore! Hehehe! Let me perform for you a song and dance number I just learned!
name: A Dance Among the Lotuses

desc: CNT Shipyard 1,800-ton small protected cruiser – Chi An.
name: Chi An

desc: May blessings reach you this coming spring. Hm? My outfit? Heehee. Since the ever-so-busy Commander came to see me on this special occasion, I naturally had to put in some effort too– Now then, set aside all your worries, and come enjoy this wonderful evening with me~♪
name: Lanternlit Stroll

desc: Phew... Fancy seeing the person of my dreams AFTER I've woken up! Heehee, if this is as fate decrees... Weary traveler, come to me and rest your tired legs.
name: Exotic Dreamland

desc: Hai Yung-class protected cruiser – Hai Yung.
name: Hai Yung

desc: Very well, Commander, I'll leave the photography to you. I entrust you to capture my grace and elegance and record it into memory! Just so you're clear though, th-this is just an outfit that's in vogue... It's not like I chose to wear it for you or anything!
name: Maple Impressions

desc: CNT-68 armored cruiser – Chien Wu.
name: Chien Wu

desc: There's still time. Let's set out once I've finished adjusting my dress... If you have nothing better to do, at least put on some tea.
name: Dressed for Just Tonight

desc: Don't just stare – help me... Look, I meant that in the "help me balance" sense... Are you trying to take my shoes off?
name: Dressed for Just Tonight

desc: Come here instead of staring blankly at the door. It took me all night to tailor-sew these details. It should perfectly meet everything you requested... Come closer and I'll listen to your important feedback before anything else.
name: All-Nighter Masterpiece

desc: 1913 Naval Expansion Project 26,000-ton battlecruiser – Huan Ch'ang.
name: Huan Ch'ang

desc: Happy New Year, Commander. Hmm? I look a bit different from usual? Why of course, it's because it was chosen to suit your tastes by none other than Chi An. Even this mask is brand new. I look "like a fairy from the sacred mountains," you say? I wonder... who taught you to say something like that?
name: Dance Beneath the Moonlight

desc: Seaplane carrier - Chen Hai.
name: Chen Hai

desc: You're here, Commander, just as promised. How do you like the atmosphere in here? Hehe, take a seat and enjoy the tea slowly. After all, we have plenty of time~
name: Vestibule of Wonders

desc: Oh my, if it isn't the Commander... Have you also come to escape the heat? What a serendipitous meeting... Or, did you perhaps have some other goal in mind? Heehee...
name: Cerulean Ripples

desc: Oh, Commander, have you come to see me? Yes, as you can see, I've been studying the art of embroidery– Just like Go, it helps me organize my thoughts and see things from a broader perspective. Why don't you give it a try as well, Commander? Heehee~
name: Sylvan Garden's Embroidery

desc: Just as promised, I present myself before you in a brand new form. Heehee... Since we have plenty of time, why don't you come take a seat, enjoy the fragrance of tea with me, and envision our future?
name: Chen Hai (Retrofit)

desc: Seaplane carrier – Hwah Jah.
name: Hwah Jah

desc: I am Hwah Jah, now in zombie form. It is an honor to see you– hmm? What's wrong, Commander? Everyone else is getting dressed up for the occasion, so I figured I'd get in on the action too... Is there something wrong with that?
name: The Festive Undead

desc: As you can see, Commander, I've completed my retrofitting. So, umm, are you surprised by my new appearance? Don't worry, though. I'll always be the same Hwah Jah you know and love~ Though, if I had to pick something different about myself... I might be a bit more open towards some fun and exciting things~♪
name: Hwah Jah (Retrofit)

desc: Seaplane carrier – Ting An.
name: Ting An

desc: I see, so this is how you're supposed to knead dough... Hmm? Commander? As you can see, I'm currently trying to make baozi. Would you like to help out?
name: Tender White Jade

desc: Umm... Alright, time to take a photo in the on-set mirror and send it to Commander... And there. Just as Commander said, it'd be disastrous if my new swimsuit's design were to get leaked... B-but if I don't do this, our plans will totally be ruined!
name: Undercover or Uncovered?!

desc: An Shan-class destroyer, No. 1 - Anshan (101)
name: 导驱type20测试机

desc: An Shan-class destroyer, No. 1 - Anshan (101)
name: 导驱type21测试机

desc: Light cruiser - Harbin.
name: Harbin

desc: Pheeew! I just love blue skies and a fair ocean breeze. Since you're already here, Commander, set aside all the boring paperwork and business stuff, and come enjoy the waves!
name: Union Between Sea and Sky

desc: Hey, there you are. Remember what I said about the two of us being partners in crime? Well, actions speak louder than words, so I reserved this whole cruise for just the two of us. Whaddya say? Sound good, partner?
name: Set Sail for Summer Treasure

desc: Sorry to keep you waiting, Commander. So, how's my new look? It's got me a bit embarrassed... But, well, all that matters is that you like it.
name: Red Paeonia

desc: Soldati-class destroyer – Carabiniere.
name: Carabiniere

desc: Lady Veneto advised me to enjoy my time off by changing into something befitting the occasion... Um, Commander, I d-don't look strange, do I?
name: Refreshing Sundress

desc: Alfredo Oriani-class destroyer – Vincenzo Gioberti.
name: Vincenzo Gioberti

desc: "To refuse a fair signorina's invitation would be most uncouth"... Hehe~ Now, Commander, would you like to partake in some refreshments? Rest assured, they're all non-alcoholic♪
name: Fair Lady's Invitation

desc: Maestrale-class destroyer – Maestrale.
name: Maestrale

desc: It's way too crowded on the beach... I'd much rather be– Oh, Commander? Are you not good with crowded places either...?
name: Lonesome Beachfarer

desc: Maestrale-class destroyer – Libeccio.
name: Libeccio

desc: Libeccio's heading towards the sea! Commander, let's go to where all the excitement is!
name: Beachbound Southwestern Wind!

desc: Navigatori-class destroyer – Nicoloso da Recco.
name: Nicoloso da Recco

desc: I know this one! It's that Sakura Empire watermelon-smashing game! Just put the melon over there, Commander! ...Relax, it'll be fine! Have some faith in my navigator's intuition! Ready? Then let's go!
name: To a Smashing Voyage!

desc: Capitani Romani-class ship – Pompeo Magno.
name: Pompeo Magno

desc: *yawn*... Nothing's impossible when you've got Captain Pompey... Hmm? Commander? Wait, I fell asleep? Seems I did... Drat, I forgot what I even came here for...
name: Quaver Daydream

desc: Oriani-class destroyer - Alfredo Oriani.
name: Alfredo Oriani

desc: Found you, Commander! How would you grade this outfit of mine? ...No, no, I wasn't asking if it looked cute or pretty, I wanted to know if I was wearing it right in the first place! You know what though, I think I'll take those compliments~
name: Vivacious Vivace

desc: Navigatori-class destroyer – Emanuele Pessagno.
name: Emanuele Pessagno

desc: Eek! Wh-why are you guys tugging at my stockings... P-please stop that... C-Commander, please... Hurry and come help me! Waah...
name: Backstage Blunders

desc: Capitani Romani-class large destroyer – Attilio Regolo.
name: Attilio Regolo

desc: Welcome to my humble abode! Bunnies, kitty-cats, and the Commander... The gang's all here! Today's tale is gonna be a wild one!
name: Castle of Inspiration

desc: I wanted to try making a fairy-tale entrance. Did I look good, Commander? When you saw me come down from the sky, did you sense destined romance?!
name: Angel from Above

desc: Oriani-class destroyer – Giosuè Carducci.
name: Giosuè Carducci

desc: Traveler from afar, allow me to pen a welcoming verse with this dance... Why'd I stop? Umm... S-silence is golden, as they say...
name: Verses in Balance

desc: Navigatori-class destroyer – Ugolino Vivaldi.
name: Ugolino Vivaldi

desc: E-examination complete... This "sick" claw machine seems to have mistaken me for a plushie... O-or did it realize how much I wanted the Commander to take me home?
name: An Unexpected Catch!

desc: Duca degli Abruzzi-class light cruiser – Luigi di Savoia Duca degli Abruzzi.
name: Duca degli Abruzzi

desc: Good evening, Commander. Here to unwind after a day's work, I take it? Even dignitaries desire a bit of luxury sometimes. Hahaha.
name: Lustrous Onyx Sirenetta

desc: Duca degli Abruzzi-class light cruiser – Giuseppe Garibaldi.
name: Giuseppe Garibaldi

desc: I am the evil swan Odile! Where oh where is my prince? ...Oh, it's you, Commander. My lines aside, pretty good performance, right?
name: Noble Ivory Plumes

desc: Giussano-class light cruiser – Bartolomeo Colleoni.
name: Bartolomeo Colleoni

desc: Hrmm... Romance novel analysis shows that this pose is the most likely to succeed... Ah. C-Commander, there you are... Ahem. "What business do you have in my private chambers?"
name: The Empress' Romantic Ambush

desc: Giussano-class light cruiser – Alberto di Giussano.
name: Alberto di Giussano

desc: O-ooohohoho... Look what I've done, knocking down the clothing rack. I suppose this is the perfect time to show you my clothing collection!
name: A Magnificent Mistake

desc: Trento-class heavy cruiser – Trento.
name: Trento

desc: The summer's scorching heat is alleviated by the ocean~ Commander, why don't you set aside your worries and... cut loose a bit~?
name: Summer's Hotness?

desc: Zara-class heavy cruiser – Zara.
name: Zara

desc: Phew... It's a perfect day for swimming. Oh my, Commander, did you come to swim too? Or... perhaps you had something else in mind? Ehehe~♪
name: Poolside Coincidence

desc: Zara-class heavy cruiser – Pola.
name: Pola

desc: Zara, how dastardly of you to spike the ball at such a time– Eek?! Commander?! Why are you in a place like that?
name: Seaside Coincidence

desc: Trento-class heavy cruiser – Trieste.
name: Trieste

desc: Oh my, are you done with your errands already? Surely, you didn't skip work just to eat lunch with... Ah, sorry for doubting you. Alright, let's go. Trento is waiting for us.
name: Rooftop Lunch Break

desc: Whew... I'm getting dizzy... I'll rest in the breeze for a moment. You okay, Commander? Step out if it's too hot. See, someone will worry about you...
name: Amore Termico

desc: Commander? As you can see, I'm putting into practice the calligraphy knowledge you taught me before. The problem is, I can't seem to nail it... Could you watch for a bit and guide me?
name: A Brush of Springtime Ink

desc: Heavy cruiser – Bolzano.
name: Bolzano

desc: I've never had a knack for dancing or exercise unlike Zara and her sisters... but if asked, I will dance as best as I can! Please keep your eyes on me, Commander!
name: A Flutter in the Moment

desc: So... The premise is that you and I were shipwrecked and ended up on a desert island... Is that right, Commander? I see... But if we weren't actually shipwrecked... what is this treasure, then?
name: Tempting Treasure

desc: I prepared so much for this festival only to run off and hide again on instinct... Oh, Commander?! Um... Are you here to see the fireworks? Or are you here to see... me?
name: A Special Night Just for Us

desc: Zara-class heavy cruiser – Gorizia.
name: Gorizia

desc: These stockings are so annoying to wear... Mmrgh... *sigh*. You can't give up already, Gorizia. If you want the Commander's attention... this is what you have to do!
name: Unrequited Office Love?

desc: Vittorio Veneto-class battleship – Vittorio Veneto.
name: Vittorio Veneto

desc: Nngh, haah... It's awfully sunny today... How long was I asleep, Commander? Oh, it's already lunchtime? In that case, I'll get started on some food. Would you like something as well?
name: The Flower of La Spezia

desc: Vittorio Veneto-class battleship – Littorio.
name: Littorio

desc: A visit to the beach with me? Then you must try your hardest to stand out. Otherwise the eyes of the world will be on me alone.
name: The Glory of Naples

desc: Welcome to Littorio's personal suite. Are you here to issue me a challenge of who can romance the most girls? Hahahah, I'm joking of course! There'd be no fun in a game I would win every single time.
name: Calabria Aurea

desc: Hello there. You'll have to forgive the loungewear; I have scarcely any reason to wear extravagant clothes in my private space away from the public eye.
name: Lounging Emerald

desc: Talk about bad luck, we're caught in a rainstorm right now. Unfortunately, it seems we'll have to wait it out here, Commander.
name: Sitting in the Rain

desc: Vittorio Veneto-class battleship – Roma.
name: Roma

desc: You seem to have known that I would be here. Then stay and spend the night with me. Just the two of us.
name: White Heron of Darkest Night

desc: I see, so this is the kind of vacation you meant. It's quite pleasant, feeling like the queen of the world even when I'm doing nothing. That said, simply sitting here is not enough. Come, Commander, and entertain me as best you can.
name: Vacation Upon the Tiber

desc: Conte di Cavour-class battleship – Conte di Cavour.
name: Conte di Cavour

desc: Commander, take this. Good, for the time being, you are a now a disciple under my command. It is time for us to mete out punishment to the unruly.
name: Fierce Beachside Battle

desc: Conte di Cavour-class battleship – Giulio Cesare.
name: Giulio Cesare

desc: Both exercise and war are at their core about willpower! Now, get ready, Commander! We're not finished until you're dripping with sweat!
name: Fitness Master

desc: Tired already? For goodness' sake, I thought you'd be more reliable than this. Don't go burning all your energy at once, we still have a whole day of recreation ahead of us.
name: High Tide Under the Sunlight

desc: Andrea Doria-class battleship – Andrea Doria.
name: Andrea Doria

desc: "I'm your stewardess, Andrea Doria, here to ensure you have a pleasant flight"... Did I sound natural, Commander? ...Still a bit on the stiff side, huh? *sigh*, this job really isn't easy for first-timers...
name: Have a Safe Flight

desc: Type UP41 battleship – Raffaello.
name: Raffaello

desc: Heheh! You were not invited to this place, and as its guardian, I must punish you by... Oh, wait, wait, stop! This angle... This outline... It's simply perfect! Turning you into stone would be a waste, so just stay here and let me observe you every day!
name: Protector of Love and Beauty

desc: Francesco Caracciolo-class battleship – Francesco Caracciolo.
name: Francesco Caracciolo

desc: Now it is laid bare before you... The shadow that even the sun's light cannot pierce. This is my complete, unfiltered confession to you.
name: Confession Under the Spotlight

desc: Aircraft carrier – Aquila.
name: Aquila

desc: Good day, my Commander. We have the day off to enjoy the sea breeze and the ocean waves~ Hehe, would you like to help yourself to some fruit?
name: Sardegnian Shallows and Sunshine

desc: Oh, my Commander? I didn't expect to meet you here! Fortune smiles upon me today. Hehe~ If you have a minute to spare, would you care to join me for a cup of tea?
name: A Sip of Sardegnian Elegance

desc: Aircraft carrier – Impero.
name: Impero

desc: Seems school uniforms are all the hype. Veneto picked this one out for me. What are you dressed as, Commander? A teacher? A classmate?
name: Languid Librarian

desc: Ugh... I don't wanna work... I don't wanna work... I don't wanna work... Commander? Finished your overtime shift? Great timing... Come and drink with me!
name: Drunken Drowsy Dreamer

desc: Brin-class submarine – Torricelli.
name: Torricelli

desc: Hehe, hehehehe... We have this little c-corner of the beach all to ourselves... Now, what should we do first... Hehehehe...
name: Shady Seaside

desc: Marconi-class submarine – Leonardo da Vinci.
name: Leonardo da Vinci

desc: Here to watch me rehearse just like these deer, Commander? Isn't it wonderful being surrounded by the beauty of nature? For a performance based on a fable such as this one, ambiance is key. Ehehe~♪
name: Riverside Pirouette

desc: Marconi-class submarine – Maggiore Baracca.
name: Maggiore Baracca

desc: Oh, I wasn't expecting that you'd come here, Commander. As the God of Death, I will have to pass "judgment" on you♪
name: The God Craves Punishment

desc: Battleship – Marco Polo.
name: Marco Polo

desc: Me? Serve as your maid? Oho! That's more like it, Commander! How magnificent and ambitious of you! ...Only temporarily? And you're content with that?
name: The Queen of Hearts

desc: Heavy cruiser – Napoli.
name: Napoli

desc: Commander... Apologies for appearing before you like this. I'll try to get up right at once... Agh... I'm still so dizzy...
name: Dreamy Night

desc: Destroyer – Vittorio Cuniberti.
name: Vittorio Cuniberti

desc: To study an animal's habits, you must first learn and imitate... B-basically, what I'm doing is imitating how cats do things! Don't read into this!
name: On the Habits of Cats

desc: Gnevny-class destroyer – Grozny.
name: Grozny

desc: Comrade Commander, are you here to see my room? Hm? That Шутки isn't funny? Then how about... did my room come to see you, comrade Commander?
name: Bad Bunny Behind Bars

desc: Hmm... If I tweak Królik around a bit like this... But, it'll probably be a problem if I don't finish this in one go... Guess I'll think about it while I eat. Mhm.
name: Bunny Remodeling Plan?

desc: Our shift starts now. Królik, Pirožkí, Manjuus – form up! Let us realize our Manjuu comrades' dreams!
name: Shadowy Syndicate Showdown

desc: *burp*... Now I think I get the appeal of tea. Why is the cup so small, though? Do you have a bigger one on hand, Comrade Commander?
name: Tea Party with Królik

desc: Uughh... Ooohh... Królik is melting... *gasp*! I'm getting lightheaded... Comrade Commander, fetch me some ice...
name: Bunny in the Banya

desc: Leningrad-class destroyer – Minsk.
name: Minsk

desc: You've violated the Minsk Protocol, comrade! Therefore, the sentence appropriate for you is imprisonment! Until when? Obviously, until your jailor is satisfied~♪
name: Thunderous Jailor

desc: Tashkent-class destroyer – Tashkent.
name: Tashkent

desc: ...*Sigh*, I never thought I'd get captured by these little guys... Dear comrade, does Tashkent really have to play along with this?
name: The Bound Cruiser

desc: Urrk... Who dares disturb Tashkent's slumber? ...Oh, it's you, dear comrade? Um, in that case... I can always get more rest later. Is something the matter?
name: The Blue Snoozer

desc: Mmph. There you are, dear comrade. I've been waiting... Oh, yeah. I'm not done yet, so... do you wanna relax with me for a bit before you go?
name: The Sprite's Snapshot

desc: How do you like my outfit, dear comrade? ...Is that so? After all of Tashkent's work to become an idol, that's how you react? Hmph. Just you wait. My next concert will rock your socks off.
name: Tashkent μ

desc: Gnevny-class destroyer - Stremitelny
name: Stremitelny

desc: It sucks not being able to play in the snow... Oh well! I'll play some games instead! Commander, let's play something fun together!
name: No Snow No Life

desc: Huh?! Commander, why did you walk here?! If you're feeling bad, just press the call button... Ugh, you can't walk around at night when you're sick! Grrr!
name: Nurse on the Night Shift

desc: Gnevny-class destroyer - Stremitelny
name: Gremyashchy

desc: Wh-who gave you the right to just barge in? ...I did? Huh. Well, seeing as you're here, I guess we could read a book together. Mm, that's all.
name: A Daytime Delight is in a Book

desc: Gnevny-class destroyer—Gromky.
name: Gromky

desc: Comrade! The morning is already here! Look how high the sun is in the sky!! C'mon, a wonderful day is calling to us~!!
name: Morning's Beckoning

desc: Project 7U-class destroyer – Soobrazitelny
name: Soobrazitelny

desc: Yes, these data and results are quite interesting... Though they mean nothing to me! I am a genius mechanic, not an analyst! Ahh-ha-ha-haah!
name: The Machinery of Life

desc: Project 48-class destroyer – Kiev
name: Kiev

desc: Seeing you here puts me at ease. I know this stakeout will go smoothly as long as you're here. Mhm, all is fine.
name: Backstreet Silver Sonata

desc: Since you're a beginner at this, Commander, let me show you the ropes. Somehow... it feels like I skate better than usual when you're around. I'm pretty good at ice skating, aren't I? This... should be fine, right?
name: Víla of the Crystal Lake

desc: Project 30K Ognevoy-class destroyer – Ognevoy.
name: Ognevoy

desc: I'm Ognevoy, the newest policewoman on the block! I've come to arrest you, fugitive! Give yourself up now! I'm going to– Ah! Oh gosh! ...Can I please get a cuter role instead?
name: Blue Nova

desc: Project 7U-class destroyer – Svirepy.
name: Svirepy

desc: Let's hear it for the graffiti master that's taken the world by storm – Svirepyyy! You people are in real luck, gettin' to witness the birth of my new piece! And if you ain't got any taste, watch yourself!
name: Rebellious Artist

desc: Pallada-class Light Cruiser, Avrora
name: Avrora

desc: "I am Avrora, the princess bound within this tower by a cruel fate... My beloved, please come for me soon..."
name: Shackled Saule

desc: "Muahaha... Now, these streets belong to me..." Sorry, I bit my tongue... Hmm, getting into this role is quite difficult for me after all.
name: Not Cut Out For This?

desc: Bogatyr-class protected cruiser – Pamiat Merkuria.
name: Pamiat' Merkuria

desc: What kinda exercise is this?! Nobody said I'd become a dang showpiece! Come on, get this thing off me, NOW!
name: Caged Minx

desc: Mmmh~ I sure could get used to this life~ Oh, Commander, thanks for being my gofer~♪ Ah, you can leave the cherries right over here!
name: Sweet Cherry Memories

desc: Aaand send DM to Rossiya... Finally you showed up, Commander! So, where are you taking me, hmm?
name: Chic and Cheeky

desc: Happy Valentine's Day~♪ Did you come here to enjoy my chocolate? Then, try guessing where I hid my chocolate – if you get it right, I'll give it to you~♪ Is it here... or maybe over here? Ahahaha~♡
name: Mercurial Chocolate Love

desc: Over here! So, Commander, which outfit do you think looks cuter – the left or the right one? Heehee – you better choose carefully, 'cause I'm gonna wear it!
name: Pick and Choose!

desc: My retrofitting is done! Look forward to seeing how both my cuteness and combat potential have been upgraded!
name: Pamiat' Merkuria (Retrofit)

desc: Chapayev-class cruiser – Chapayev.
name: Chapayev

desc: Commander, what's going on? Did I... do something wrong...? This was all just... meant to be an exercise, right?
name: The Captive Cavalier

desc: Phew... Oh my, Commander, I'm sorry I didn't welcome you at the door. You don't have to be so tense - I already know not to try doing anything weird with you. Hehe~
name: White Cavalier's Respite

desc: You've been looking for me? Heehee, sorry if I made you worry, I just had to feel the night breeze in my hair for a bit. Why don't you stay and enjoy it with me?
name: Indigo & Lantern-Lit Summer Night

desc: Why are you here... Oh, that was rude of me to ask. Maybe you just wanted a change of scenery, or you were drawn by the music. Or maybe my feelings have reached you... I think I like the sound of that one the most. Hehehe.
name: Melody of the White Cavalier

desc: Kirov-Class cruiser—Kirov
name: Kirov

desc: Comrade Commander, you've come at a good time. I've recently taken a liking to this blend of coffee. Want some as well? No need to be shy.
name: Blend R

desc: Halt! You have nowhere left to run!! ...Well done, Comrade Commander, what a thrilling chase we had on our hands! What, you think I'm well-suited for this job? You tease too much, bahaha!
name: Drifting Justice

desc: ...Hmph! Just short of a new personal best, huh? But make no mistake, Comrade Commander. Keep watching me and your patience WILL be rewarded with a breathtaking record!
name: High Jump Star

desc: Chapayev-class light cruiser – Kuybyshev.
name: Kuybyshev

desc: ...Thus marks the end of this tune. The Dragon Empery has graciously allowed me to perform in their Spring Festival celebration. Are you here to listen, Commander? In that case... How did you like the song? Heehee.
name: Maestro of Sterling Strings

desc: Commander... You smell like rain. Let me warm you. The bandage? It's a part of the service. Take a guess as to how it's used... Heehee.
name: Rainy Day Blues

desc: Omaha-class light cruiser – Murmansk
name: Murmansk

desc: ...Achoo! Uhh, good morning... Snow? Yeah, it is snowing today... Woah, it's really coming down hard... Ahaha~
name: Sceneries of Pure Snow

desc: Hello there, Comrade Commander~ Come take a deeeep breath of this. Sniiiff... Can you smell this room's fragrance? Hm? You can't tell? Oh. Uh, my incense may have stopped burning.
name: Chamber of Fragrance

desc: Kirov-class light cruiser – Voroshilov.
name: Voroshilov

desc: Comrade Commander, is the bath to your liking? I'm glad. Heehee, it's a good thing I trusted that "Top 10 Dates for Snowy Days" article and chose this secluded hot spring.
name: Devoted as the Warm Snow

desc: Don't move, please. You're playing the patient, and I'm playing the nurse, so it's only natural that the distance between us is different from usual... Hm? What does that have to do with this pose? Ahem. Now that you mention it, umm...
name: The Nurse's Special Rehearsal

desc: Bogatyr-class protected cruiser – Oleg.
name: Oleg

desc: *yaaawn*... Nothing beats relaxing after a nice bath! Now that I've changed into my warm pajamas, what should we do next? Hm? Go to sleep? No, no, it's too early. I only yawned because I was getting comfortable!
name: Repose by the Fireplace

desc: Heavy cruiser - Tallinn.
name: Tallinn

desc: What, you've never seen the inside of a shipgirl's room? It's not like you're here on official business, so stop standing around already. Find a place to sit and relax.
name: Nostalgic Pilsner

desc: You've reached the Bureau of Investigation... Oh boy, another case. Commander, finish up your paperwork ASAP. We've got witnesses to interview.
name: As You Say, Ma'am!

desc: I'm not letting my guard down, even when dressed like this. Take your eyes off me for just a moment and I'll escape to the moon. With you, of course, heheh. Someone has to keep pushing you forward, after all.
name: Night of Full Moon and Overflowing Love

desc: Heavy cruiser – Kursk.
name: Kursk

desc: This steamy hot spring... is a rather novel experience. I left a spot for you, so come sit down already – Wait, why haven't you taken your clothes off yet?
name: Lone Wolf Amid the Steam

desc: I prefer talking face-to-face, but if you really insist... Heavy cruiser Kursk sits in an office chair, donning a Dragon Empery dress. What's next, Commander?
name: Beauty and the Hunter

desc: Gangut-class battleship – Gangut.
name: Gangut

desc: You have my thanks for this exercise, comrade! I shall gladly carry out the important duty of judge, jury, and rehabilitator!
name: Imposing Warden

desc: ...Bwahaah! I've had all kinds of liquor, but nothing beats the stuff back home! Comrade, let's have a toast to the coming off-duty days!
name: Keeper of the Firewater

desc: Sovetsky Soyuz-class battleship – Sovetsky Soyuz.
name: Sovetsky Soyuz

desc: This is Agent Sovetsky Soyuz, codename Polyarnaya Zayats, commencing infiltration. I'd hate to spend long on breaking through the security, so please just surrender now. It's not too late.
name: Skyfall Agent

desc: Curses... To think I'd fall for such an elementary trap... I take it you're going to "interrogate" me now, Comrade Comander? Oh, no, it's just... if you don't know the proper technique, I could assist you.
name: Stringed Interrogation

desc: So here you are, Comrade Commander. You're usually so well-guarded, yet now you're all by yourself – something I can only describe as careless. I, Sovetsky Soyuz, shall take you on.
name: Stringed Interrogation

desc: Sovestsky Soyuz-class battleship - Sovetskaya Belorussiya.
name: Sovetskaya Belorussiya

desc: To pass the time by proactively reading, or by passively enjoying the company of others... Ah, good morning, Comrade, I've been expecting you. Hahaha!
name: Relaxation Stratagem

desc: Haha! Did you not expect this to be our rendezvous spot? Oh please, even I wish to unwind in the sand sometimes. Since you're here, accepting my invitation, won't you keep me company to kill some time, Comrade?
name: Ripples and a Fluttering Veil

desc: Sovetsky Soyuz-class battleship – Sovetskaya Rossiya.
name: Sovetskaya Rossiya

desc: "Situation normal in all sectors of the facility..." Oh, it is you. I was just giving Minsk the daily report. Do you have something?
name: The Lackadaisical Lookout

desc: R-class battleship – Arkhangelsk
name: Arkhangelsk

desc: Your choice treasure now belongs to master thief Arkhangelsk! Think you can arrest me? Then stop gawking and come get me!
name: Grandiose Getaway

desc: I am Arkhangelsk, the royal sorceress who resides in the tower to the north. So, you wish to study magic to defeat the Demon King? Very admirable... You're deserving of the title of "Hero." I will be equally sincere and impart my teachings to you sternly.
name: Supporting Sorceress

desc: Gangut-class battleship – Sevastopol.
name: Sevastopol

desc: Phew... This is... Comrade Commander? Fancy meeting you at this time of night. Me? Heh, heheheheh... You wouldn't believe me if I said I got too drunk and went in first, would you?
name: More than a Little Drunk

desc: Gangut-class battleship – Poltava.
name: Poltava

desc: Heehee... Oh, are you ready for your audience with me? Remember the important thing – minding your manners. Queen Poltava's time is very, very precious indeed.
name: Meeting the Mafia Queen

desc: Type 21 battleship – Kazan.
name: Kazan

desc: Ah, you're up, Commander. Heehee. Good morning. It's so sunny today that even the kitchen is a bit hot. That's okay, though – I've made a refreshing breakfast for you. Go wash your face, then it's time to dig in.
name: The Warm Morning Sunshine

desc: Project 72-class aircraft carrier – Volga
name: Volga

desc: Volga here. I'm currently tracking an important witness. *gurgle* ...Is my stomach rumbling because this AR game requires so much stamina? Ugh, lost track of the witness just now...
name: An Irresistible AR Adventure

desc: Project 69-class cruiser – Kronshtadt
name: Kronshtadt

desc: Listen up, assholes! We have you surrounded! I'm Kronshtadt, squad leader of the Northern Parliament Special Forces! You have only one option: come out with your hands in the air and surrender!
name: Begin the Rush!

desc: When you said "special animal costume," I was expecting some sort of mascot costume... not whatever this is! B-but don't worry, Comrade Commander! This is no big deal for an agent of the Northern Parliament!
name: Animal Agent

desc: Aircraft carrier - Chkalov.
name: Chkalov

desc: Oh? What made you come over here instead of heading down to the beach? Surely you didn't ditch your friends on a hard-earned day off just to see me? But, I don't mind. It's called a day off because you get to decide how to spend your time.
name: Seaside Sunset

desc: Aircraft carrier – Admiral Nakhimov.
name: Admiral Nakhimov

desc: What are you doing on the set, Commander? Here to check on the progress? But won't this spoil your first impression of the final cut? Well, the video is made for you anyways, so consider this a preview.
name: First Time in the Limelight

desc: Commander, come here and plant a saxaul... Oh, I look like I'm enjoying this a lot? Yeah. It's because I don't get to do much outdoor work, since I'm always stuck in my workshop, poring over data and equipment. Also, you're here with me.
name: A Fresh, Green Day

desc: Placing: first. Congratulations on your victory, Commander. I'm glad if my cheerleading played a part... My mechanical skills also played a part, you say? True. Then I guess I'm pretty glad.
name: Cheerleading Mechanic?

desc: Light cruiser – Dmitri Donskoi.
name: Dmitri Donskoi

desc: Yoohoo! Welcome, Commander! How do you like your room? Does it make your heart flutter? Hehe, we've got all kinds of services – I can put you to bed with a massage, or do whatever animal role-play you're into... Bunny Dmitri's here to make all your dreams come true!
name: Bedside Bunny

desc: Le Fantasque-class destroyer – Le Triomphant.
name: Le Triomphant

desc: L'Adroit-class destroyer – Forbin.
name: Forbin

desc: It's good to be able to stop and smell the roses every now and then. Um, Commander, would you be able to accompany me a bit longer?
name: Fleur Blanche

desc: Even though I'm an Iris Libre squire, I'm currently working hard to have a rich student life. Um... maybe this is a bit too laid back?
name: École de Chevalier

desc: Good evening, Commander. I am currently enjoying the party in the company of my friends, as my duties as a squire entail. Um... I've had a bit too much to drink? R-really...?
name: Feast of Champagne

desc: At long last, this wonderful day is here. It feels like I'm dreaming... I'm so happy, I just... Forgive me, I promised myself I wouldn't cry... I, Forbin the squire, shall remain by your side for the rest of my life!
name: Fleur de Mariée

desc: My hard work has finally paid off! Commander, thank you for your guidance all this time! I'll return the favor by bringing you even more honors in battle!
name: Forbin (Retrofit)

desc: Le Hardi-class destroyer – Le Téméraire.
name: Le Téméraire

desc: Commander, I've finished changing into my swimsuit! Heheh~ let's head down to the beach and enjoy ourselves as much as we can!
name: Summery Temeraire!

desc: How do I look? These pajamas are super cute, aren't they? Ehehe, I really like this one! It even matches with Opiniâtre's!
name: Dreamy Dolce

desc: Let's go, let's go! Allons-y! Whew... Heehee, you here to watch me rehearse, Commander? Okay, and how was my performance just now? Did that manage to motivate you?
name: Cheering Star

desc: Le Hardi-class destroyer – L'Opiniâtre.
name: L'Opiniâtre

desc: It is said that the summertime sea holds an extraordinary enchantment over people... but the only supernatural thing I'm feeling is this accursed heat... Am I missing something?
name: Beachside Magician

desc: Le Hardi-class destroyer – Le Hardi.
name: Le Hardi

desc: Gulp, gulp... Ahh! That hits the spot! Cold and refreshing... There's nothing in the world like a glass of cold milk after steaming in the sauna.
name: Sticky Situation

desc: Le Fantasque-class large destroyer - Le Terrible.
name: Le Terrible

desc: Zzz... Commander...? Sorry... for showing you this unsightly side of mine... I'm just, not a morning person... Zzzzz...
name: Silence, Slumber, and Solace

desc: How goes your day, Commander? Hehe, are you looking for my clever sister, Le Malin? If so, you would do well to search somewhere less... popular~♪
name: Sunlight, Seaspray, and Sanctity

desc: Vauquelin-class destroyer – Maillé Brézé.
name: Maillé Brézé

desc: H-h-halt, intruder! Thou art intruding in the domain of an Iris Libre Templar Knight, a crime punishable by... Eek! I'm begging you, spare my life! ...It's you, Lord Commander?!
name: The Noble Knight's Last Stand

desc: Enjoying sweet pastries in a lovely dress – heehee, such bliss! ...I care not how unbecoming this is of a knight! I saved these desserts for my holiday! Let me enjoy myself, would you!
name: Sugary Sabbatical

desc: I am the Le Hardi-class destro– Wait, no! Right now, I'm Tem, AKA Le Téméraire, an idol with the unit Cyanidin! Keep your eyes peeled for my debut performance, Commander!
name: Le Téméraire μ

desc: Light cruiser – Émile Bertin.
name: Émile Bertin

desc: Commander, does my swimsuit pique your fancy? I'm actually quite proud of my fashion sense. *Giggle* Now, let's enjoy midsummer together~
name: Côte d'Azur

desc: I heard of this romantic concept of maid outfits, and thought I'd try one on to see how it feels~ What are your thoughts, Commander?
name: Maid Fantastique

desc: Modest though it may be, isn't this a lovely little garden? Come, Commander! Let us dance surrounded by Mother Nature~
name: Gilded Dance

desc: Émile Bertin, retrofit complete! I feel like a completely new person! To show my gratitude, Commander, I'll perform a brand new dance for you!
name: Émile Bertin (Retrofit)

desc: Light cruiser – Jeanne d'Arc.
name: Jeanne d'Arc

desc: "O chosen hero, I bestow this sword upon you so that you may clear any obstacles in your path..." Commander, how did that sound?
name: Saintess of the Sea

desc: Oh, Commander, would you like to release a lantern? I hear they're a way to send wishes into the heavens above... May our Lord bless our companions and bring peace and joy to all.
name: Patron Saintess of Celebration

desc: De Grasse-class light cruiser – Guichen.
name: Guichen

desc: Advanced technology is indistinguishable from magic—and that goes for this icy stage, too. Commander, please enjoy this demonstration of our heaven-bestowed sacrament until the very end~♪
name: Sorcière on Ice

desc: It's almost time to wake up, dear guest... Don't open those eyes just yet. Let me use my magic to spirit away that last bit of sleepiness.
name: Milk and Kisses

desc: ASMR触发面占坑
name: Milk&Kiss

desc: Duguay-Trouin-class light cruiser – Duguay-Trouin.
name: Duguay-Trouin

desc: Commander, this is where we'll be praying today. Nobody can disturb us here... You already know what to do, I'm sure?
name: Covetous Bathgoer

desc: Suffren-class heavy cruiser – Suffren.
name: Suffren

desc: Hm? The door's open! ...Commander? Oh, ahaha... Silly me, I should've put up a card with "occupied" on it... Then again, I... I guess I don't mind if you're the one who sees me~
name: Impulsive Incident

desc: Oh, Commander. Were you waiting for little old me? You've gotta take your time sorting out your dress if you wanna look snazzy! Heheh, feast your eyes on this cute little kni– Uhh, how are you supposed to tie this thing?
name: Unrivaled Winsomeness

desc: C5-class heavy cruiser – Brennus.
name: Brennus

desc: Swordbearer, you've come at the perfect time. I need your help. Hm? What's with that look on your face? You didn't expect it would be a difficult feat to arrange the clothes you requested I wear, did you...?
name: Musician on Blade's Precipice

desc: An encounter under the moonlight – the work of fate, or the very laws of their world? Ah, Swordbearer... Those weren't rehearsed lines, but a simple greeting to you.
name: Timeless Nocturne

desc: Duquesne-class heavy cruiser – Duquesne.
name: Duquesne

desc: This wine bath mustn't be wasted. One must strip off their clothes and submerge themselves deeply in this rich bath of life. Be not so reserved, Commander, just... Huh?! N-no, I would never peek whilst you got changed!
name: Wetness of a Crimson Night

desc: Type 1913 battlecruiser – Masséna.
name: Masséna

desc: Commander, this spring has a sweet taste to it. You should try it.
name: Sweetly Intoxicating Spring

desc: Richelieu-class battleship – Richelieu.
name: Richelieu

desc: This swimsuit... Yes, the one Émile picked out for me, seems a bit skimpy... I didn't think she'd be the type to trick me into wearing something like this, but... Commander, where are you looking?
name: Fleuron of the Waves

desc: Commander, I wish you a Happy New Year. May you avail yourself of the period of repose that follows the culmination of the year's duties. I pray that you and everyone else may receive the blessing of the Heavens.
name: Evergreen Prophecy

desc: Lyon-class battleship – Lyon.
name: Lyon

desc: Mmh... Pilates may be easy to learn, but it seems difficult to master... Are you still okay, Commander? Me? I-I can keep going...
name: Paired Exercise

desc: Alsace-class battleship – Alsace.
name: Alsace

desc: Thish one ish battleship Alsace – a-artifact of the unifuh... guardian of the Holy See, donning summer clothes... One's frame is overheating and the only fix is submersion in water... Aahhh...
name: Heat-Beating Summer Sacrament

desc: This one is Battleship Alsace – the Sacramental Blade, the Swordbearing Oni Protector of the Backwoods. One has awaited your arrival. *burp*... Um, pretend that didn't happen, Commander...
name: Tipsy Oni on a Sacred Night

desc: Independence-class light aircraft carrier – Bois Belleau.
name: Bois Belleau

desc: Finished your sacred work? I looked into hot spring therapy a little to help you relax a little. It's the warmest and most pleasant healing method I've ever seen. Would you... come in with me?
name: Steamy Therapy

desc: Aircraft carrier – Béarn.
name: Béarn

desc: Are you perhaps feeling unwell, Commander? Oh, I see, you're just looking for a shaded place to rest? Acknowledged. In that case, you may sit here if you'd like.
name: Summer Lifeguard

desc: Joffre-class aircraft carrier – Painlevé.
name: Painlevé

desc: Phew... Commander...? Would you like to... hnnngh... stretch with me? Don't worry, it won't hurt. We have plenty of time, so we can take it slow...
name: Team Stretching

desc: Mm... Aah, that hits the spot! I just hope my prayers are answered and it suits the Commander's tastes... Heehee, maybe if I personally feed–eep?! C-Commander? D-did you just hear that...?
name: Fresh and Fortunate

desc: Cruiser submarine – Surcouf.
name: Surcouf

desc: Hmm? Commander, are you shopping as well? If so, why don't you come along and take a look around? ... Huh? Of course you can't climb on. That'd be illegal.
name: Shopping Time!

desc: Mmmh~ Bonjour, Commander~ Nothing feels better than the waves lapping at your skin~ Oh, Commander, why don't you come lie down and experience it for yourself?
name: Loisirs Balnéaires

desc: Heavy cruiser – Saint Louis.
name: Saint Louis

desc: With all due respect, Commander, this finery and this throne are not fit for one such as myself. Despite the hallowed name I have inherited, I am nothing more than a warrior. —However, if such an arrangement pleases you, then I shall hold my objections.
name: Holy Knight's Resplendence

desc: Commander, regarding your next appointment... Ah, hard work is one of the highest virtues of the Iris's holy knights. On weekdays or vacations, in knights' armor or the Dragon Empery's attire, there can be no pause to my prayer, my training, or my duties as the administrator of your will.
name: Alluring Administrator

desc: Battleship – Champagne.
name: Champagne

desc: It is not against the teachings to halt one's pursuit of destiny and to surrender to the warm draft of festivities. It is mankind's prerogative to seek out auspicious portents.
name: Lapis Lazuli's First Dream

desc: An ode of gratitude for the venerable Iris, echoing tones condensing to pure prayer. Seek blessings not in public worship, but in humanity's true triumph: our everlasting bonds.
name: Adulation Eternal

desc: Large cruiser - Brest.
name: Brest

desc: "I devote this paean to thee, Champion of seas blue and free." There, the song is completed. But we've come all this way... Shall we continue our adventure through these undersea ruins, Champion?
name: Marine Muse

desc: O Champion, what manner of floral makeup would look best upon my brow? Or, could I perhaps... call upon you to apply it for me? ♪
name: Moonlit Night's Spring Vista

desc: Light cruiser – Bayard.
name: Bayard

desc: Welcome, Commander. ...You really don't know what I'm doing? So there are things even you don't know. This is a new means of training knights, you see. Expect ever greater exploits from me.
name: The Most Treacherous Trial

desc: No description
name: Königsberg

desc: No description
name: Karlsruhe

desc: No description
name: Köln

desc: Kent-class heavy cruiser—Suffolk, Hull Number 55!
name: Suffolk

name: Norfolk

name: Hood

desc: I'm Blanc, awaiting your orders. Could you tell me something interesting about the world?
name: Blanc

desc: I'm the Goddess of Leanbox, Vert! I'm exceptionally skilled at shooting games. Feel free to ask me for help!
name: Vert

name: BLACK★ROCK SHOOTER
