desc: L'Adroit-class destroyer – Le Mars.
name: Le Mars

desc: It's summer~! Summer is here, Commander! Let's head down to the beach to play! I'll show you why I'm feared in water gun fights!
name: Été Brillant

desc: Hey! Over here! Hehe. I didn't expect to run into you at school, Commander. What are you doing here?
name: Écolière Heureuse

desc: Commander, thanks for coming to pick me up! I don't often get the chance to wear formal clothes, though it is a little hard to move around... Oh, but I can deal with it!
name: Splendorous Debut

desc: Retro~ fit~ com~ plete! The new and improved Le Mars is at your service~!
name: Le Mars (Retrofit)

desc: Vauquelin-class destroyer – Tartu.
name: Tartu

desc: Commander, you're not going to get into the water? ...Ah, I'm fine right here. To tell you the truth, I once got washed away by the waves, and then got laughed at by Vauquelin... so I'm perfectly fine right here.
name: Overthinking Summer

desc: Vauquelin-class destroyer – Vauquelin.
name: Vauquelin

desc: Commandeeer! What are you doing? It's our day off! Turn the work part of your brain off and just have fun! C'mon, let's enjoy ourselves on the beach!
name: Innocent Summer Knight

desc: Yes, the strings... I can hear the celebratory melody... Now, follow my lead and we'll take this song to greater– Oh, Commander? What's all this, you ask? Uhh... You know... Ahahaha...
name: One-Girl Orchestra

desc: *crash*! Found another coin! Check it out, Commander! I got all these from smashing pots! ...Breaking the law? Heheh! The one law among thieves is that there are no laws♪
name: Otherworldly Adventure

desc: Vauquelin-class destroyer – Kersaint.
name: Kersaint

desc: Phew... Commander? So the Iris brings us together once again... I-I'm sorry for being so sudden, but... Would you like to join me on my run?
name: Reverent Runner

desc: C-Commander, p-please hurry and stop this creature! Otherwise! You might! Get hurt! ...WoooooOOOOAH! Phew... That was a close one... Haah... Praised be the Holy Iris... Urgh...
name: A Saint's Mercy Can Do No Wrong

desc: Le Hardi-class destroyer – Fleuret.
name: Fleuret

desc: Welcome, welcome! I'm Fleuret, your game master. Are you ready to make a wager? Heehee!
name: Up All Knight to Get Lucky

desc: Le Hardi-class destroyer – Épée.
name: Épée

desc: Oh, wh-what do I do now... Fleur and the others are doing so well, and I can't even clean a table without messing up... If I worry the Commander, then... Whah?! C-Commander?!
name: Poor, Lonely Knight

desc: Mogador-class large destroyer – Mogador.
name: Mogador

desc: Commaaander! I'm struggling with my swimsuit. Come and give me a hand. Oh, that's fine – I locked the door as soon as you came in here. Don't be shy, I'm all yours now... Heheheh♥
name: Locker Room Lechery

desc: Commaaander♥ You pressed the call button, so here I am... You don't remember that? Heehee♥ Do you have a fever or something? Gosh, you poor little thing...♥
name: Olfactory Nursery Call

desc: Le Fantasque-class destroyer – Le Malin.
name: Le Malin

desc: Morning, Commander~ Mm, the Sabbath is the day of rest, so I shall not budge from my sacred charge even if you were to call Triomphant over. I solemnly swear to do absolutely nothing today.
name: Sleepy Sunday

desc: I must commend you for being able to find my secret base, Commander... but unfortunately for you, I refuse to return to the office today. Just... *yawn*...let me spend the whole day sleeping here...
name: Mercredi at the Secret Base

desc: Zzz... zzz... Huh? Commander? I was in the middle of a nap... Oh, this outfit? It's cool, comfy, and cute. If you don't need anything from me, I'm going back to sleep...
name: Listless Lapin

desc: I am the Iris's shining sword, Le Malin. As the shimmering idol who chases the waves, may your souls be healed by my songs of prayer.
name: Le Malin μ

desc: Le Fantasque-class destroyer – L'Indomptable.
name: L'Indomptable

desc: What a farce, making a proud Templar Knight portray a helpless little girl... Why am I lying here, you ask? Hmph. Because Le Malin asserted this is the best way to get in touch with my "vulnerable side"...
name: Little Red Riding Hood's Worries

desc: Hmm... Traveling by foot from here would be quickest. Ah... It's snowing. Hmph! A little snow and wind can scarcely faze a noble Templar Knight! I'll be back shortly!
name: Temp in Low Temperatures

desc: Le Fantasque-class destroyer – L'Audacieux.
name: L'Audacieux

desc: Urgh... As a Chevalier, I simply cannot get used to wearing an outfit like this. But, if I tell myself it's for the Commander's sake... Alright! I shall complete today's sacred duties to the utmost of my abilities!
name: Protector Beneath the Parasol

desc: La Galissonnière-class light cruiser – La Galissonnière.
name: La Galissonnière

desc: Summertime means pool time! Oh, hey, Commander. What are you waiting for? Come over and let's have fun!
name: Pristine Piscene

desc: Happy New Year, again! So, you wanna try sharing this "cross-cupped wine?" What, it's not a drinking game? Welp, I guess I've still got a whole ton to learn about the Dragon Empery's customs~
name: Lush Spring Dreams

desc: If you ignore me, I'll use my black cat magic to turn you into a pumpkin! Is that Halloweeny enough? Ahahaha! I'm just messing! C'mon, let's go do somethin' fun tonight, Commander!
name: Black Cat of All Hallows' Eve

desc: La Galissonnière-class light cruiser – Marseillaise.
name: Marseillaise

desc: Alright, aim at this part of the ball, and drop my hips... Nngh?! I, I'm alright! The fighting angel, Marseillaise, will not be defeated by this... Hyeep?!
name: Fighting Angel's Regimen

desc: Suffren-class Heavy Cruiser—Foch
name: Foch

desc: Yo, Commander, did I keep you waiting? Sorry 'bout that. You know how it goes, sometimes it's really hard for a girl to pick out the right thing to wear. Anyway, let's get going~♪
name: Rainbow Rendezvous

desc: How are you today, Master? Your humble butler Foch patiently awaits your orders... Hahah! I sure look the part, don't I?
name: Majestic Majordomo

desc: Algérie-class heavy cruiser – Algérie.
name: Algérie

desc: Oh my, hehe... Are you enjoying the warmth of the sunlight here? I'm glad that you're finding some time to relax here, but wouldn't you rather come play with everyone else?
name: White Sand Paradise

desc: Oh my, it seems that the one who ended up coming wasn't little Alice, but you instead... Do you plan to defy me as well, Commander? If so, I'll have to put you on trial for your sins... How was my acting just now? Hehe~
name: Red Queen's Decree

desc: Suffren-class heavy cruiser – Dupleix.
name: Dupleix

desc: Good timing, Commander. There are some parameters I need you to check... Come on, this is safety we're talking about. As an inspector, I can't just ignore them. Anyway, come sit next to me so we can get started.
name: Final Check

desc: Dunkerque-class battlecruiser – Dunkerque.
name: Dunkerque

desc: I've been waiting so long for summer... and it's so worth it - the sun, the sand, the waves, and everyone's laughter. Commander, why don't we take this opportunity to enjoy some crullers together?
name: Summer Sucré

desc: Don't you simply adore the atmosphere in this place? It's one of my favorites. The desserts here are to die for. Would you like a taste?
name: Afternoon Venus

desc: Dunkerque-class battlecruiser – Strasbourg.
name: Strasbourg

desc: Commander? I can't believe you found me... As you can see, I'm finishing up this car's pre-race checks. If you have time to spare, would you mind lending me a hand? Oh, and of course, keep this a secret between the two of us. I can count on you for that, yes?
name: Faerie of the Race Circuit

desc: Richelieu-class battleship – Jean Bart.
name: Jean Bart

desc: The guest of honor shouldn't be wandering around looking for girls drinking alone... Hmph, might as well have a drink while you're here anyway.
name: Uninhibited Bloodstone

desc: You damn scalawag... You don't just sneak into someone's hideaway without consequences, ya know. Though, I found this place by pure chance too. Don't go tellin' anyone else about it!
name: Private Après Midi

desc: Bonne année... Or rather, I should say "Happy New Year" here, yes? A year of peace and prosperity passes, and we are here to welcome another... and I must thank you for making that possible.
name: First Snow Upon the Cutlass's Edge

desc: What're you starin' daggers through me for? Are ya that excited about this new outfit? Alright, then feast your eyes on my fashion sense. Yeah, I didn't put it together just for your sake this time – more like to demonstrate my tastes.
name: Springlight Étoiles

desc: Richelieu-class battleship – Clemenceau.
name: Clemenceau

desc: The skies are blue and the wind is calm, a perfect day for golfing... Commander? I didn't bring you here just to watch the scenery, you know? Brace yourself, because you're in for a long day with me.
name: Splendid Breeze

desc: Gascogne module change process complete. New directive: sing for the world. Master's order is my will.
name: Gascogne μ

desc: Joffre-class aircraft carrier – Joffre.
name: Joffre

desc: Were you planning on freeing me from this spell? Then I suppose you're prepared to lock lips with me. Even though I'm already awake, um... that's just part of the ritual.
name: Ensorcelled Snow White

desc: Do you feel refreshed? Even without a holy ritual, the Iris would be happy to know that I've managed to soothe you with this bath. Was it not enough? Then... Shall we go back in?
name: Sublime Elysium

desc: Commander, have you prepared yourself adequately for this race? I hope your machine is able to perform to its full potential... and of course, the same goes for you too.
name: Blessings' First Flight

desc: Battleship – Gascogne.
name: Gascogne

desc: Gascogne uniform change complete. Directive assigned: have fun on the beach with Master. Requesting detailed instructions for how to "have fun on the beach."
name: Tropical Environs Acclimation Service Equipment

desc: Mode change to "traveling with Master" complete. Travel navigation verified. Master, requesting new destination or observation target.
name: Traveling Mood Mechanism

desc: Battleship – Flandre.
name: Flandre

desc: *sniffle*... Oh, Commander, what have I done...? I was supposed to serve You, and now I've committed a grave sin of messing everything up... Where did I go wrong...?
name: If Love is a Sin, Thou Art Forgiven

desc: Admiralen-class destroyer – Evertsen.
name: Evertsen

desc: Commander, relax wherever you like. ...Why so far? You won't get any sun there.
name: Basking by the Window

desc: De Zeven Provinciën-class light cruiser – De Zeven Provinciën.
name: De Zeven Provinciën

desc: Good morning, Commander. Did you sleep well? Oh, there are petals in your hair. I'll get them for you~
name: Snuggling for Warmth

desc: Heavy cruiser – Gouden Leeuw.
name: Gouden Leeuw

desc: After all that messing around in the bathroom, it's time to clean myself. Commander, would you please assist me? I'll be still for you, of course. For instance... How about this position, hmm?
name: An Intimate Cleaning

desc: Sailing frigate – Royal Fortune.
name: Royal Fortune

desc: Tonight's dessert is not a cake or a pastry... What are you looking around for? YOU'RE my dessert! Heheh, scared you, didn't I?
name: Treats from the Deep

desc: Hell of a proposition, this. Keeping an eye on your booty for the whole day so nobody steals it. But I said I'd do it, and a real Tempesta always keeps her word. You're all mine for today♪
name: Eyes on the Prize

desc: Sailing frigate – São Martinho.
name: São Martinho

desc: Here you see the opposite side of the retainer of the golden light. Be not afraid. I am still me, and my feelings and my beliefs have not changed. Still, if it unnerves you, perhaps you should get to know me again?
name: The Golden Shadow

desc: Sailing frigate – Golden Hind.
name: Golden Hind

desc: How do you feel about this look, my darling? ...Not scary enough? How odd... I thought Mary Celeste had the right idea. Wait, I know~ What if I hold this axe, hmm? ♡
name: Forlorn Femme Fatale

desc: Sailing frigate – Mary Celeste.
name: Mary Celeste

desc: I am Mary Celeste, the silent reaper of the moonless night... Aye, this attire befits a ghost ship such as I.
name: Grim Night's Reaper

desc: Sailing frigate – Whydah.
name: Whydah

desc: You've summoned the angel of tricks and treats... Huh? Why am I dressed like this? Meh, it's too much of a pain to answer that... In any case, gimme candy or else! Commander, time is of the essence here. The sooner I can go home, the sooner I can continue my gaming session...
name: Lazy Pirate Angel

desc: Sailing frigate – Adventure Galley.
name: Adventure Galley

desc: "Ahahahah! I've finally found yooou, Master! Dinner is ready, so just follow me to the... You're not hungry? Aww, but the meat is fresh off the bone..." Commander? Why are you backing away?
name: Carnival Under the Blood Moon

desc: Sailing frigate – Ganj-i-Sawai.
name: Ganj-i-Sawai

desc: You heard my song? Thank goodness... Someone has finally come for me! Say, could you please remove the seal on me?
name: Mermaid in Distress

desc: Sailing frigate – Fancy.
name: Fancy

desc: Oh... You've found me. This is horror fashion, and I've heard it's pretty popular. Boo. Scared?
name: Grave of Your Liking

desc: Sailing frigate – Amity.
name: Amity

desc: Well, well, look who's got nowhere left to go. Kidding, kidding. I win again, so I'll be taking your treasure! Follow me down if you're brave enough to jump.
name: Friendly Franken

desc: Sailing frigate – Portsmouth Adventure.
name: Portsmouth Adventure

desc: Wait, Commander?! You're here way ahead of time! N-no, this is NOT what my special surprise is supposed to be!
name: Adventurous Surprise

desc: Sailing frigate – Dolphin.
name: Dolphin

desc: *yaaawn*... Was it you who awoke me? Heehee, thanks. Oh, don't be scared! Sure, rising out of a coffin is a bit creepy... but still, I'm not going to hurt you. Promise.
name: Incantation of Revival

desc: Sailing frigate – Queen Anne's Revenge.
name: Queen Anne's Revenge

desc: You, lost mortal, have awakened an indescribable supreme being. You will become my retainer and aid me in completing my ritual.
name: Call of the Creeping Embrace

desc: Sailing frigate – Lyme.
name: Lyme

desc: Ugh... Where am I? Why do I feel so weak? Did I... trigger a trap that corrupts its prey? Grgh! Was it you who laid the trap? You will pay for this!
name: Corrupting Trap

desc: Sailing frigate – Pearl.
name: Pearl

desc: Oh sweet hero, you who charged into this forbidden and dangerous castle alone for the sake of your beloved angel... What a scene you've arrived to. The power of potions is really something, isn't it...
name: Fallen Angel in the Dark Castle

desc: Sailing frigate – Royal James.
name: Royal James

desc: Where... am I? Brrr, it's cold... What am I supposed to– Oh, you look pretty warm, stranger. Would you mind... sharing a little of your body heat?
name: The Forbidden Slurp

desc: Sailing frigate – Adventure.
name: Adventure

desc: There you are... Don't think I didn't notice you skulking around my castle! Can't believe you made it here without triggering my traps... Does that mean I'm not safe here, either?!
name: Master of the Safe House

desc: Greetings, Commander. I'm Hunter. I hunt, as you might've surmised. Is this place... my new base?
name: Hunter META

desc: Well met, Commander. My name is Fortune. Please don't worry about these ch-chains... They're there to... keep my power in check.
name: Fortune META

desc: You're helpless... So helpless it's worrying me. Oh, also, no need to concern yourself with who I am. Just think of me as the one who'll help you get your act together.
name: Hatakaze META

desc: I am Kimberly of the Fletcher class, ready to serve. That should do it for introductions. What's important is that I am your sword – all you need to do is tell me what to cut.
name: Kimberly META

desc: The adorable Vampire, messenger of the dark night, graces thee with her presence. Hehe, thou smellest sweet♪ Thou art certainly the one I've dreamed of♡
name: Vampire META

desc: You... have summoned Kasumi. Commander, what do you need of me?
name: Kasumi META

desc: I'm Royal Navy destroyer Grenville, returning to the battlefield in META form. Long ago, I... No, that's all in the past now. Just give me a chance, Commander. I swear to keep the fleet safe this time.
name: Grenville META

desc: So you're the Commander. I am Kawakaze, a roamer of the lands. We will be walking the same path for some time. Let's be cordial.
name: Kawakaze META

desc: So you're the Commander? Name's Yuudachi! Think of me as a Shiratsuyu class. By the way, you guys got any food here? You do? Then we're all good!
name: Yuudachi META

desc: I'm destroyer Dewey – Dewey META – and I'm pleased to be serving as your tactical advisor. I'll provide professional strategic assistance from the sidelines which I hope will be of use to you.
name: Dewey META

desc: Were you looking for me? I am willing to lend you my power – provided that you promise not to hide anything from me.
name: Helena META

desc: I'm Memphis. You may not know me, but I know you and I know you well. Don't you worry, I'm not a threat – you can trust me. Today I assume the role of your right hand and bodyguard.
name: Memphis META

desc: So you're the Commander... in other words, my Master. Alright, got it. The name's Sheffield, and the game's pointing my gun at vermin – Ah, please disregard that little gesture I made just now.
name: Sheffield META

desc: I'm La Galissonnière, the shipgirl from hell! I've come for your soul! ...Wow, didn't even flinch. Guess it's true that you don't fear death. Heheh, let's see if I can get a more interesting response out of you next time~♪
name: La Galissonnière META

desc: I am the light cruiser named Jintsuu. I take it you summoned me because you need help? ...Very well. Then I shall humbly devise plans that will serve your fleet.
name: Jintsuu META

desc: Tovarishch Ofitser, our meeting here will send trembles across the world! All my strength is yours to realize your ideals with. Let us fight, together!
name: Kirov META

desc: Yoohoo! Nice to meet you, Commander... When can I start? Heehee. You clearly don't understand the situation here. If you want the privilege of working with the noble Lady Pamiat' Merkuria, you'll have to earn it!
name: Pamiat' Merkuria META

desc: Commander, I'm the META Boise... It's my job to give you and your fleet the protection you all need.
name: Boise META

desc: Part of Flare? No. The Council? Not that either. Maybe the Ashes, then? Ah, forget it. Who or what you serve doesn't matter! I'm Cleveland, a Knight of the Sea! Let's be buds!
name: Cleveland META

desc: I am heavy cruiser Trento, and I will be your assistant. The best thing I could ask for is that my support helps you achieve your goals.
name: Trento META

desc: You must be the Commander. I am the heavy cruiser Algérie. So, what pleasures can I experience here? I do hope you won't disappoint me. Heehee~
name: Algérie META

desc: Hey and good day, Commander. I am Foch, the Warlord. Heehee, the Warlord of what, you ask? That should be obvious – the Warlord of Hell! Hahaha! It's good to be serving you.
name: Foch META

desc: You the Commander? Alright, say no more. Take me into battle and I guarantee ya won't be let down!
name: Wichita META

desc: I'm Admiral Hipper, lead ship of my class and sister to Eugen and Blücher. Got it memorized?
name: Admiral Hipper META

desc: I am Bolzano, a knight of the Sardegnia League. Commander, I await my next task.
name: Bolzano META

desc: You're... the Commander, right? In other words, the one with the authority to control me. Though I have no interest in you as an individual, I will still obey your orders... At least for the time being.
name: Gneisenau META

desc: I'm Iron Blood battlecruiser Scharnhorst. I am keen to join forces with a Commander as talented as you. Don't let my expectations of you be misplaced.
name: Scharnhorst META

desc: I'm Repulse, Renown-class battlecruiser. I've been through a lot... but that's in the past. Now, I'm a part of this port. Whenever you're in a pinch, come see me.
name: Repulse META

desc: Salutations to you, Commander. I am battlecruiser Renown. I hope that this battle-worn blade can become your power.
name: Renown META

desc: Battlecruiser Hiei, at your service. What shall we do next, Commander? I am ready to patrol or head into battle, so let us sortie at your earliest convenience.
name: Hiei META

desc: I'm battlecruiser Dunkerque. Yes, I'm not purposefully giving you this tense look, it's just that I just returned from the battlefield. People call me things like "the Dessert Demon." Would you like to know why they call me that, Commander?
name: Dunkerque META

desc: I am battleship Fusou. I have come to bring peace to this world's tormented souls. Commander, do you seek blessings... or redemption?
name: Fusou META

desc: Are you this fleet's Commander, Milord? I see. You have great potential, but your skills need some refinement. I wonder what's the best way to train you... You'll see soon enough – stay alert until then!
name: Yamashiro META

desc: I am Arizona... This may be improper of me, but is it really alright for me to stay here? ...Very well, Commander. If that is what you've decided...
name: Arizona META

desc: So you are the Commander? Very well. From this point forth, you will use your courage and intellect for our purposes! ...We don't have all day, now. You are our servant, so this won't go anywhere until you swear your fealty.
name: Queen Elizabeth META

desc: On behalf of all Rodneys, greetings... You must understand, "I" am a physical representation of the concept of "Rodney." "I" am no more than that...
name: Rodney META

desc: I am Nagato, Guardian Fox of the "Sakura Empire". Tell me, why have you summoned me? For power? Or for a wish you would like to have granted?
name: Nagato META

desc: I am Giulio Cesare, conqueror of the empire. Spare me the needless chatter. I have no desire to squander time on such things.
name: Giulio Cesare META

desc: I'm Andrea Doria, of the Sardegnia League. Is this your port, Commander? I see... It's a lovely place. I think I'll like it here.
name: Andrea Doria META

desc: Yo, young'un. I know you've got things under control here, but this port may not be peaceful forever. You should stay with me from now on! I'll keep you safe no matter what happens!
name: Nevada META

desc: Ahahahaha! The fact that you've chosen me means you clearly have a discerning eye. So, what now? Where's the enemy you need me to sink?
name: Hiyou META

desc: I'm... Junyou. Please give me your orders... Commander.
name: Junyou META

desc: Aircraft carrier Princeton, reporting for duty. I'm afraid I'm still a bit disoriented... would you mind briefing me on the situation?
name: Princeton META

desc: Commander, I am Houshou. Henceforth, I will take veeery good care of you. Forget all your concerns and just let me handle everything. Heehee♥
name: Houshou META

desc: I'm getting all fired up! The name's Hiryuu, Hiryuu from the 2nd CarDiv. As a member of this fleet, I'll obey your orders. I do hope that you are qualified to lead us.
name: Hiryuu META

desc: Aircraft carrier Ark Royal, at your service. I hereby vow to lend you my strength for as long as you harbour honourable ambitions!
name: Ark Royal META

desc: I am Souryuu of the Sakura Empire's 2nd CarDiv. Let's skip the formalities and get to work right away.
name: Souryuu META

desc: I am Béarn, a high mage and a humble seeker of knowledge and power. If I may ask, can I expect to find any supreme Sacraments in this place?
name: Béarn META

desc: Finally... Finally, I've met you, my Commander! My thirst has been quenched and the hole in me has been filled! Heehee... Now if you don't mind, I'm going to melt you little by little with my immense love♥
name: Taihou META

desc: You're the Commander of the fleet? Nice meetin' you! I'm Hornet, the youngest among the Yorktown class. I may not be as amazing as my big sisters, but I'm still pretty capable... probably!
name: Hornet META

desc: Good day to you, Commander. I'm the Royal Navy aircraft carrier Glorious. It's an honour to be here, and I thank you for having me.
name: Glorious META

desc: ...It's a pleasure to meet you. Or should I say... we meet again. Just keep staring like that, Commander. I want to bask in this calm moment for a while longer...
name: Yorktown META

desc: U-556, the Parzival of the Seas, has arrived! Let's see if there's really anything I can help with here. Seeing as I'll be staying here – nice meeting you♪
name: U-556 META

desc: I... assume you're the Commander? Don't worry, I can see that you're in good health. I'm Vestal. Bring your sick to me, and I should be able to assist with treatment and repairs...
name: Vestal META

desc: I have arrived, heeding your summon. Worry not, this isn't a nightmare, but rather a fateful mercy. Now, make a pact with me and become an acolyte of darkness.
name: Erebus META

desc: Well, well, the dweeb has finally showed up. You're a horrible person, walking in on a girl while she's bathing♥ So, are you gonna do something or just stand there?
name: Imp of the Bathtub

desc: Heya! My name's Neptune! Nice to meet you!
name: Neptune

desc: Are you the commander? Hmm... Very well. I'm Noire. The CPU of Lastation. You can put your mind at ease now that I'm here.
name: Noire

desc: I'm Blanc. Nice to meet you. Maybe you could introduce some intriguing books from this world to me...
name: Blanc

desc: My name is Vert, I am the CPU of Leanbox. I'm very good at first-person shooters, so please let me handle all combat-related matters!
name: Vert

desc: I am Purple Heart, the CPU of Planeptune. And you must be the commander. I will follow your orders from now.
name: Purple Heart

desc: Oh, Commander? Won't you join me in a short conversation? I'll tell you things about Planeptune. Oh, and I'm eagerly awaiting the day you come to Planeptune for a visit.
name: Goddesses' Promise

desc: I'm the CPU of Lastation, Black Heart. I've rushed here all the way from Gamindustri to lend you my aid. Be grateful.
name: Black Heart

desc: It's good to take it easy and celebrate once in a while, but especially in moments like these, you can't afford to let your guard down. Commander, why don't we spar for a bit? Don't even think about holding back - come at me!
name: Goddesses' Smile

desc: I'm White Heart, the guardian CPU of Lowee. Pleased to meet you. I'm gonna give you a taste of a CPU's power!
name: White Heart

desc: B-bastard! Where are you looking? I bet you're thinking I look like a kid! Eh....? They're just right? If Commander says something like that... I don't know how to react...
name: Goddesses' Humility

desc: I am the CPU of Leanbox, Green Heart. No matter who the enemy is, I will not hold back. Are you ready?
name: Green Heart

desc: Commander, are you having a good time? Ehehe, I certainly am. It's not often that we get to relax like this. Why don't we head out and enjoy the breeze?
name: Goddesses' Moment

desc: HAI DOMO! Kizuna AI here! Are you the commander I've heard rumors about? It's a pleasure to meet and work with you!
name: Kizuna AI

desc: The clothes from the Sakura Empire are so stylish! Commander, since it's a rare occasion, let's go take a look around! Ah, of course, don't forget to run the reel~♪
name: Festive Kizuna AI

desc: Well met. I'm Kizuna AI, the new addition to your base. I will do all in my power to be at least of some use. It is a pleasure meeting you, Commander.
name: Elegant Kizuna AI

desc: Kizuna AI here, wearing a dress, coming at you! Be it concert or combat, I'll give it my all!
name: Anniversary Kizuna AI

desc: HAI DOMO! Virtual Gamer Kizuna AI here! Don't worry, Commander, I've played AL a whole bunch before! ... Wait, I've become a ship now?!
name: Super Gamer Kizuna AI

desc: We meet at last! I'm Hololive's virtual fox, Shirakami Fubuki! Commander, now that you've called me, we're gonna have a foxin' good time! Now then, let's get to work!
name: Shirakami Fubuki

desc: Tada~! It's your favorite Shirakami Fubuki, Hololive Summer version! Commander, pleased to be your fox!
name: Beachside Fox

desc: Hey Commander, it's nice to meet you~! I'm Tokino Sora, a virtual idol affiliated with Hololive! I'll do my absolute best here like I always do! I'll be in your care, so cheer me on, Commander!
name: Tokino Sora

desc: "Hello, my friends! I hope you're well~! This is Sora, on site at a beach in a slightly different world!" Beach visits just feel so invigorating, don't they? On another note, I can't swim…
name: Under the Clear Sky

desc: G-Good Aquafternoon...! I'm Minato Aqua, the Gamer Maid from Hololive~ U-Ugh... I didn't know I would have to introduce myself in this outfit!
name: Minato Aqua

desc: Commander, good Aquafternoon~! Nice to meet you, it's Aqua, the Gamer Maid from Hololive! I'll show ya what the strongest maid can do!
name: Marine Maid

desc: I'm the lovely high school girl affiliated with Hololive, Natsuiro Matsuri!! I love singing and having all kinds of lively conversations with people, so make sure to keep your eyes on me!
name: Natsuiro Matsuri

desc: I'm the lovely high school girl, now in her extra-pure pajamas, Natsuiro Matsuri! Hey hey, Commander, what do you think? Surprised? Don't gawk at me too much~
name: Matsuri's Day Off

desc: Be cheery, for here's Nakiri! Ay am Nakiri Ayame, Hololive's virtual demon! Ay have come from the great beyond with my accompanying spirits!
name: Nakiri Ayame

desc: Be cheery, for here's Nakiri~! Ay am not used to this outfit and am a little embarrassed... But Ay am Nakiri Ayame, Hololive's virtual demon!
name: Summertime Nakiri

desc: I am the mastermind magician, Murasaki Shion! Come and be bewitched by my mature, seductive outfit!
name: Murasaki Shion

desc: Here comes Murasaki Shion, Hololive's famous virtual magician! This world will bear witness to my brilliance!
name: Virtual Magician

desc: Good Miovening! I'm Ookami Mio. Over here, I seem to be... some sort of aircraft carrier. Let's get along well.
name: Ookami Mio

desc: I changed into my swimsuit, but I wonder if it looks right on me? An outfit like this might make you feel breezier just by looking at it~
name: Summer Vacation

desc: Hello! Oh... What am I supposed to call you? "Commander"? Got it! My name is Marie Rose. Just call me Marie, okay? I'm counting on your support, Commander!
name: Marie Rose

desc: Hmm, this swimsuit is pretty cute, but isn't it a bit childish? ...In any case, if you like it, then it's all good!
name: Devilish Servant Against the Splashing Waves

desc: Phew... So warm and comfy~♪ Wanna join me, Commander? Oh... It's a little embarrassing, though, so... Don't look my way too much, okay?
name: Steamy Venus

desc: Um... Are you the Commander? Oh, perfect! It's nice to meet you. My name is Honoka! I don't know how much I'll be able to help, but... let's be friends!
name: Honoka

desc: Whoa, the sea is so pretty~! It's as beautiful as the Venus Islands! I'm so blown away, I don't even feel the heat anymore!
name: Summer Angel on the Shore

desc: Are you the Owner of the port? The "Commander"? Hello. My name is Kasumi, I'll be staying here for the foreseeable future. I hope we can both get along on friendly terms.
name: Kasumi

desc: I was amazed to see the port had such a scenic place as this... Truly, you can't go without taking this view in. Right, Commander?
name: Springside Mist

desc: It's nice to meet you! From what I've heard, you're the "Commander," right? I'm Misaki. I have experience with various part-time jobs, so... I'm confident that I can be of help to you all. Let's do our best!
name: Misaki

desc: A photoshoot? That'd be similar to what I did before coming here, but... um, this swimsuit is a bit much... Commander, is this what you're into? Geez... It's so embarrassing...
name: Golden Photoshoot

desc: Are you the person who led Misaki to this port? You go by the name... "Commander"? Hmm... I don't know how you sweet-talked her into it, but you're not fooling me. The moment you do anything strange... you better be on guard! My name? It's Nagisa. You... silly dog!
name: Nagisa

desc: Whew! The wind feels great! ...What are you staring at me like that for, you silly dog? You're the one who said you wanted to go to the beach, remember? To start with, how about... we take a stroll?
name: Blue Skies, Good Vibes

desc: Oh? You don't seem to fear me... Who might you be? ...I see, so it is you who rules over this place. Then I shall call you "Commander." I am Nyotengu. You would do best to keep me entertained, hehe.
name: Nyotengu

desc: Oho! To think there was a place with this much class... Not bad! I shall hereby be enjoying my hot springs vacation right here, hehehe.
name: Scarlet-Tinged Hot Spring Vacation

desc: Are you the one in charge here? The "Commander"? I'm Monica, the dealer! Well, dealer-in-training. I know it's sudden, but would you care to gamble with me? The stakes will, of course, be high!
name: Monica

desc: "Welcome to Monica's Fantabulous Casino! Where you can have your every whim satisfied!" ...Oh, that doesn't sound very casino-managery? Heheh!
name: The Ace of Hearts

desc: H-hmm... Wh-where am I? ...Me? I'm Luna, a scholar. Umm... You go by the Commander? Well, I'm hungry... Do you have anything to eat? I'd prefer roasted sweet potatoes...
name: Luna

desc: Hmm... Commander, I'm tired from all this frolicking. How about we take a break, or have a snack? You know, nobody knows we're all alone right here... Heehee~♪
name: Venus of the Beach

desc: Hmm? Where am I? Ohh, I get it now... I drank way too much yesterday... Ahahah. Oh well♪ There's tons of cuties here to keep me entertained❤ My name's Tamaki. It's a pleasure, Commander❤
name: Tamaki

desc: Heehee~ I've been waiting, Commander♪ Come on, there's no need to be shy♥ I'm going to show you a lovely time, darling, so you'd better get ready♪
name: Venus Shower Time

desc: Hello, Commander! I'm the idol, Haruka Amami! I'll do my best to share my dreams with everyone in port! Let's all have a great time together!
name: Haruka Amami

desc: Good evening, Commander! Are you also taking a break? If so, let's go get some candied apples and have a little chat~♪
name: A Taste of Tranquility

desc: Pleased to meet you. My name is Chihaya Kisaragi. Are you the one in charge of this port? I look forward to working with you.
name: Chihaya Kisaragi

desc: Oh, the fireworks display is starting. I'm planning to meet up with the others after this, but... Why don't we spend some time enjoying the view here first?
name: Reflections of Heavenly Flowers

desc: Hello, hello~! My name is Iori Minase! It's such a pleasure to meet you! ...Huh? There's no need for me to force myself...? Hey, wait a second, what do you mean by that?!
name: Iori Minase

desc: Blowing bubbles while sitting on a swing... It might seem a bit childish, but there's nothing wrong with enjoying activities like these every so often.
name: A Little Evening Secret

desc: Why hello, my name's Azusa Miura~ Um, this is a port, right? And these are... shipgirls? Um~ Where exactly am I?
name: Azusa Miura

desc: Listening to the wind flow through the chimes on the porch seems to carry the summer heat right away. Commander, would you also like to come unwind with me?
name: Midsummer Relaxation

desc: Pleased to meet you. My name is Ritsuko Akizuki. I was wondering what was going to happen to me when I suddenly got blown away, but... In any case, I'm pleased to make your acquaintance!
name: Ritsuko Akizuki

desc: Sorry, what? A paddle showdown? Commander, please... You play that in a kimono, not a yutaka. But if you insist... If I win, you're buying me an ice cream!
name: Paddle Showdown - Summer Formation

desc: Nihihi! I'm the idol, Ami Futami! This place seems awfully lively, just perfect for pranking~! See you around, Commander!
name: Ami Futami

desc: Summer's all about the festivals, and Ami Futami's the queen of festivals! Even the fireworks soaring through the sky can't hold a candle to how brilliant Ami is, so keep your eyes on me, Commander~♪
name: Summer Flowers and Sizzling Beats

desc: Nihihi~♪ I'm the idol, Mami Futami! You'll get to feast your eyes on how alluring Mami is, so look forward to it, Commander~!
name: Mami Futami

desc: Woah~! They're starting to send up the huge fireworks! ...Hey, Commander, just where are you looking? Did Mami's alluring yukata make you go crazy with desire~?
name: Alluring Festival

desc: Um, my name is Rikka Takarada. I'm still a bit confused about what's going on, but... I guess for the time being, I'm in good hands.
name: Rikka Takarada

desc: The train still isn't here yet? ...Oh, what a coincidence to see you here, Commander. Where were you headed?
name: Blue Sky Station

desc: Ack, Commander?! Geez, look, I at least want to be able to relax in my own room. Let it go just this once, okay?
name: Bedroom Attire

desc: Hey there, the name's Akane Shinjo. This rigging looks super cool, like it's right out of a mecha. Now if only there were some kaiju around, that'd be the best...
name: Akane Shinjo

desc: Welcome back, Commander. You sure brought a lot of goodies back for me, huh? Now then, don't just keep standing there, hurry and come to me~
name: A Vacation Just for Two

desc: Hey, Commander, what's up~? You're not intoxicated by my good looks, are you? Pssh, lighten up, I'm kidding~
name: Room of Secrets

desc: Hello, I'm Hass. I was suddenly blown away to this strange place... But, I guess it seems interesting enough here. By the way, is it okay to shoot some videos here?
name: Hass

desc: Hass here. Tonight, we're going to take a walk around the port at night. Aaaand, we even have a special guest– the Commander! ...Psst, hey, look at the camera real quick!
name: Seaside Scoop!

desc: Heyyo, it's Namiko! Uhh, wait, is this that whole getting-reincarnated-in-another-world thing that's been super popular? ...It's not, huh. Well, in any case, nice to meet you!
name: Namiko

desc: Woo, you're here! So, how was it? This meeting spot was pretty easy to find, right? Welp, let's get going then!
name: Miss Street-Wise

desc: Hello, my name is Yume Minami. I've ended up in this world for whatever reason. I'll do my best to contribute to the fleet as a heavy cruiser.
name: Yume Minami

desc: How lovely. From here, you can see across the entire port, as well as the shimmering ocean... Oh, Commander, here to enjoy the view with me?
name: A Dream Upon an Open Windowsill

desc: You're wondering why I'm so carefree? Uhh... Because I'm comfortable with you... Let's leave it at that.
name: Morning Routine

desc: Woahhh, I somehow ended up in a totally unknown place... Oh, um, my name's Chise Asukagawa! Since I might be here for a while, thanks for looking after me!
name: Chise Asukagawa

desc: Woaah, the sun's coming out! It feels so great outside after the rain... Oh, Commander! Let's take a stroll through the sky together!
name: Together, Swimming through the Sky

desc: Aww man, I hate to be seen in such a lazy-looking outfit. It's embarrassing, y'know~?
name: Laundry Day

desc: Kaiju Eugenicist, Mujina. I suppose I'm a battleship now. Just asking to be sure... There are no kaiju in your world, correct?
name: Mujina

desc: You've come as well, Commander? In that case, let's accompany each other back while watching the gingko leaves fall.
name: Golden Promenade

desc: Oh, where am I now... Ah. Good to meet you. Call me The 2nd. I'm with the Gridknight Alliance... Not that it matters in this world, I'd assume.
name: The 2nd

desc: Would you mind waiting a moment? I just have this one report. Oh, and can I interest you in coffee, Commander? Ah... Sorry, this is my only mug. We could... share it?
name: Private Time

desc: What? Where am I? Oh, umm, what may you need of me, young one? ...You don't need anything? Ahahah... Well met, person from this strange land. My name is... You know what, just call me "Princess Hime."
name: Princess Hime

desc: Oh! Guess you found me... Look, it doesn't matter what I wear when I'm drinking at home... What's that? Does me being a bit flushed from the drinks really get you that fired up?
name: Nightcap Time

desc: Augment Module Effect
name: Augment Module

desc: Augment Module Effect
name: Augment Module

desc: Augment Module Effect
name: Rogue Kaiser Gridman

desc: Hey there, Commander! Hehe, it's been a long while since I had a sleepover with someone. You know, I've really been looking forward to today. So, what would you like to do first?
name: Late-Night Alchemist

desc: Oh, do I have it on too high? It's burning in there... Or maybe that's just soot? Hmm... This machine is convenient and all, but I can't get the hang of it. What do I do now, Commander?
name: New Culinary Horizons

desc: Hehe, today was such a fun day... Oh, good evening, Commander. I was just writing my diary entry for the day. Since you're here, why don't you help me out?
name: Bedtime Memories

desc: Phew, that's everything taken care of for the day... Huh?! Commander, how long have you been there?! I-I apologize for letting you see my slovenly side... Please, just come over here for now.
name: Rest Betwixt Dreams and Reality

desc: You shouldn't be up this late. What, you can't sleep? You want to stay up with me? ...Fine, I'll keep you company. I haven't been able to get a wink of sleep anyway.
name: Moonlit Encounter

desc: An elegant verdure, a pellucid azure. I never knew there was such a lovely place at this port... Oh Commander, are you also out on a nighttime stroll?
name: Fairy Dreamer Beneath the Starry Sky

desc: I expected this sort of work to be effortless for me... but I see how wrong I was. It's not as simple as they say... Well? Are you just going to stand there and watch, or are you going to help?
name: Chief Turned Chef

desc: Hello! I'm Asuka, second-year student at the Hanzō Academy! Wait... this isn't the new shinobi base at all! This place is your port, you say? Okay then... Well, no matter where I end up, I'll always train as best as I can!
name: Asuka

desc: Blue skies, white sands, and oceans that stretch as far as the eye can see... I've seen this on TV before – this place is heaven on earth! Thanks so much for inviting me here, Commander! Now, it's time to have fun!
name: Blue Oceans

desc: I am Ikaruga, a third-year student at the Hanzō National Academy, serving as the shinobi class representative. How should I conduct myself in this foreign place? I would be most grateful if you would provide me with your assistance.
name: Ikaruga

desc: Wow! The fish are so cute! The water's so clear that you can see everything under the waves! I've never seen an ocean like this before, and being able to relax while rocking back and forth on the water... is just like one of those "vacation paradises" I've read about in various books!
name: A Moment of Peace

desc: My name's Homura. I'm the leader of Homura's Crimson Squad. I was once affiliated with a school, like many others, but... stuff happened. Anyway, don't let that bother you.
name: Homura

desc: Fish! Heheh, that's a biggun! We'll be eating good tonight... Wait, I guess I don't need to worry about food now. Old habits die hard, it seems... Commander! Hey! I know you're over there! I'm gonna let you have a taste, so stop staring all enviously like that!
name: The Shinobi Angler

desc: I am Yumi, third-year student at the Gessen Girls' Academy. Though I know not why I was brought here, I am committed to justice, no matter where I go.
name: Yumi

desc: Here, Commander – shaved ice. Say "aah"... Heehee. I've not fed someone like this many times before, so please don't get mad in the event that I spill some.
name: Afternoon Teatime

desc: I am named Fubuki. I try to keep out of the public eye, so how have I wound up in this strange place? Also, you may want to leave me to my own devices. If you wonder why, well...
name: Fubuki

desc: Ohh, it's so wonderful, being in the calm water with you, Commander... Eek! What's this?! A fish hook's caught on to me... Please stop reeling it in, or my swimsuit will untie itself!
name: Sunset Witch

desc: I'm Murasaki... from Hebijo Clandestine Girls' Academy. Umm... what is this place? I'd like to go home now... The outdoors are scary...
name: Murasaki

desc: When you're in a swimsuit, listening to the waves, eating ice cream, and playing a beach game... can't you say it counts as being on the beach, even if you're indoors?
name: The Shut-In Princess's Lament

desc: My name is Yūyaki... and I'm the leader of the Tohno Tengu Shinobi Group... To be honest, I'm not great around water... Bad things always happen when I'm around it... And this place is a whole ocean, right? What should I do...?
name: Yūyaki

desc: Phew... Nothing beats a cold shower. I'm still not great with water, but this cool and soothing sensation really makes me feel refreshed. Commander, do you want to join in?
name: Blue Sky Lagoon

desc: I'm Lala, and I'm from Planet Deviluke. What's your name? ...Just call you Commander? Okay, Commander, it's great to meet you!
name: Lala Satalin Deviluke

desc: Go Go Vacuum-kun might be malfunctioning a little, hehe... But I'll fix it right away, so don't worry!
name: A Princess Imprisoned

desc: Uh-huh, so you're the Commander? I'm Nana, Lala's little sister. This port you've got here is pretty lively... Well, it was nice meeting you.
name: Nana Astar Deviluke

desc: There you are, Commander. I'm on a real hot streak today! Wanna come play with us and test your skills?
name: High Roller

desc: Hi there. You're the Commander of this port, right? I'm Momo Belia Deviluke, but you can just call me Momo. I look forward to fighting with you, and I hope we'll be best friends♪
name: Momo Belia Deviluke

desc: Oh my, Commander. Did I wake you? You didn't look very restful... Were you having a nightmare? Don't worry. Everything's okay now~
name: A Waking Dream

desc: I'm Golden Darkness. Pleasured to make your acquaintance.
name: Golden Darkness

desc: Commander, why have you entered without my express permission? Prepare to die.
name: Pajama Status: On

desc: Nice to meet you, Commander. My name is Haruna Sairenji. I'm going to be in your care for a while, but if there's anything you need my help with, don't hesitate to ask!
name: Haruna Sairenji

desc: I made some black tea, Commander. We could drink it together, if you'd like...? These are my favorite tea leaves.
name: On One Serene Night

desc: Are you the Commander? I'm Yui Kotegawa, and I'm pleased to make your acquaintance. Some strange circumstances brought me here... But if I'm to intrude on your port, then I promise to uphold discipline in return!
name: Yui Kotegawa

desc: Come on over, I'm not scary~... Wha, Commander?! H-hey... don't go barging into people's rooms! Look, you're scaring my new friend!
name: The Disciplinarian's Day Off

desc: Are you... my enemy? No... I don't sense hostility, but instead, strong willpower. So this world is full of struggle, too. You are... the Commander? I am BLACK★ROCK SHOOTER, and I will protect you.
name: BLACK★ROCK SHOOTER

desc: The babbling of brooks and the crashing of waves were once such minor things to me. As people who do battle on the sea, you all must see something greater in them, too. But I wonder... if this swimsuit isn't very well-suited for combat.
name: Goddess in Black

desc: Now where exactly am I? Hmm... Well, this is a mess, isn't it? I want you to tell me everything, but if I'm here, then she must be, too... Oh, don't worry about it. I'm DEAD MASTER, and I guess I'm sticking with you for a while. There's got to be a good reason I'm here, after all.
name: DEAD MASTER

desc: Oh? Commander, stop staring and come over here. Let's have a cup of tea and relax... Huh? You're concerned about my outfit? Aren't swimsuits common sights here, or am I special somehow?
name: Warrior's Respite

desc: Huh? Where am I? This isn't Eustella, and it certainly isn't Aladiss... Um, excuse me, stranger, could you tell me about this world we're in? Oh, I'm Yumia... Yumia Liessfeldt, an alchemist... Well, do you know what alchemy is?
name: Yumia Liessfeldt

desc: Ah, sure. Could you wait just a minute? These are nearly done baking. Mmh, that smells wonderful! I reckon these are my pièce de résistance. Speaking of baking, I think it has a surprising amount of things in common with alchemy.
name: Everyone's Favorite Patissier

desc: I'm Isla von Duerer! Call me Isla! I'm with the Order of Eustella and the Aladiss Research Team... So hey, why am I here?! Do you know why?
name: Isla von Duerer

desc: Hello and welcome to my wonderful cookout! I tried out all kinds of special BBQ recipes! Well, everything looks tasty, right? ...Huh? Me? I'm not on the menu!
name: Open-Air Vacationeer

desc: Well, hello there. I'm Nina, a member of the Research Team... Not that it matters much to you. Anyway, I'm not sure what to do now... Oh? You want me to go to your house? My, my, are you sure that's appropriate?
name: Nina Friede

desc: Heehee, what's got you staring, Commander? Is it this piping-hot burger that's stolen your attention? Or... Heehee, well, that can wait for later.
name: Café & Diner Mode

desc: Uh, um... I-I'm... Lenja. A-although we've never met, I'd... um... I-I-I'm so sorry! I don't know anything right now, so c-could you... take me under your wing?
name: Lenja

desc: So, um... This is my first time trying this, so... I just... Ah, right! Since we're all here, let's make the most of it and have fun together!
name: Summer Vacation Time

desc: I'm Hestia, the Patron Goddess of Hestia Familia, believe it or not! What? That doesn't surprise you at all? Hmm. You're nothing like the kiddos I've seen before.
name: Hestia

desc: Hey-hey, Commander! You're finally here. I've been waiting my butt off! I've already had the full beach experience... Ah, wait, I still have things I wanna do, so do me a solid and stick around!
name: Godly Vacation!

desc: Who are you? No – Where am I? This doesn't look like Orario. You must be the one who saved me, so thank you. My name is Ryu Lion, and I work as a waitress at the Hostess of Fertility pub in Orario.
name: Ryu Lion

desc: W-welcome... Don't stare at me, please. This pub's uniforms are a little revealing, so I'm nervous. I-if you insist, though, I can make time to chat after closing time.
name: Night at the Pub

desc: Identify yourself. Are you my enemy? ...Perhaps not. Hmm... Could this be a different world entirely? No wonder I've seen so many unfamiliar things. Regardless, my name is Tohka Yatogami. It's an important name, so you'd best remember it. I suppose I'll be in your world for the time being. On that note... I'm hungry. Do you have anything to eat?
name: Tohka Yatogami

desc: Hmm? What's the matter? Oh, this? Someone gave it to me to have as a little treat! I won't keep it all to myself, though. I'll share some with you! What would you like? Vanilla? Chocolate? Or strawberry? No, the kinako-flavored one is MINE! But you really want it? Hmm... Maybe just a little...?
name: Break Time

desc: Is this... a different world from the one I came from? ...Understood. Panic accomplishes nothing. I will do my utmost to resolve this situation. I am Origami Tobiichi, former AST Master Sergeant. May I ask you to state your affiliation and rank?
name: Origami Tobiichi

desc: What do you think about my swimsuit? As long as you like it, that's all that matters. It is a masterpiece that incorporates the opinions of many different shipgirls. During that time, I was advised that it would be better for it to include *** and ***, but I reluctantly excluded them due to my high levels of situational awareness.
name: The Spirit of Allure

desc: Where the heck am I... I can't get a hold of Fraxinus... Don't tell me, we've crossed a dimensional wall?! In any case, I need to get a handle on the current situation—Oh, got a moment? My name's Kotori. Kotori Itsuka. I'm just a schoolgirl... You'll buy that, right? Sorry, but can I have a moment to speak with you?
name: Kotori Itsuka

desc: So, I got changed into my swimsuit and... What? If you have something to say, make sure I can hear it. ...Eh? It's cute and looks good on me and you want to see even more? ...D-don't say embarrassing stuff like that!
name: Waterside Goddess

desc: Eh... ah... umm... "Wooow, what a spectacle. What the heck even happened to us? Where even IS this?" E-Excuse me...I, I'm Yoshino...and this is...Yoshinon. C-Can we...chat for a bit?
name: Yoshino

desc: Um...I still tend to be a bit shy...when it comes to unfamiliar places. So...is it okay if I stay here...a bit longer? "You've already done the prep. Now what you need is the courage! Say, Commander, mind giving us a hand over here?"
name: Secret Base

desc: My, my... Now, where exactly might this be? Hmm, I seem to have... crossed into another world without realizing it. Kihihihi... It looks like things are about to get a lot more interesting. Ah, but please disregard that for now. Please allow me to introduce myself first. I am Kurumi Tokisaki. What might your name be?
name: Kurumi Tokisaki

desc: My, my. It seems that we've been seen, the other "Me". "Indeed. Such a passionate gaze is naturally going to make me feel flushed." ...So, how long do you intend to stand there staring?
name: Twin Rose

desc: Mwahaha! We are the Children of Typhoon who raze everything! Kaguya Yamai, and... "Concur. Yuzuru Yamai." Wait, what? Where are we? "Confusion. It seems we've wound up in another world." S-seriously? Wh-wh-what do we do now, Yuzuru?! "Composure. Calm down. We should ask someone what is going on. You there, please explain as much as you can."
name: Kaguya Yamai・Yuzuru Yamai

desc: I now entrust this body of mine to the beautiful flow of the sea god! Come, Commander, and give me your hand! "Request. Let us hold hands so that we don't get lost in the sea." Come on, don't be shy!
name: Blue Ocean Rendezvous
